NK040(thi)003:1: // bdud kyi gcod yul dgos 'dod kun 'byung rin po
NK040(thi)003:2: che mu tig gi phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK040(thi)003:4: spyi don gnyis pa nad gdon gzer bu la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:5: nad gcod par byed pa'i rims pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:6: gdon gcod par byed pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:7: log non gzer bu'i gdams pa dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:9: 'go ba'i nad drag po yod pa'i sar 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:10: snyem ma zhugs par nyams nga dang bag tsha med par lhan gyis phyin la /
NK040(thi)003:11: rang gis lus sems phral la /
NK040(thi)003:12: nad de la yang drag tu snom cing /
NK040(thi)003:13: sna bug gis nang du rngub cig khong du mid
NK040(thi)003:14: pas nad thams cad rtsa dbu ma'i nang la yar
NK040(thi)003:15: song bas / thams cad rang bzhin med par stong sang sang song bar bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)003:17: zhal gdam bcu gsum ma las /
NK040(thi)003:18: khyad par tsha ba'i nad rtags la //
NK040(thi)003:19: ro stod yan chad gang yang rung //
NK040(thi)003:20: gzer gyi rigs byed mda' rgyab 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:21: dbugs rgod lud pa khams nag 'ongs //
NK040(thi)003:22: de la dmigs pa 'di ltar bya //
NK040(thi)003:23: sems bskyed skyabs 'gro lus mchod ni //
NK040(thi)003:24: grangs med bargya'am lo grangs gcig /
NK040(thi)003:25: yang na nyi shu rtsi gcig bya //
NK040(thi)003:26: de rjes gzer ram gang na sar //
NK040(thi)003:28: lag na gnam lcags 'bug chung gis //
NK040(thi)003:29: gtam gyis phug nas khrag gis nad //
NK040(thi)003:30: khong khrag nad dang bcas pa de //
NK040(thi)003:32: de la ci nus grangs mang bya //
NK040(thi)003:33: gzhan yang rang gis mdun nyid du //
NK040(thi)003:34: mtshan mo rdzas la rig pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:35: rig pa nang du mi bskyil na //
NK040(thi)003:36: phyir phyung gling bzhi bskor bar dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:37: bar bar stong nyid spros bral la //
NK040(thi)003:38: ma yeng rig pa hrig ger bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:39: ci ltar gzer thung gar bcas kyang //
NK040(thi)003:41: tsha nad bcos pa'i gdam pa yin //
NK040(thi)003:42: bar bar chu yi 'khor lo yis //
NK040(thi)003:43: ro stod yan chad gang nas ni //
NK040(thi)003:45: dmigs pa gtad cing sbyang gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:46: kha zas sha chang drod can rten //
NK040(thi)003:48: grang ba'i nad sel gsung sgros ni //
NK040(thi)003:49: smad du na ba grang ba yin //
NK040(thi)003:50: rgyu long 'khrog cing mkhal rked na //
NK040(thi)003:51: sbos zhing 'khrog zhing sbrang la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:52: de la dmigs pa 'di bzhin bya //
NK040(thi)003:53: sems bskyed skyabs 'gro lus mchod sogs //
NK040(thi)003:54: bargya'am lo grangs nyer gcig bya //
NK040(thi)003:56: lus po lcags bsreg 'bar ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:57: grang ba'i rigs byed thams cad rnams //
NK040(thi)003:58: r+ts+wa sbur me la sreg pa bzhin //
NK040(thi)003:59: bsreg nas nad kyang ma lus te //
NK040(thi)003:60: rus pa sngon por gyur par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:61: ma yeng rig pa de la gtad //
NK040(thi)003:62: rlung gnyis kha sbyor drag tu bzung //
NK040(thi)003:63: gzhan yang me yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK040(thi)003:64: rang nyid tshud par bsam byas la //
NK040(thi)003:65: rig pa nang du gcun par bya //
NK040(thi)003:66: rig pa phyi ru mi phyung nas //
NK040(thi)003:67: dmigs pa'i rang bzhin gsal gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:68: ci ltar grang ba'i rigs byed rnams //
NK040(thi)003:69: ma lus sel ba byed pa yin //
NK040(thi)003:70: rlung gi nad sel gsung gi sgron ma ni //
NK040(thi)003:71: mgo dang yan lag na ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:73: bar du spyi khyab lus kun yang //
NK040(thi)003:74: g.yo zhing skig pa la sogs te //
NK040(thi)003:76: da ni rlung nad bcos pa'i thabs //
NK040(thi)003:77: rang gi lus dang longs spyod la //
NK040(thi)003:78: chags sems 'dzin pa mi bya la //
NK040(thi)003:79: sems bskyed skyabs 'gro lus mchod ni //
NK040(thi)003:80: snga ma bzhin du grangs med bya //
NK040(thi)003:81: rig pa rang sar klod la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:82: ma rung gdug pa'i gzugs can gyis //
NK040(thi)003:83: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK040(thi)003:86: grangs med bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
NK040(thi)003:87: sha zos khrag 'thung bted par sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:88: shes pa kun tu mi 'phro zhing //
NK040(thi)003:89: dbang po zhi dmad zhi gnas la //
NK040(thi)003:90: sems nyid ma bcos klod la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:92: mgo bo na zhing ma bde na //
NK040(thi)003:93: mgo bo pad+ma stong du gas //
NK040(thi)003:94: kha khar gyes la shes pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:95: klad pa bya khyung grangs med kyis //
NK040(thi)003:96: zos nas dmigs med ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:97: mig nad ling tog la sogs la //
NK040(thi)003:98: 'jigs pa'i seng zhon mgo mang gis //
NK040(thi)003:99: mig gnyis brus nas bya la byin //
NK040(thi)003:100: shul du phus btab ldag pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:101: bdud sgo bar du ha re dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:102: bem po byin nas skye med sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:103: cham pa ya ma sna bsub na //
NK040(thi)003:104: sbrul nag bdug pas sna gnyis nas //
NK040(thi)003:105: 'dzul nas sna mtshul nad rnams zos //
NK040(thi)003:106: 'jib nas rang sar yal bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:107: rna ba 'on dang gzer la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:108: 'jigs pa'i seng zhon rgyab nas byung //
NK040(thi)003:110: rna ba gnyis nas rgyab pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:111: phar ral tshur ral sreg pa bsam //
NK040(thi)003:112: lus por byin nas spros med bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:113: gang zhig lce ni na dang lkug /
NK040(thi)003:114: stag zhon mgo mang mdun nas byung //
NK040(thi)003:115: lce ni shar mo bcu gcig byas //
NK040(thi)003:116: bcu gcig kha ru bcug nas 'jib //
NK040(thi)003:117: lus sbyin byas nas skye med bsgoms //
NK040(thi)003:118: so la srin bu na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:119: seng zhom mgo byas 'jigs pa brgyas //
NK040(thi)003:120: so la do shal phreng ba byas //
NK040(thi)003:121: lhag ma lha 'dre yongs la bkye //
NK040(thi)003:122: gag pa'i dmigs pa 'di bzhin bya //
NK040(thi)003:123: bya khyung me yi gshog pa can //
NK040(thi)003:124: spyang ku sngon mo lcags mgo can //
NK040(thi)003:125: pho rog nag po ser mig can //
NK040(thi)003:126: dug sbrul gdug pa'i lce dug can //
NK040(thi)003:127: de bzhis 'gos byas grangs med pas //
NK040(thi)003:128: nad dang sha khrag bcas pa zos //
NK040(thi)003:129: shul yang ma lus skye med sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:130: mig cus mid khug na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:131: mi nad zhe sdang sbrul mgo can //
NK040(thi)003:132: kha nas 'dzul nas pho bar sleb //
NK040(thi)003:133: pho ba mig thag bcas pa zos //
NK040(thi)003:134: tho lum 'bar bas shul yang sreg /
NK040(thi)003:135: lhag ma khyung gis ma lus zos //
NK040(thi)003:136: mig bcus phan pa the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:137: glo ba rnag gis khengs na ni //
NK040(thi)003:138: mi nag dred dang stag zhon gyis //
NK040(thi)003:140: kho dga' ya le shes pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:141: bar bar stod kyi gzer sa ru //
NK040(thi)003:142: dper na ja tshag 'dra ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:143: bug pa byas nas nad rlang rnams //
NK040(thi)003:144: sngo dmar dag tu thon par dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:145: bar bar shes pa gling bzhi bskor //
NK040(thi)003:146: skye med spros bral ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:147: mchin par nam mkha' rlung skyes na //
NK040(thi)003:148: gnam lcags rdo rje rgya gram gyis //
NK040(thi)003:149: mchin pa'i dkyil rgyab bskor ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:150: mar la lcags bsregs rgyab pa bzhin //
NK040(thi)003:151: mel du zhu nas khrag tu song //
NK040(thi)003:152: mkha' la seng zhon stag zhon gyis //
NK040(thi)003:153: zangs kyi sbu gu sbyar nas 'byongs //
NK040(thi)003:154: res 'ga' khyi nag gsum gyis zos //
NK040(thi)003:155: rkang lag lhu tshig na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:156: sbrul nag 'dom dgu pa gcig gis //
NK040(thi)003:157: gang na'i rkang lag bcings par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:158: bar bar lus sbyin snying rje sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:159: rkang dang rus pa khol ba la //
NK040(thi)003:160: 'jigs pa'i mgo mang klu rigs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:161: gnam lcags s+t+wa stil rgyab nas gtub //
NK040(thi)003:162: rkang dang rus pa dang bcas rnams //
NK040(thi)003:163: snang srid lha 'dre yongs la bkye //
NK040(thi)003:164: rjes med spros med ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:165: rkang lag zha na 'jug gcod kyis //
NK040(thi)003:166: dmigs pa sbrul gyis bsdam pa des //
NK040(thi)003:167: bya khyung dmar nag grangs med kyis //
NK040(thi)003:168: sbrul dang rkang lag lhan du zos //
NK040(thi)003:169: lhag ma ma lus sgyu lus sbyangs //
NK040(thi)003:170: gang zhig mo nad na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:171: bu snod nang du zla ba bsam //
NK040(thi)003:172: zla ba zhu nas bdud rtsir bsam //
NK040(thi)003:173: rtsa sbug 'grim nas lus kun khyab //
NK040(thi)003:174: sbyin pa lus mchod yang yang bya //
NK040(thi)003:175: gzhung par chu ser zhugs nas reng //
NK040(thi)003:176: gzhung tshig nang du nyi ma 'bum //
NK040(thi)003:177: chu ser nyi ma'i 'od la thim //
NK040(thi)003:178: lus sbyin skye med ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:179: mkhris nad mkhris pa mig ser la //
NK040(thi)003:180: mi nag lcags mgo lcags mchu can //
NK040(thi)003:181: mchin kha brdung nas mkhris pa 'jongs //
NK040(thi)003:182: lhag ma bya nag yongs kyis zos //
NK040(thi)003:183: skye med sgom pa man ngag yin //
NK040(thi)003:184: bad kun spyi khyab na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:185: a dkar dag gis lus kun kheng //
NK040(thi)003:186: lus sbyin dkar tshogs mchog tu gces //
NK040(thi)003:187: lhog rgod byung na 'di ltar byed //
NK040(thi)003:188: rang lus lcags kyi rdo rje sgom //
NK040(thi)003:189: lha 'dre rang dang gnyis med sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:191: sna khrag byung nas ma chod na //
NK040(thi)003:192: sna khrag byung tshad gtor mar bsngo //
NK040(thi)003:193: lus dang bcas pa gtor mar bsngo //
NK040(thi)003:194: rgyab lag byas la mchong khrab bya //
NK040(thi)003:195: skyug nas zas mi lan pa la //
NK040(thi)003:196: mid nang sha yis bcad par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:197: 'pho bar sha sbrang rnams kyis zos //
NK040(thi)003:198: lus sbyin bya zhing nad la lta //
NK040(thi)003:199: bshal rjes ma chod log non ni //
NK040(thi)003:200: rgyu zhabs rgyu mas bcings par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:201: des ni mtha' gtad log non no //
NK040(thi)003:203: 'brum pa la sogs 'go ba'i nad la dmigs pa 'di ltar byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:204: rang gi ltag pa'i sdud sgo nas /
NK040(thi)003:205: lhan cig skyes pa'i bdud bya ba mi nag re ba'i ba dan can gcig gis /
NK040(thi)003:206: ba dan g.yab pas nad bdag bos nas /
NK040(thi)003:207: ltag pa'i sdud sgor zhugs pas /
NK040(thi)003:208: lus po kun nad bdag gis gang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:209: sha zos khrag 'thung rus pa mur ste /
NK040(thi)003:210: thams cad mnyes zhing tshims nas dga' bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:211: de ma thag tu sdeb nas kyang /
NK040(thi)003:212: thams cad nyog gis btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:213: de'i ngang nas phata ces brjod pas /
NK040(thi)003:214: thams cad lcags ri'i rgyab tu dor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:215: 'brum bu'i rtse mo tog nas kha ru bcug /
NK040(thi)003:216: kha zas mi 'dzem chu ru nyal //
NK040(thi)003:217: de rjes skye med ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:218: 'du ba nyal nyil gyi nad gso ba'i zhal shes ni /
NK040(thi)003:219: lus kyi lto rgyab thams cad nas /
NK040(thi)003:220: gra ba'am khros ma lta bu khreng shug par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:221: nad kyi kha rlang sngo na khog stod dmar du nas /
NK040(thi)003:222: nam mkha'i 'ja' bzhin yal bar dmigs pa yang yang byed /
NK040(thi)003:224: khyad par skrag mig gar byung sar bya khyung nag po zangs me'i mchu can gyis //
NK040(thi)003:225: skrang thog mchu to rgyab nas khul du brus shing zos par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:226: skran la mi nag mgo mang gis //
NK040(thi)003:227: tho lum 'bar bas rgyab nas bshus //
NK040(thi)003:228: seng zhon mi khyis bza' btung dang //
NK040(thi)003:229: khyung dang sbrul la za res dbab //
NK040(thi)003:230: snying nad snying rlung snying 'dre zhugs //
NK040(thi)003:231: smyo 'dar shes pa dran stor na //
NK040(thi)003:232: snying ni tshon rkud sna lngas dkris //
NK040(thi)003:233: sems ni mar me lta bur bsam //
NK040(thi)003:234: de la ma yengs gtad na sel //
NK040(thi)003:235: yang gcig 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i gur //
NK040(thi)003:236: de nang ma cig tshon gang bskyed //
NK040(thi)003:237: ma cig thugs kar gser gyi ni //
NK040(thi)003:238: rdo rje langs nas yod pa la //
NK040(thi)003:239: rig pa gtad la snying rje sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:240: snying nad 'jom par the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:241: pho nad zas mi 'ju ba la //
NK040(thi)003:242: mi nag mgo mang 'jigs pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:243: pho khar btug nas 'jib zos nas //
NK040(thi)003:244: bar bar sha sbrang dag gis pho ba khengs //
NK040(thi)003:245: pho nad bcas par zos par dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:246: rlung gnyis bzung la skye med sgom /
NK040(thi)003:247: mcher nad dmigs pa 'di bzhin bya /
NK040(thi)003:248: mcher pa la lcags sreg 'khor lo bskor //
NK040(thi)003:249: zhu nas dom zhon sbu gus 'jongs //
NK040(thi)003:250: de yang mang byas stong nyid sgom //
NK040(thi)003:251: long srin long dug na ba la //
NK040(thi)003:252: lcags kyi 'khor lo rtsib brgyad pa //
NK040(thi)003:253: rno ngar ldan pas long phug 'khor //
NK040(thi)003:254: nad dang long kha bcas pa bzhus //
NK040(thi)003:256: mkhal nad mkhal ma grang mkhal la //
NK040(thi)003:257: bya khyung me'i gshogs pa can //
NK040(thi)003:258: mkhal ma tshil dang bcas pa bros //
NK040(thi)003:259: gshog pa brdab pas shul yang bsregs //
NK040(thi)003:260: rtsa rgyud nang du me dmigs btang //
NK040(thi)003:261: des ni zhi bar the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:262: rdel nad rlig rlug lang pa la //
NK040(thi)003:263: seng zhon 'jigs pa'i bya nag gi //
NK040(thi)003:264: sgang pa gnyis phyung khyi la byin //
NK040(thi)003:265: shul du lcags sgang 'bar gnyis btsud //
NK040(thi)003:266: khog smad lcags sreg dmar rngam la //
NK040(thi)003:267: shes gtad rlung bzung the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:268: rtsa chu 'gag pa'i nad byung na //
NK040(thi)003:269: 'dus mdor khyung lnga'i mkhar gcig brtsigs //
NK040(thi)003:270: bad ka nor bus brgyan pa gces //
NK040(thi)003:271: gtan du bzhugs ces gsol ba gdab //
NK040(thi)003:272: 'di yis sel ba the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:273: bsen mos thig le 'phrog pa la //
NK040(thi)003:274: nor bu'i 'jig rten gang bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:275: bsen mo nor bu'i rtse la skyon //
NK040(thi)003:276: nor bu langs pa'i rtse la khyer //
NK040(thi)003:277: nam mkha'i dbyings la gzhon mdzes 'phang //
NK040(thi)003:278: rgya mtsho'i gting du dngos med song //
NK040(thi)003:279: yang gcig gang rmis 'dza' mor bskyed //
NK040(thi)003:280: rtag tu 'dza' mor byed par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:281: rtag tu lhan nyams lus sbyin bya //
NK040(thi)003:282: yid la chags med skye med sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:283: bar bar rdo rje'i dmigs pa bya //
NK040(thi)003:285: gzhang 'brum gnya' ma za ba la //
NK040(thi)003:286: rkub nang srin bu ser po ni //
NK040(thi)003:287: mgo mang grangs med bsam byas la //
NK040(thi)003:288: gnya' ma srin bu bcas pa rnams //
NK040(thi)003:289: khyung gis btus te zos par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:290: srog rlung srog rtsa 'chug pa la //
NK040(thi)003:291: dred zhon lag ring byung nas su //
NK040(thi)003:292: gshang lam dag tu lag pa rgyus //
NK040(thi)003:293: srog rtsa bcad nas sa 'og khyer //
NK040(thi)003:294: gser gyi sa gzhi'i steng du zos //
NK040(thi)003:296: lus kun zos nas sa 'og song //
NK040(thi)003:297: srog rlung 'joms par the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:298: grib sel ba'i dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:299: rang gi snying khar sgo gcig yod par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:300: mkha' 'gro dmar mo phyag na 'gugs byed lcags kyu yis /
NK040(thi)003:301: grib dang grib bdag la sogs pa /
NK040(thi)003:302: sgo nas 'grim ste lus po'i nang thams cad grib dang /
NK040(thi)003:304: de yang pho gdon snying kha /
NK040(thi)003:306: sha khrag rus gsum zos pas mnyes zhing tshim nas dga' bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:307: de nas rkang zhabs su yi ge yam ljang khu /
NK040(thi)003:311: pho gdon mo gdon rag rag su tshig zhing bsreg par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:312: grib sel grib srung gang la yang //
NK040(thi)003:313: mang du byed pa man ngag yin //
NK040(thi)003:314: gang zhig rgyu ma na gyur cing //
NK040(thi)003:315: khrag gam skya bshal 'khrog la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:316: ci ltar bzod rlag med gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:317: rang nyid spros bral ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:318: rgyu ma gnya' ma la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)003:319: rang gis mdun nam gang rung du //
NK040(thi)003:320: khyi spyang bya rog la sogs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:322: shes pa gtad cing dmigs pa sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:323: gzhan yang rang gi rgyu ma ni //
NK040(thi)003:324: rtsi shing brag zur la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)003:325: dkris shing mnar nas khyer bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:326: rlung gnyis kha sbyor mchong khrab bya //
NK040(thi)003:327: bshal dang sbos zhib myur du dbyung //
NK040(thi)003:328: shes pa gsal la rig pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:329: ci ltar gzer yang khrag nad sogs //
NK040(thi)003:331: ma cig zhal gdam bdud rtsi yin //
NK040(thi)003:334: ma yi lus la yod dus nas /
NK040(thi)003:336: ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur dang /
NK040(thi)003:337: yum chen mo'i dbang bskur dang /
NK040(thi)003:338: ma cig gis ye shes dbab pas /
NK040(thi)003:339: sri'u khong pa'i nang du dmigs la dbang bskur /
NK040(thi)003:340: btsas pa dang ga te phar phyin rten 'brel snying po gser la sogs pas bris la /
NK040(thi)003:343: rang gi rig pa dang sri'u'i rig pa bsres la nam mkha' go 'byed bya /
NK040(thi)003:344: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog dmar mo gcig tu bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:345: rang gi phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i mkha' 'gro ma bzhi sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:346: phata byas pas mkha' 'gro ma dpag med 'phros nas /
NK040(thi)003:347: chung sri chung 'dre sri'u la gnod pa byed pa gar gnas kyang /
NK040(thi)003:348: skad cig nyid la 'dir bkug nas /
NK040(thi)003:349: phata kyis rang dang sri'u gnyis ka'i sha khrag gtor /
NK040(thi)003:350: chung sri bkug cing kha ru bardzonga /
NK040(thi)003:351: dam la ma thog bar du bkug /
NK040(thi)003:352: nang nub gnyan sar gcod la khrid /
NK040(thi)003:353: mdze pho mdze mo'i mchil snab blud /
NK040(thi)003:354: des ni 'tsho bar the tshom med /
NK040(thi)003:356: phata gnyis byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:357: gcig gis rje btsun ma gri gug can gyis lkog
NK040(thi)003:358: ma sha khrag dang bcas pa btub cing bcad par
NK040(thi)003:359: sgoms / gcig gis rje btsun ma rnams kyis zos par sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:360: phata de la dus re brgya re byed /
NK040(thi)003:361: de'i rjes su lus sems phral la skye med du bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:362: 'bras la na sar rdo rje rgya gram dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:363: rgya gram steng du sbud mchu dod //
NK040(thi)003:364: khrag rul chu ser rnag khrag rnams //
NK040(thi)003:366: rdo rje rgya gram 'khor bar dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:367: snying rje lus sbyin sems bskyed sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:368: ngag mnan bzlog pa'i bzlog thabs la //
NK040(thi)003:369: rang gis lce rkyang ba'i steng du //
NK040(thi)003:370: ngag la gnod par byed pa'i rbod gtong snang srid dang bcas pa 'dus nas /
NK040(thi)003:371: kha btsum zhing mid pas lus kun mer gyis kheng nas bde skyid ldan pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:372: khros mas rkang pa nas bzung nas dbang med sa la brdab pas /
NK040(thi)003:374: rang gi nad gnas su sems can kun gyi nad bsdu la /
NK040(thi)003:375: byang chub ma thob kyi bar du sems can thams cad kyi nad med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:376: bdag gis nad 'di nam yang mi btang par bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)003:377: rlung la skyon cing sems can thams cad kyis nad
NK040(thi)003:378: gtan nas med nad rnams sdud sgo nas bsdu zhing
NK040(thi)003:379: snying khar thim / 'thun pa'i lcags rgyab pas snang srid lha 'dre der dngos med btang /
NK040(thi)003:380: der gnas snang srid lha 'dre ro bcas srid rtser yar bteg nas /
NK040(thi)003:382: sha khrag dang bcas rdul du song /
NK040(thi)003:383: gnag sdong po gser klag las nad lug nad bcas pa la //
NK040(thi)003:384: lhan du bsdus la dbang bskur bya //
NK040(thi)003:385: bdag dang gnyis med dbyings rig bsre //
NK040(thi)003:386: phata kyis sha khrag gtor la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:387: skabs su chu sbyin lan chags gtor //
NK040(thi)003:388: gnyan sar de la god 'dre bkug /
NK040(thi)003:389: bdag dang gnyis med sha khrag dang //
NK040(thi)003:390: rig pa gcer grol phur snyam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:391: god 'dre'i kha ru sha khrag bardzonga //
NK040(thi)003:392: dam thog tshar tshad ma byung tshe //
NK040(thi)003:393: nan tan bskyed la rig pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:395: spyir na tsha sdug bsngal gzer zug ci byung yang //
NK040(thi)003:396: sngon gyi las 'bras sgyu ma lta bu yi //
NK040(thi)003:397: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal zhi bar smon lam 'debs //
NK040(thi)003:398: skyon dag yon tan dag dang 'jal bar nges //
NK040(thi)003:399: ma cig lab sgron zhabs la 'dud /
NK040(thi)003:400: lhog pa bsha' ba'i man ngag la /
NK040(thi)003:401: rang nyid lab sgron nag mor bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:402: lhog ro sa gzhi dang bcas pa blang nas /
NK040(thi)003:403: dgung rim pa bcu gsum gyi steng du yar khyer la /
NK040(thi)003:404: mal du lcags sreg gi sa gzhi dmar ngam me ba /
NK040(thi)003:405: tsh+wa tsh+wa si li li khol bar byed pa /
NK040(thi)003:406: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du me'i bya khyung grangs med
NK040(thi)003:407: pas bskor bas gshog pa rdeb pa tsam gyis me
NK040(thi)003:408: ri me dpung 'u ru ru 'bar bas /
NK040(thi)003:409: de'i dkyil du mar rgyab pas lhog ro nad 'dre
NK040(thi)003:410: dang bcas pa de thar gyi gtor nas bya khyung
NK040(thi)003:411: rnams kyis zos / lhag ma nad 'dre dang bcas pa bya sgro sreg pa ltar tshig par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:412: khro chu khol ma'i mtsho nang du rgyab par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:413: de nas rang nyid gcer bu phud /
NK040(thi)003:415: rang gi rkang pa gnam lcags kyis phur pa zur gsum chu srin gyi dbal so dang ldan pas /
NK040(thi)003:416: lhog ro lhog pa lhog bdag dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:417: lcags sreg mar la rgyab pa bzhin du song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:418: de nas mgo bcad nas yar la 'phang /
NK040(thi)003:420: de nas khrag lus la bku /
NK040(thi)003:422: snyem mi byed pa phyag rgya chen po'i ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:423: de drag po thog rdzis kyi bsha' lugs yin /
NK040(thi)003:425: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bla ma'i rnal 'byor gsol 'debs bya zhing /
NK040(thi)003:426: lus sems phral la rang gi sha khrag dang lhog pa gnyis bdud rtsir bsres la /
NK040(thi)003:427: rdo rje 'chang man chad kun la bkye /
NK040(thi)003:428: zhi ma drag la dmar 'gyed bya /
NK040(thi)003:429: phal cher la thog rdzis byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:430: 'di byed dus snyems dang bral ba gal che /
NK040(thi)003:431: dmigs pa 'di yi ge'i ris med pas snyan brgyud byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:432: bdag gi brjed dogs su bris pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:433: yang rang la lhog pa'i nad phog na 'di ltar bya /
NK040(thi)003:434: rang lus lcags kyis rdo rjer sgom //
NK040(thi)003:435: lha 'dre rang dang gnyis med bskyed //
NK040(thi)003:438: phata gcig byas pas khog stod gar na sa der tshag ma bzhin du sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:440: nad rnams du ba sngo dmar gyi tshul du phyu
NK040(thi)003:441: ru ru song nas na bun yal ba bzhin song
NK040(thi)003:442: bar sgoms / de ni nang par yar langs tsa grangs med bcun pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:444: des ma thub mtha' gtad byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:445: phata kyis rang dang gzhi bdag gnyis kyi rnam shes kyi ngo bo mi nag 'jigs su rung ba /
NK040(thi)003:446: g.yas na gnam lcags kyis phur pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:447: g.yon na zangs kyi sbu gu dmar tse re ba 'dzin pa gcig tu sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:449: gcig gis phur pa des khog stod gar na sa
NK040(thi)003:450: der rgyab nas yar bal te mal du khrag nad
NK040(thi)003:451: dang bcas pa phyu ru ru byung bar sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:452: de la zangs ma'i sbu gu rgyab nas 'jong zhing kho dga' yal le song ste /
NK040(thi)003:453: nad rnams rje btsun mar sangs rgyas par sgom zhing /
NK040(thi)003:456: na sa log na dmigs pa spo ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:459: gnyis pa gdon gcod pa la gnyis te /
NK040(thi)003:461: bye brag so so'i gdon gcod gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:462: spyi'i gdon gcod la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:463: rje dam pa rgya gar gyi zhal nas /
NK040(thi)003:464: gdon chen lus la sbrul ltar 'khril na /
NK040(thi)003:465: dmigs pa gar mkhan gyi lag pa ltar bsgyur ba dang gcig /
NK040(thi)003:466: rbod gtong sprin ltar gtib na /
NK040(thi)003:467: dmigs pa rlung ltar sbud pa dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:468: gdon btsan thabs su gnod na /
NK040(thi)003:469: dmigs pa mdung ltar bskor ba dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:470: de la rkyen ngan grogs su 'khyer dgos pa yin gsungs /
NK040(thi)003:471: de la dang po gdon chen lus la sbrul ltar 'khril na /
NK040(thi)003:472: dmigs pa gar mkhan gyi lag pa ltar bsgyur ba la gsum /
NK040(thi)003:473: gdon skyengs su bcug pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:474: gdon btson du bzung ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:476: de la dang po gdon skyeng du bcug pa la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:479: khong par pho brang bca' ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:480: de la lus tshogs su 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:481: gnod byed de yid kyis bkug nas spyan 'dren la /
NK040(thi)003:484: ma bcos pa'i ngang la lhod kyis bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:488: thams cad phangs pa med pa kho la ci 'dod du 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)003:489: gnyis pa lus 'brum btsir ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:490: bdag gis sha rus phyi nang gi bar thams cad du /
NK040(thi)003:491: sbal sbrul nya lcong sdom sdig la sogs lha 'dre'i rang gzugs kyis khengs par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:492: lus la gces 'dzin med par khyed rang rnams kyis zo zhig /
NK040(thi)003:493: khyer cig ci 'dod kyis bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:495: skye med kyi ngang du khrol gyis bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:496: gsum pa pho brang bca' ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:497: rang gi khong par gdon gyi pho brang khri stan dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:499: rang gi khong par bzhugs su gsol la /
NK040(thi)003:500: rang gi sha khrag nang rol rnams 'phang pa med pa kho la sbyin /
NK040(thi)003:501: khyed rnams gar ma 'gro la 'dir bzhugs cig /
NK040(thi)003:505: spros bral gyi ngang la seng nge zhog /
NK040(thi)003:506: de nas gdon skyengs su bcug pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:507: gnyis pa gdon btson du bzung ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:511: brtson khong du bzhugs pa dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:512: de la dang po gdon brid pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:513: lus 'di dper na bdag po med pa'i khong stong sgo med du /
NK040(thi)003:514: dgra rkun la sogs sems can su yang 'gro ba bzhin /
NK040(thi)003:515: lus kyi bu ga dgu ste ha re yod pa'i nang du /
NK040(thi)003:517: glo snying nang rol rnams hab thob byas nas zos par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:519: skye med kyi ngang du lhan gyis bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:520: gnyis pa 'dza' bshes bya ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:521: rang nyid snying de gdon gyi pho brang du bsam /
NK040(thi)003:522: nad pa'am gzhan sems can gyi gdon kyang spyan drangs la de la tshur stim /
NK040(thi)003:523: lus po sha khrag dbang po nang rol thams cad /
NK040(thi)003:524: phongs pa med par khong rnams la khyer bcug pas /
NK040(thi)003:525: khyed rnams bdag gis byang chub bskul ba'i drin can
NK040(thi)003:526: yin pas lus 'di'i sha khrag nang rol 'di rnams
NK040(thi)003:528: khyed rnams gar ma 'gro la dus rtag tu 'dir 'dug cig bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:530: gdon de rnams yid la gces par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:531: rig pa nam ma khar 'phangs te spros bral ngang du lhod kyi klod /
NK040(thi)003:532: gsum pa gdon brtson khang du gzhug pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:533: rang gi lus 'di khang pa bzhin bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:534: sgo de ltag khung du dod par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:535: sgo de mnyam por 'ong ba'i bdud gnas pa'i ltag pa'i sdud sgo zhes bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:536: sgo de ha re bye ba'i nang nas mnyam por
NK040(thi)003:537: 'ong ba'i bdud des gdon bgegs rnams bos pas gdon
NK040(thi)003:538: dang lha 'dre rnams ston mo mgron 'dus pa ltar
NK040(thi)003:539: 'ongs nas sgo der 'ongs nas lus mer gyis gang
NK040(thi)003:540: bar bsam / de nas ltag pa'i sdud sgo de
NK040(thi)003:541: thag gis chod nas lha 'dre thams cad 'gro sa
NK040(thi)003:542: bar bsam / med de / dper na nas sgro kha bcings ba lta bur bsam /
NK040(thi)003:545: lus khang pa rdibs pa ltar chom gyis rdib nas
NK040(thi)003:546: lus dang lha 'dre gdon bgegs dang bcas pa thal
NK040(thi)003:547: ba rlung gis khyer ba ltar med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:549: skye med du khrol gyis bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:550: de ni gdon brtson du bzung ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:551: gsum pa gdon mgo bskor ba la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:552: ri dwags smig sgyu ded pa ltar mgo bskor ba dang gcig /
NK040(thi)003:553: 'ja' mtshon nam mkhar yal ba ltar mgo bskor ba dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:554: nam mkha' thugs phrad du mgo bskor ba dang gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:555: de la ri dwags smig sgyu ded pa ltar mgo bskor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:556: gdon thams cad yid kyis bkug la /
NK040(thi)003:557: rang gi lus kyi bu ga dgur zhugs nas /
NK040(thi)003:558: dper na na bum gyi nang na 'gro ba ltar /
NK040(thi)003:559: gdon bgegs rnams kyi sha khrag la sogs gzung 'dzin rgyu med par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:561: rig pa skye med ngang du lhod kyi bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:562: gnyis pa gzhan 'ja' tshon nam mkha' la yal ba ltar mgo bskor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:563: gdon bgegs thams cad yid kyis bkug la /
NK040(thi)003:565: lus brtsig mkhar zhig pa ltar khrol gyis thal nas /
NK040(thi)003:566: lus 'byung bzhi'i g.yar po yin pas 'byung bzhi so so la thim /
NK040(thi)003:572: skra dang ba spu rtsi shing la thim /
NK040(thi)003:573: de ltar 'byung bzhi'i lus 'di skad cig gis so sor thim nas /
NK040(thi)003:574: gdon bgegs byed kyi rgyu ma rnyed par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:575: sems nam mkhar 'phang ste spros bral du sangs kyi bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:576: gsum pa nam mkha' thugs phrad du mgo bskor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:577: bdag kyang ye nas dngos por ma grub ste stong par snang /
NK040(thi)003:578: de nas rang dang gdon bgegs gang yang ye nas
NK040(thi)003:579: dngos por ma grub par stong par snang ba yin
NK040(thi)003:580: no // de yang dam pa'i zhal nas /
NK040(thi)003:581: thams cad stong par snang ba /
NK040(thi)003:582: nam mkha' nang 'phrad la phyogs ris med /
NK040(thi)003:583: stong pa nang 'phrad la phan gnod med /
NK040(thi)003:584: thams cad gang yang ma grub pa /
NK040(thi)003:586: gdon dang gnod byed sus mi mthong //
NK040(thi)003:588: de ni gdon mgo bskor ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:589: de ltar dmigs pa dgur bstan pa de ni /
NK040(thi)003:590: gdon chen lus la sbrul ltar 'khril nas dmigs pa
NK040(thi)003:591: gar mkhan gyi lag pa ltar bsgyur ba gces so
NK040(thi)003:593: rbod gtong sprin ltar btib na /
NK040(thi)003:594: dmigs pa rlung ltar sbud pa la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:595: gnod byed lha ru 'bod pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:597: rang gshed rang la dbab pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:598: de la gnod byed lha ru 'bod pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:599: rbod gtong gang nas byung ba'i phyogs de na /
NK040(thi)003:600: gnod byed spyan drangs rang gi 'dug sa'i gnas khang de /
NK040(thi)003:603: lus sha khrag nang rol dang bcas pa de khong rnams la 'bul /
NK040(thi)003:604: phongs sems med par sil gyis 'bul la /
NK040(thi)003:606: khyed rnams bdag la byang chub bskul ba'i slob dpon yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:607: dus rtag par gnas 'dir bzhugs cig /
NK040(thi)003:609: chung ba'i nor rdzas rnams ci 'byor khyed la 'bul bsam /
NK040(thi)003:611: sems nam mkhar 'phangs la spros bral du sing gi bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:612: des kho'i gnod sems zhi nas /
NK040(thi)003:613: ma mgon lha dang chos skyong du gyur pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:614: gnyis pa ltas ngan g.yang du len pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:615: rmi lam du rbod gtong gi mtshan ma drag po byung na /
NK040(thi)003:616: sems rnam rtog mi bya la /
NK040(thi)003:617: ngas dge sbyor le lo shor ba la /
NK040(thi)003:618: bskul ma 'debs pa yin bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:619: yid kyis rmi lam cho 'phrul gang byung ba de rang gzugs su bkug la /
NK040(thi)003:620: lus ling gis bor nas phang sems med par sil gis bshigs la /
NK040(thi)003:621: gnod byed rnams la ci dga' byed du bcol /
NK040(thi)003:622: sems nam mkha' la 'phang ste spros bral du bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:623: de nas byad ma des ma tshor bar 'gro la /
NK040(thi)003:624: rab kho'i gtor khri'am hom khung gi rtsar /
NK040(thi)003:626: tha ma yang kho'i phyogs su kha bstan la /
NK040(thi)003:628: kho'i rbod gtong de kho rang la ldog go //
NK040(thi)003:629: gsum pa bden pa'i stobs kyis rang gshed rang la dbab pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:630: rbod gtong de yid kyis bkug la /
NK040(thi)003:634: byang chub ljon shing la rgyab gtad pa gcig bsam /
NK040(thi)003:637: dgra bcom pa'i tshogs kyis bskor nas sangs rgyas kyis chos gsungs par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:638: de la rbod gtong rnams gnod sems kyis 'ongs nas /
NK040(thi)003:639: de la gnong zhing 'gyod sems skyes nas /
NK040(thi)003:640: sangs rgyas kyi zhabs drung du chos nyan par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:642: spros bral du seng nge bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:643: des rbod gtong de kho rang la phar log ste /
NK040(thi)003:644: kho rang gi bdud du 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)003:645: dmigs pa gsum pa de dag rbod gtong sprin ltar
NK040(thi)003:646: gtib na dmigs pa rlung ltar sbud pa'i gdam ngag
NK040(thi)003:647: go // gsum pa gnod byed btsan thabs su gnod na /
NK040(thi)003:648: dmigs pa mdung ltar bskor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:649: glo bur nyams mi dga' ba /
NK040(thi)003:653: bdud dang rtog pa rnams skye ba'i dus su phata brjod la gcig gis lus sems phran /
NK040(thi)003:654: bdag med kyi phung po de gnod byed la gzan du skyur /
NK040(thi)003:655: brten med kyi rigs pa de nam mkhar 'phang /
NK040(thi)003:656: ma bcos pa'i ngang la lhod kyis bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:657: gong gis dmigs pa de la gang zin gong 'og med /
NK040(thi)003:658: des yid la gang byung sgom mo //
NK040(thi)003:659: des gnod byed dang rig pa thugs phrad zhi nas /
NK040(thi)003:660: bar chod thams cad chos nyid du slong bar byed do //
NK040(thi)003:661: des dmigs pa gdon thog dbab pa /
NK040(thi)003:662: drag sngags kyi nus pa khyad du gsod pa'i gdam ngag go //
NK040(thi)003:664: gnyis pa bye brag so so'i gdon gcod ni /
NK040(thi)003:665: rgyal 'gong dag gis gdug pa'i mi'i //
NK040(thi)003:666: nyer zhi rin chen sgron ma las //
NK040(thi)003:667: lha sku rten gsum 'bab la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:668: gser g.yu rin chen gnas dang 'khor //
NK040(thi)003:669: li li spre'u ri bong dang //
NK040(thi)003:670: gcan gzan rigs dang ban bon rigs //
NK040(thi)003:671: btsun pa bu chung cho 'phrul sogs //
NK040(thi)003:672: chu dang shwa rbud shal rong dang //
NK040(thi)003:673: gnag khyu bya dkar khyi la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:674: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dmigs shing //
NK040(thi)003:675: mgo dang yan lag dong ka sogs //
NK040(thi)003:676: skam khol byed cing lhu tshig na //
NK040(thi)003:677: lus sdug yid kyang mi dga' zhing //
NK040(thi)003:678: khro gtum byed cing tshig pa za //
NK040(thi)003:679: rgyal 'gong nad du shes par bya //
NK040(thi)003:681: rang gdon 'dre yi gtso byas pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:682: nam mkhas khyab tshad sems can rnams //
NK040(thi)003:683: sngon 'gro skyabs sems lus mchod bya //
NK040(thi)003:684: de nas rang lus lha khang gyo 'dab gsum pa gcig tu bsam /
NK040(thi)003:685: nang du 'bag rigs dang rgyal dkor khra gco ger yod par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:686: de'i nang du gser khri'i steng du /
NK040(thi)003:687: g.yas su rgyal po gser thul can /
NK040(thi)003:690: skye bo shan pa gri thog /
NK040(thi)003:698: re re la yang brgya brgya yod pa bsam /
NK040(thi)003:699: g.yon du rgyal mo la bsen mo'i tshogs kyis bskor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:700: phata byas pas sgo 'den par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:702: sngon rgyab gnyis nas stag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:703: g.yas g.yon gnyis nas gzig gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:704: de nas sngun rgyab g.yas g.yon gnyis nas zos par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:705: phata byas pas khong rnams dga' yal yal song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:706: phyi nang gi sha khrag kun zos nas med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:707: de'i gnas kyi lha khang 'dre can dur khrod der /
NK040(thi)003:708: klu gnas ri gnyan ma yin te //
NK040(thi)003:709: 'di yang rtog pa chod mi nus //
NK040(thi)003:710: de phyir gnyan thog 'gro ba gces //
NK040(thi)003:711: de ltar byas kyang ma chod cing //
NK040(thi)003:712: rgyal po'i mgo bskor byung ba na //
NK040(thi)003:713: thod pa gri gug gis bcad nas //
NK040(thi)003:714: gdon dang lus po 'thas pa yang //
NK040(thi)003:715: rbad kyis bcad nas thod par blugs //
NK040(thi)003:716: rmi lam gang byung thod par sbyangs //
NK040(thi)003:717: byin gyis rlabs nas sngar ltar gsol //
NK040(thi)003:718: gang zhig dmu'i nad rnams na gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:719: lus lji skyug dang smra mi grol //
NK040(thi)003:721: shes pa lji zhing 'thib pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:722: gang zhig nad pa'i rmi lam du //
NK040(thi)003:723: rta phyugs lug khyu phug ron dang //
NK040(thi)003:724: skya mi mang dang mun rub dang //
NK040(thi)003:726: de 'dra byung na dmu'i gdub pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:727: bdud kyi rtags kyang 'di lta ste //
NK040(thi)003:728: mgo lus med par khol shing na //
NK040(thi)003:729: pha ma la sogs nye dur sprul zhing 'ongs //
NK040(thi)003:730: shes pa 'phyo zhing gnyid mi nyan //
NK040(thi)003:731: nub mo gnyid pa'i rmi lam du //
NK040(thi)003:732: mun pas g.yog dang rta nag zhon //
NK040(thi)003:733: gos nag gyon dang g.yag nag gis brdung //
NK040(thi)003:734: skya mi mang pos khrid pa rmis //
NK040(thi)003:735: de 'dra byung na bdud kyi gdub pa yin //
NK040(thi)003:736: btsan gyis nad rnams 'di ltar ston te //
NK040(thi)003:737: lus po khor bur gzer ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:738: snyad med chu bur byung ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:739: mi dmar skya dmar mang po yis //
NK040(thi)003:740: khrid nas rgyal khams bskor ba rmis //
NK040(thi)003:741: de ni btsan gyi cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:742: de gsum gcod lugs 'di ltar bya //
NK040(thi)003:743: rang gdon 'dre yis gtsor byas pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:744: nam mkha' mtha' khyab sems can la //
NK040(thi)003:745: sngon 'gro skyabs sems lus mchod bya //
NK040(thi)003:746: de nas gsum sbyor 'di lta ste //
NK040(thi)003:747: rang gi lus kyi bdag po ni //
NK040(thi)003:748: lkug par smra bar mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK040(thi)003:749: gri thog shan pa dpag med dang //
NK040(thi)003:751: brdung zhing sha rus med par btang //
NK040(thi)003:752: de rgyab mi dmar gri thog ni //
NK040(thi)003:753: snang srid kheng pa tsam byung nas //
NK040(thi)003:754: sha rus khyer nas dga' mgur ldan //
NK040(thi)003:755: rang sar sun sun song bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:757: nad pa'i sems dang rang sems gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:758: gcig tu bsre la mkha' la bsre //
NK040(thi)003:759: lus po lha 'dre ma lus la //
NK040(thi)003:760: mchod par 'bul ba man ngag yin //
NK040(thi)003:761: btsan gnas brag dang chu gnas sogs //
NK040(thi)003:763: chu bo chen po'i 'gram du gcod //
NK040(thi)003:764: gzhan ma rgya ya chod mi nus //
NK040(thi)003:765: de ltar byas kyang ma chod cing //
NK040(thi)003:766: btsan gyi mgo bskor byung ba na //
NK040(thi)003:767: bem rig mi phral rir skyur bya //
NK040(thi)003:768: kho rang 'dod pa tshim par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:769: grang mang byas pas myur du sel //
NK040(thi)003:770: klu bdud la sogs klu rigs kyi //
NK040(thi)003:771: nad kyis zin pa'i las ngan de //
NK040(thi)003:772: mtsho dang chu mig ne'u seng ngam //
NK040(thi)003:773: sbrul dang lcang mo ngang dur dang //
NK040(thi)003:776: sha bkra bas ldag glang shu dang //
NK040(thi)003:778: gnyid med sems yang mi dga' zhing //
NK040(thi)003:780: rog la gsang zhing yid mi ches //
NK040(thi)003:781: de ni klu yi dug gi zin pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:782: gnyan gyi zin nam gnod pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:783: sbal dang chu rta ba glang dang //
NK040(thi)003:784: gcan gzan rnam pa sna tshogs rmis //
NK040(thi)003:785: rang gi lus kyi tshig rnams khol //
NK040(thi)003:786: ro stod gzer zhing shes pa 'phyo //
NK040(thi)003:788: rmi lam la sogs rtags rnams te //
NK040(thi)003:789: byung na gnyan gyi cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:790: sa bdag gdug pa'i cho 'phrul ni //
NK040(thi)003:791: sbal pa byi ba lug la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:792: sdom sdig ri dwags la sogs rnams //
NK040(thi)003:793: gnyan dang sa bdag cho 'phrul ste //
NK040(thi)003:794: khyad par sa bdag cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:795: rkang lag rus pa kun na zhing //
NK040(thi)003:796: khyad par lus lji shes pa 'thib //
NK040(thi)003:797: bying ba la sogs sa bdag nad //
NK040(thi)003:799: rang gdon 'dre yis gtso byas pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:800: nam mkha'i khyab tshad sems can la //
NK040(thi)003:801: sngon 'gro skyabs sems lus mchod bya //
NK040(thi)003:802: rang gi gdos bcas lus po 'di //
NK040(thi)003:803: sbrul nag mgo dgu ze ba can //
NK040(thi)003:804: glang dmar me stag 'phro ba gcig /
NK040(thi)003:805: sbal pa khra bo chen po gcig /
NK040(thi)003:806: gzhan yang sbal sbrul 'bum phrag gis //
NK040(thi)003:807: sgyu lus gdos bcas lus po la //
NK040(thi)003:808: mal kyang ma bzhag sun gyis zos //
NK040(thi)003:809: ma yengs rig pa drag tu bcun //
NK040(thi)003:811: nad pa'i sems dang rang sems gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:812: spros bral nam mkha'i dkyil du bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:813: dmigs pas drag tu gcun phata kyis gdab //
NK040(thi)003:814: rma shu la sogs gar na sar //
NK040(thi)003:815: chu yis bkrus nas gnyan sar gtor //
NK040(thi)003:816: nad pa'i sha khrag ma lus pa //
NK040(thi)003:817: gnyan sa'i gzhi bdag de la ni //
NK040(thi)003:818: gus pa'i tshul gyis 'bul bar bsgom //
NK040(thi)003:819: klu gnyan sa'am mdze can nam //
NK040(thi)003:820: gnyan gnas lha khang la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:821: gnyan sar nyams len byed pa gces //
NK040(thi)003:822: de ltar byas kyang ma chod cing //
NK040(thi)003:823: sa bdag mgo bskor byung ba na //
NK040(thi)003:824: rig pa d+aa ki'i bem po bshag /
NK040(thi)003:825: sha rus lpags pa brdal ba'i steng //
NK040(thi)003:826: gting nas 'gul skyod med par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:827: bdun las mang ba mi bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:828: gang zhig mdze nad gcod pa la //
NK040(thi)003:829: ri gnyan gdug par phyin pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:830: sngon 'gro lus mchod sbyin pa bya //
NK040(thi)003:831: de nas nad gcod dmigs pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:832: rang gis rig pa dbyings su 'phangs //
NK040(thi)003:833: lus po sha khrag dpag med la //
NK040(thi)003:834: phyi nas sbrul dang sbal bas zos //
NK040(thi)003:835: zhabs nas nya dang lcang mos zos //
NK040(thi)003:836: lhag ma rjes med stong par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:837: gzhan yang tsha tsha ga sha mgul la //
NK040(thi)003:838: dug sbrul 'jigs pas zos par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:839: sha ro sbrid bam gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:840: glang dmar dug gi kha rlang can //
NK040(thi)003:841: phas phas brdung nas zos par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:842: rma dang shu thor gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:843: zangs lcags sbrang bu 'bum gyis 'jib par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:844: bal ldag shu bur gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:845: pho rog 'bum gyis gtor bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:846: sna khrag chu rnag gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:847: khyi nag 'bum gyis ldag par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:848: zha khum reng ba gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:850: tsha tshag tsha ber gar byung sar //
NK040(thi)003:851: lcags sreg phug pas bsur bar bsam //
NK040(thi)003:852: yang yang gnad du dril la sgoms //
NK040(thi)003:853: stong nyid dgongs pas zil gyis mnan //
NK040(thi)003:854: lus sbyin mchod pa lan chags barngana //
NK040(thi)003:855: gzer 'debs dmigs pas nad gdon gcod //
NK040(thi)003:856: de yang dang po gdon gyi gnod pa de //
NK040(thi)003:857: mtsho dang chu mig la mi khyer nas //
NK040(thi)003:858: yun ring dag la skam gcod byed //
NK040(thi)003:860: ces nyer zhi sgron ma las gsungs so //
NK040(thi)003:861: tsi ti dz+wa la'i nad las grol bar shog /
NK040(thi)003:862: gza' bdud la sogs gza' brgyad dang //
NK040(thi)003:863: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK040(thi)003:864: klu gnyan sde brgyad kun sdang bas //
NK040(thi)003:866: thog dang mda' rdo ral gri sogs //
NK040(thi)003:867: 'dab chags rigs dang skar mda' dang //
NK040(thi)003:868: ka ba bu yug 'tshub la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:869: rang nyid g.yog gam khyer ba la //
NK040(thi)003:870: ser ba 'bab dang sprin gtib pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:871: spyang ki rmi dang 'od la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:872: thib pa'i rtags ni 'di lta ste //
NK040(thi)003:873: kha yo mig sle me ris dang //
NK040(thi)003:874: chu bur la sogs zha dang rengs //
NK040(thi)003:876: rgyal dang skyug la sogs pa rnams //
NK040(thi)003:877: bza' bdud gdug pas zin pa'i rtags //
NK040(thi)003:879: rang gdon 'dre yis gtsos byas pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:880: nam mkha' khyab tshad sems can la //
NK040(thi)003:881: sngon 'gro skyabs sems lus sbyin bya //
NK040(thi)003:882: rang gi sgyu lus phung po la //
NK040(thi)003:883: gza' bdud 'jigs pa'i mgo dgu dang //
NK040(thi)003:884: nyi ma la sogs gza' brgyad dang //
NK040(thi)003:885: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK040(thi)003:886: gdong mo bzhi la sogs pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:887: sdong ya'i lha srin sde brgyad la //
NK040(thi)003:888: shin tu yid mdzes skyes bu yis //
NK040(thi)003:889: phung po gdung nas yang yang 'bul //
NK040(thi)003:890: bar bar spros bral ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:892: nad pa'i sems dang rang sems gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:893: gcig tu bsre la nam mkhar 'phang //
NK040(thi)003:894: nad pa'i sgyu lus phung po ni //
NK040(thi)003:895: gza' bdud la sogs lha 'dre yis //
NK040(thi)003:896: ma bzhag zos khyer lhag ma med par dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:897: gzhan yang lha 'dre ma lus pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:898: zos zhing rang sar bun song nas //
NK040(thi)003:900: klu gnyan lha khang dur khrod mdze can rnams su gcod pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:901: e ka tsa ti la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)003:902: ma mo mkha' 'gro sha za dang //
NK040(thi)003:903: bsen mo thel rang grong rgyug gis //
NK040(thi)003:905: mo rigs madzo'am drel la zhon //
NK040(thi)003:906: sbra nag phub zhing sha khrag gcod //
NK040(thi)003:907: bdag la brtse zhing sha khrag stobs //
NK040(thi)003:908: gzhan yang bud med mang 'dus ste //
NK040(thi)003:909: mi sdug cho 'phrul chags pa spyod //
NK040(thi)003:910: rmis pa ma mo'i cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:911: rang nyid skyug dang khrag rnag 'dzag /
NK040(thi)003:912: khrag bshal khrag ni skyug dang rims //
NK040(thi)003:913: sgo yi nor la god yam 'ong //
NK040(thi)003:914: de rnams ma mo'i cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:915: ma mo mtsho sman la sogs dang //
NK040(thi)003:916: dam sri bsen mo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK040(thi)003:917: gdug rtsub nyon mongs gcod pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:918: rang gdon 'dre yi gtsor byas pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:919: mkha' mnyam sems can thams cad la //
NK040(thi)003:920: sngon 'gro skyabs sems lus mchod bya //
NK040(thi)003:922: e ka tsa ti la sogs pa'i //
NK040(thi)003:923: ma mo mkha' 'gro sman btsun dang //
NK040(thi)003:924: gnod byed srin po bdud mo dang //
NK040(thi)003:925: dam sri srin mo phung 'dre mo //
NK040(thi)003:926: ma lus thams cad 'dus pa la //
NK040(thi)003:927: sha khrag dmar gyis tshim byas nas //
NK040(thi)003:928: rang dga' kun kyang gnas su gshegs //
NK040(thi)003:929: nad pa la dmigs pa yang yang bya //
NK040(thi)003:931: nad pa'i sems dang rang sems gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:932: gcig tu bsre la mkha' la 'phangs //
NK040(thi)003:933: snang srid lha 'dre ma lus dang //
NK040(thi)003:934: gcan spyang stag gzig dom dred dang //
NK040(thi)003:935: gnas pa'i lha 'dre la sogs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:936: dgyes nas so sor song ba ni //
NK040(thi)003:937: rang dang nad pa gnyis kas dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:939: matsho'am dur khrod dag la gnas //
NK040(thi)003:940: dben gnas snying pa la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)003:941: khyad par mi gtsang mdze yug dang //
NK040(thi)003:942: dme po sdig can dam med la //
NK040(thi)003:946: mgar gyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:949: sbrang bu'i skad ltar gzir sgra grags pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:950: tsir sgra rna bar grags na da lta nyid du 'ongs /
NK040(thi)003:951: de la thog srung bzlog gcod gsum gyi shan 'gyed ni /
NK040(thi)003:953: phata gnyis byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:954: gcig gis rang nyid rje btsun ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK040(thi)003:955: rang 'dra ba'i mkha' 'gro ma bzhis bskor te /
NK040(thi)003:956: dbu la rdo rje rtsa lnga pa /
NK040(thi)003:957: lnga lnga re'i nang du rigs lnga bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:958: steng gi nam mkha' la sh+aakya thub pa la bskal
NK040(thi)003:959: bzang gi sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis kyis bskor nas
NK040(thi)003:960: bzhugs par sgoms / phata gcig gis rang gi thugs kar gser gyi ga'u kha sbyor gyi nang du /
NK040(thi)003:961: srung bya 'khor khal rta dang bcas pa tshud pa'i steng du /
NK040(thi)003:962: me'i 'khor lo rtsibs stong dang ldan pa g.yon du 'khor ba las /
NK040(thi)003:963: ye shes kyi me chen po 'bar bas /
NK040(thi)003:964: thog bdag thog dang thog byed /
NK040(thi)003:965: sprin 'brug dang bcas pa hrag gis sreg par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:966: yang na mtha'i lcags ri'i rgyab tu ded nas song bar bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:967: de ni thog srung gi shan 'byed do //
NK040(thi)003:968: gnyis pa bzlog pa'i shan 'byed ni /
NK040(thi)003:969: rang gi rigs pa'i ngo bo de //
NK040(thi)003:970: gser gyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa //
NK040(thi)003:971: phata kyis nam mkha'i dbyings su 'phang //
NK040(thi)003:972: thog bdag thog dang thog byed rnams //
NK040(thi)003:973: phar rdzur tshur rdzur d+r+wa bar btang //
NK040(thi)003:974: rdo rje'i 'od la ma lus thim //
NK040(thi)003:975: rje btsun dmar mor gyur par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:976: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis yal nas stong pa'i ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:977: de ni bzlog pa'i shan 'byed do //
NK040(thi)003:978: da ni thog gcod ngo bo ni /
NK040(thi)003:979: thugs kar gser gyi rdo rje ni //
NK040(thi)003:980: rtse dgu phata kyi mkha' la 'phang //
NK040(thi)003:981: thog bdag thog dang thog byed rnams //
NK040(thi)003:982: rdo rje'i 'od la thim par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:984: rdig chom byed cing mar byung nas //
NK040(thi)003:985: rang dang nad gdon la sogs pa //
NK040(thi)003:986: sha khrag bcas pa gnyan sal brdal //
NK040(thi)003:987: snang srid lha 'dre bstod par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:988: ma zhi bar du phata la grangs med brjod pa man ngag yin //
NK040(thi)003:989: rjes su phata kyis skye med sgom //
NK040(thi)003:990: des thog gi srung bzlog gcod gsum gyi shan 'byed song /
NK040(thi)003:991: yang na thog gi dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:992: ma cig gzer bu'i gdam pa las /
NK040(thi)003:993: thog nyid skad cig dran rdzogs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:994: gnam lcags tho lum 'bar ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:995: rang dang gnyan sar lhan du gdal //
NK040(thi)003:996: stong pa nyid la ma bcos bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:997: dkar sbyor las thog ser sbrag ma'i dmigs pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:998: 'og tu nyi ma steng zla ba //
NK040(thi)003:999: nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor nang //
NK040(thi)003:1000: rang dang yul zhing 'khor bcas rnams //
NK040(thi)003:1001: lha 'dre dang bcas gang bar dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:1002: zla ba'i steng du ma gcig dang //
NK040(thi)003:1003: yi dam sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK040(thi)003:1004: sprin ltar gtib la shes pa gtad //
NK040(thi)003:1005: dkar tshogs dmigs pa gong dang 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:1007: des ni 'ong bar mi srid do //
NK040(thi)003:1008: yang ma cig gi dmigs pa phran tshig las /
NK040(thi)003:1009: ser ba la rang yum chen mo /
NK040(thi)003:1010: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad rje btsun ma la me ri me dpung 'bar bas gang nas /
NK040(thi)003:1011: ser bdag thams cad bsreg par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1012: snye ma dang yung ma thams cad lab sgron dkar dmar nag po gsum sgom ste /
NK040(thi)003:1013: phata rkang dung la sogs 'bud nas bshad pa drag po bton phata bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:1014: gcod sgar pa byin po'i tshar tshad rdzogs la /
NK040(thi)003:1015: re re la tshar tshad ma byung nas chag na /
NK040(thi)003:1016: gzhi bdag bkug la rang dang lhan cig tu sbrul nag gis dkris /
NK040(thi)003:1017: pho brang phata sgras gdabs mgo btum /
NK040(thi)003:1018: gos kyi tha ma rdos mnan la nyal /
NK040(thi)003:1019: ngag tu mi rnams la tshar tshad byung nas thal /
NK040(thi)003:1020: khyed rang re gnyis 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du lhan cig sdod pa yin bya /
NK040(thi)003:1024: gsum pa log gnon gzer bu'i gdams pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1025: gnyan sar glo bur na ba'am /
NK040(thi)003:1026: lus la rma dang chags grug byung zhing /
NK040(thi)003:1029: nad pa'i sngun du me chen po byas la /
NK040(thi)003:1030: khyi lud mi lud mdze gos dor rta la sogs pa'i rdzas ngan bsreg la /
NK040(thi)003:1031: nad pa'i khrus chu blugs nas thabs bsur chen po bya /
NK040(thi)003:1032: nad pa'am rog gi 'o dod 'bod cing 'di shi na ro 'dir sreg /
NK040(thi)003:1034: snang srid lha 'dre rnams nyon cig 'dir 'dus /
NK040(thi)003:1040: lus de me la sreg nas thal ba bun gyis song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1041: nub mo nyal ba'i dus su /
NK040(thi)003:1042: gnyan sa go zlog bya ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:1043: gos mgo bzhug bsgyur nas gyon /
NK040(thi)003:1044: mgo phyir rjes su bstan la nyal lo //
NK040(thi)003:1045: de ni khrus 'don khra bo yin no //
NK040(thi)003:1046: nad pa'i khrag gtar la me nang du blug cing /
NK040(thi)003:1047: byed las gong ltar byed pa ni khrus 'don nag po'o //
NK040(thi)003:1048: nad pa'i khrus chu ri brag thams cad la gtor zhing gong ltar byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1050: gnyan sar yun ring bsdad kyang cho 'phrul ma byung na /
NK040(thi)003:1051: gsol ba drag tu 'debs pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:1052: khro bo'i drag sngags bzla ri bsnyil /
NK040(thi)003:1055: mtsho dkrug pa'i dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1056: ma cig gis phyag na gser gyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams nas /
NK040(thi)003:1057: klu'i gnas khang thams cad dkrug par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1058: shing bcad de'i dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1059: ma cig gis phyag nas gser gyis zor ba bsnam nas der gnas pa'i ba spu dang /
NK040(thi)003:1060: co do bred par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1061: na ba brko de'i dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1062: ma cig gis phyag na gnam lcags kyis 'jor bsnam nas /
NK040(thi)003:1063: kho'i yul khams ming nas bshigs par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1064: brag brdung pa la sogs pa byed /
NK040(thi)003:1066: ma cig gis phyag nas gnam lcags kyis rdo rje bsnams nas /
NK040(thi)003:1067: kho'i gnas khang la rgyab nas shig shig byed par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1068: de ni phyi yi mtha' gtod do //
NK040(thi)003:1069: phyi'i mtha' gtad de rnams ni /
NK040(thi)003:1070: bshan pa lag dmar dang 'dra bas mi byed pa gal che /
NK040(thi)003:1071: de na gang byed na gsang ba'i mtha' gtad byed pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:1072: brag dang pha 'ong ma slong na /
NK040(thi)003:1073: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa yis /
NK040(thi)003:1074: rig pa gser gyi rdo rje rgya gram gyis /
NK040(thi)003:1075: brag ri rming nas bshig par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1076: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:1077: gnas pa'i lha 'dre thams cad kun /
NK040(thi)003:1078: rang dbang med par zhabs su btsud //
NK040(thi)003:1079: bka' nyan gsung sdod byed par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1080: phata de gnyis la brgya re brjod //
NK040(thi)003:1081: snying rje lus sbyin kun la 'gres //
NK040(thi)003:1082: ri bo che dang la btsas ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1083: ngag tu phata brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1085: ri rgyal rming nas bshig par sgom //
NK040(thi)003:1086: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1087: gnas pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1088: mtsho dang na 'khor chen po ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1089: khros pa'i bya khyung dpag med kyis //
NK040(thi)003:1090: gshog pa sder mo me ru 'bar //
NK040(thi)003:1091: mtsho la hub btang drangs bar sgom //
NK040(thi)003:1092: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1093: gnas pa'i klu srin gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1094: shing gcig gnyan po ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1096: rig pa rgya s+t+wa ngar mas ni //
NK040(thi)003:1097: shing phung rtsad nas bcad par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1098: ngag tu phag gcig brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1099: gnas pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1100: shing nags 'thug po ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1101: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1102: rig pa ral gri ngar ldan gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1103: 'phra bcad sbom bcad byed par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1104: ngag tu phata gcig brjod pa tsam gyis //
NK040(thi)003:1105: gnas pa'i lha 'dre gang ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1106: chu mig ma slong mtha' gtad ni //
NK040(thi)003:1108: rig pa rje btsun dmar mo yis //
NK040(thi)003:1109: chu mig dkrug nas hub kyis btab //
NK040(thi)003:1110: yul mi gcig par 'phos nas ni //
NK040(thi)003:1111: shul du gram pa skam por bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1112: ngag tu phata gcig gnas pa'i klu srin gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1113: sa phug brag phug ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1115: rig pa tho lum 'bar ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:1116: rming nas bshig te brlag par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1117: ngag tu phata gnas pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1118: lam srang rgya gram brag srang dang //
NK040(thi)003:1119: gong bu mda' stong 'dra ba rnams //
NK040(thi)003:1120: ma slong mtha' gtad byed pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:1121: ngag tu phata rig pa rdo rje'i brag rir gyur //
NK040(thi)003:1122: brag gsang rgyu lam bcad par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1123: ngag tu phata rgyug pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1124: lung pa sum mdo ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1125: ngag tu phata rig pa khro bo stobs chen gyur //
NK040(thi)003:1126: rdzu 'phrul sprul pa dpag med kyis //
NK040(thi)003:1127: ri rgyal rtse mo man chad dang //
NK040(thi)003:1128: gnam sa ri brag yan chad kyis //
NK040(thi)003:1130: ngag tu phata lha srin sde brgyad gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1131: lha khang mchod rten khang ral ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1132: gnam lcags rdo rje rtse dgu yis //
NK040(thi)003:1133: khrol gyis bshig nas dpung gis btang //
NK040(thi)003:1134: gnas pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1135: dur khrod tshong 'dus ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1136: ngag tu phata gcig rig pa rdo rje rtse dgu yis //
NK040(thi)003:1137: phar rdzur tshur rdzur byed par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1138: ngag tu phata gnas pa'i lha 'dre gong ltar ro //
NK040(thi)003:1139: sgong rgyud ri sul zam pa ma slong na /
NK040(thi)003:1140: rang nyid glang po che gzi brjid dang ldan pas /
NK040(thi)003:1144: 'jug mas lung mdo kheb par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1145: thang chen sgang leb ma slong na /
NK040(thi)003:1146: gser gyi mchod rten chen po gcig gis kheb par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1147: ri rgyud ma slong ma thul na /
NK040(thi)003:1148: rigs lnga 'dom bskor dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1149: dbus su rnam snang rigs bzhi phyogs bzhi /
NK040(thi)003:1150: sku smad gnam lcags phur pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:1151: ri'i khug par zug par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1152: rigs lnga g.yas bskor bro 'khrab pas //
NK040(thi)003:1153: 'dam la phur pas bskor ba ltar //
NK040(thi)003:1154: gnas pa'i lha 'dre thams cad kun //
NK040(thi)003:1155: bka' nyan gsung sdod byed par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1156: gnyan sa gnyan chen ma slong na //
NK040(thi)003:1157: rang nyid lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pa //
NK040(thi)003:1158: spyan nas tsh+wa tsh+wa me stag 'phro ba /
NK040(thi)003:1161: lag pa bco brgyad g.yas g.yon gdeng pa /
NK040(thi)003:1162: gnyan sa der gnas pa'i lha 'dre rnams dang /
NK040(thi)003:1163: sa rdo phar 'phen tshur 'phen byas nas /
NK040(thi)003:1164: ri brag rtsi shing la gnas pa'i lha 'dre thams cad phar dkrug tshur dkrug byas par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1165: khas blangs dam bcas bka' nyan gsung sdod byas par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1166: des ma slong na nang gi mtha' gtad byas pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1168: phata gcig gis khra ther de lab sgron mthing nag gcig tu bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:1169: gcig gi chon thag de lcags kyi d+r+wa bar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1170: gcig gis chon phur bzhi de rje btsun ma me 'bar ba bzhi bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1171: gcig gis rnga sge rnams rje btsun mar baskyedanasa /
NK040(thi)003:1172: khro bo'i sngags brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:1173: rang nyid khro bo 'jigs su rung ba gcig tu
NK040(thi)003:1174: bsgom pa'i thugs ka nas khro chung zhing lpags 'dzin
NK040(thi)003:1175: pa rang 'dra ba grangs med pa 'phros pas sa
NK040(thi)003:1176: gzhi sing gi gang bar bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:1178: gos nang ma ni mgo mjug bsgyur te sa la brdab pa dang sprad la /
NK040(thi)003:1179: phata brjod cing khra ther la g.yon bskor bdun re byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:1181: khro bo kun gyis gnas gdan gyi mgor zhing lpags brdab pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:1182: sa gzhi dang bcas pa 'dar chum chum byed ste /
NK040(thi)003:1183: gnas gdon kun gyis phyag rgya bca' zhing /
NK040(thi)003:1184: bka' nyan gsung sdod byed par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1185: de ni nang gi mtha' gtad do //
NK040(thi)003:1186: yang na mtha' gtad dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1187: rig pa phud nas d+aa kir bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1188: phata brjod d+aa ki'i thugs ka nas /
NK040(thi)003:1189: mkha' 'gro dmar mo tho ba can /
NK040(thi)003:1190: lcags kyu 'dzin pa grangs med spros /
NK040(thi)003:1191: sde brgyad ma lus bkug nas bcom sgo dgu gdangs pa'i nang btsud nas /
NK040(thi)003:1192: sgo dgu ram dang me yis bcad //
NK040(thi)003:1193: lus dang dbyer med 'dres par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1194: rtsa rnams ram gyis phreng ba bya //
NK040(thi)003:1195: bol gong gnyis la ram gnyis bya //
NK040(thi)003:1196: ram yam brjod pas d+aa ki yis //
NK040(thi)003:1197: thugs ka nas kyang yam ram 'phros //
NK040(thi)003:1198: yam dang ram la thim pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:1199: me rlung sbyor bas thal bar btang //
NK040(thi)003:1200: thun rting d+aa ki'i thugs ka nas //
NK040(thi)003:1201: yam byung rlung gis gtor nas su //
NK040(thi)003:1202: bam byung chus bkrus skye med bsgom //
NK040(thi)003:1203: srog la thug na min pa mi bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:1204: mtha' gtad byed pa'i lag len ni //
NK040(thi)003:1205: dang po gsang ba'i mtha' gtad byed //
NK040(thi)003:1206: des ma nyan na nang gi mtha' gtad byed //
NK040(thi)003:1207: des ma nyan na phyi yi mtha' gtad byed do //
NK040(thi)003:1208: yang na mtha' gtad 'byung bzhi'i gzer ni /
NK040(thi)003:1209: mtha' gtad me'i gzer bu la dmigs pa 'di ltar bya /
NK040(thi)003:1210: sur nag spen ma la sogs pa'i shing gang yin la /
NK040(thi)003:1212: de nas bsreg gzhi sa steg steng rdul tshon nam
NK040(thi)003:1213: sol bas gru gsum dbus su yi ge h'u bris
NK040(thi)003:1214: / de steng shing sna tshogs gru gsum brtsegs /
NK040(thi)003:1215: brtsig mar dang 'bru'i phye ma bsres la lus bkru ba'i chu dang rtsa'i chus sbrus la /
NK040(thi)003:1216: lus la drug yag byed la ro 'dra ba gcig byed la gos kyis gtum la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:1217: khrus chus lan chags brgya dang rtsa brgyad /
NK040(thi)003:1218: sha dum bu brgya dang rtsa brgyad /
NK040(thi)003:1219: skra sen dri ma rnams kyang blugs /
NK040(thi)003:1220: skra sen rnams mgo rkang lag so sor btsug /
NK040(thi)003:1221: de nas gzhi'i steng du rtsi shing sna tshogs brtsigs /
NK040(thi)003:1222: dri chu mtha' gtad mgo ltar bya ste /
NK040(thi)003:1226: bem po dang dbyer med ling+ga ngar mi chang bu
NK040(thi)003:1227: sha dum 'di la sogs me spar me de nyid
NK040(thi)003:1228: sdig pa nag po ngo bo khros ma bsgom kha
NK040(thi)003:1230: ma 'gal sa kha nas me dmar po lhab lhab 'bar ba /
NK040(thi)003:1231: lus gnyer mas gang ba'i gseb na /
NK040(thi)003:1232: me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba gcig tu bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1234: de nas ngar mi de lag tu bzung la /
NK040(thi)003:1235: rang nyid rje btsun khros ma nag mor bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:1236: nad pa de'i lus la gnod pa'i rgyal bsen klu la sogs pa pho gdon rgyal 'gong dam sri /
NK040(thi)003:1240: lus gdon rgyab brten dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:1241: nad nad bdag dang bcas pa gdon sna 'dren dang
NK040(thi)003:1242: bcas pa gnam lcags sdig gi rgod 'bar ba'i zhal
NK040(thi)003:1245: sdig pa chen po de'i zhal du 'phangs par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1246: ngar mi de me nang du 'phangs /
NK040(thi)003:1248: lus gdon nad 'dre gcong sri rnams //
NK040(thi)003:1249: gnam lcags sdig pa'i zhal du bstab //
NK040(thi)003:1250: bzhes shig rol cig kha ram kha hi //
NK040(thi)003:1251: rnam shes chos kyi dbyings su drongs //
NK040(thi)003:1253: lan chag re dang sha dum re sprad la me nang du 'phang pa'i dus su /
NK040(thi)003:1254: nam mkha' go 'byed byed cing sha khyer khrag khyer byed do //
NK040(thi)003:1255: sdig pa de'i khar lus ltos pa med par 'phang par 'dod /
NK040(thi)003:1256: de nas nad pa gang yod de me la mchong bcol la /
NK040(thi)003:1257: rang nyid rje btsun ma khros ma nag mo /
NK040(thi)003:1258: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum bsgrad pa mche ba bzhi gtsig pa /
NK040(thi)003:1259: rab tu khros pa cha byad can /
NK040(thi)003:1260: phyag na me'i hom gzar bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)003:1261: me tho dgu de gcig spar la /
NK040(thi)003:1264: shar phyogs lho nub byang dbus 'og mtshams bzhir /
NK040(thi)003:1265: byang phyogs sogs mtha' nas nar 'ded yin gsung /
NK040(thi)003:1267: rgyab dus 'o dod chen po gcig bya /
NK040(thi)003:1268: de nas nad pa gang yod kyi tshul dang bstun nas me tho rnams spar la /
NK040(thi)003:1269: mus mus tshur blang la rgyab /
NK040(thi)003:1270: me tho re re de rje btsun ma'i phyag gis hom gzar du dmigs la rgyab pas /
NK040(thi)003:1271: nad pa de'i lus gdon gang yin pa de nag thul thul song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1272: de nas mi bzhi'i nad pa'i gzugs bzhi la bzung la me'i kha la mchong 'khrab bya /
NK040(thi)003:1273: yang na nad pa phyar ba'i nang du skyog byas la me'i khar stab par bya /
NK040(thi)003:1275: de nas thang la nar gyis bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:1276: me hom gyi sdig rgod 'od du zhu nas h'u gyur pa de dbyings su gshegs par gyur /
NK040(thi)003:1277: de nas de nub bdag gzhan gang gis kyang /
NK040(thi)003:1278: phata dang dmigs pa gang yang mi bya bar mgo mjug bzlog la gnam sa go bzlog bya /
NK040(thi)003:1279: lus gces 'dzin phral la nyal la bsdad /
NK040(thi)003:1280: phyir nang phatah rang gi thugs ka nas nad pa'i
NK040(thi)003:1281: rnam shes de thig le 'od dang bcas phar 'phros
NK040(thi)003:1282: nas / spyi bo nas zhugs snying khar thim par gyur //
NK040(thi)003:1283: dmigs pa 'di ltar byas gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:1284: lus gdon ji ltar dbyings che yang //
NK040(thi)003:1285: slong tshad nad kyi chod tshul myur du 'byung ngo //
NK040(thi)003:1286: mtha' gtad me'i gzer bu ma cig gis thugs bcud gcig brgyud min pa bka' rgya yod /
NK040(thi)003:1288: mtha' gtad chu'i gzer bu la /
NK040(thi)003:1290: rang gi rnam shes de dbang po sgo lngar bud /
NK040(thi)003:1291: rang gi lus po de rgya mtsho chen po lnga ru bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:1292: rang gi rig pa 'di gnam lcags kyiis rdo rje
NK040(thi)003:1293: rtse dgu pa gcig gis thang re rgya mtsho'i zhabs
NK040(thi)003:1295: rgya mtsho yang hrag hrag btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1296: thang re rgya mtsho'i kha nas yar bud pas rgya mtsho yang phyu ru ru byung bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1297: rang dang nad pa gang yang gcer bur bud la /
NK040(thi)003:1298: mtsho chu mig gang yin yang /
NK040(thi)003:1299: rang gi lus po dkrus la phyogs med kun tu
NK040(thi)003:1300: gtor la snang srid lha 'dre la 'o dod 'bod
NK040(thi)003:1301: / gnyan sa 'di na gnas pa'i lha 'dre sde brgyad rnams dang /
NK040(thi)003:1302: klu gnyan sa bdag gi rigs su gyur pa rnams dang /
NK040(thi)003:1303: mtsho chu mig 'di la gnas pa'i klu rgyal rigs rdo rje rigs /
NK040(thi)003:1307: thams cad nga'i lus po 'di sha khrag gi longs spyod rgya chen po 'di tshogs gsogs /
NK040(thi)003:1308: bdud rtsi'i longs spyod du 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)003:1309: khyed rnams kyang zag med kyi bdud rtsi la lus
NK040(thi)003:1310: longs spyod pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig
NK040(thi)003:1311: / dmigs pa 'di ni gnyan dang klu gnyan sa
NK040(thi)003:1312: bdag gnod pa thams cad 'phral gyis chod par 'gyur
NK040(thi)003:1313: / ro // ma cig gi thugs bcud chu'i mtha'
NK040(thi)003:1314: gtad gzer bu gcig brgyud min pa bka' rgya yod
NK040(thi)003:1316: da ni mtha' gtad 'byung bzhi'i gzer bu las /
NK040(thi)003:1317: phata kyis rigs pa dbyings su 'phang /
NK040(thi)003:1318: lus ni 'byung bzhi kha khar phyes /
NK040(thi)003:1319: ngar mi dkar ser dmar ljang bzhi /
NK040(thi)003:1324: 'byung bzhi yang de'i kha dog bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1325: nub mo bzhi la ngar mi la mgo bstan res byas la nyal /
NK040(thi)003:1326: dkar po la mgo bstan dus su /
NK040(thi)003:1327: lha'i bu'i bdud dkar po dpag tu med pas sha khyer khrag khyer bya /
NK040(thi)003:1329: ser po la nyon mongs pa'i bdud ser po /
NK040(thi)003:1330: dmar po la phung po'i bdud dmar po /
NK040(thi)003:1331: ljang gu la 'chi bdag gi bdud nag po dpag tu med pa la sha khyer khrag khyer bya /
NK040(thi)003:1334: de'i dus sgo phyi nang gi mtshams su mchong khrab byed la /
NK040(thi)003:1335: ha ha phata phata kyi sgra 'debs la /
NK040(thi)003:1336: gzhog g.yas g.yon thams cad thal lcags rgyab cing 'o dod chen po btab /
NK040(thi)003:1337: rig pa dbyer med nam mkha' la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1338: bem po 'byung bzhi so sor bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1339: snang srid lha 'dre khyed rnams la /
NK040(thi)003:1340: bem rig gnyis gces 'dzin yod dam med /
NK040(thi)003:1341: yod na lus sha khrag gis gtor ma rgya chen
NK040(thi)003:1342: po 'di khyed rnams gang 'dod la tshogs su 'bul
NK040(thi)003:1343: / gza' khyi go 'dus la nub mo bzhi mchong khrab dang ha phata byed /
NK040(thi)003:1344: ngar mi 'byung bzhi so sor bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1349: rig pa rnam shes 'byung bzhi la gtad /
NK040(thi)003:1351: lus sems phral dbyings rigs bsre /
NK040(thi)003:1352: de ni 'byung bzhi'i mtha' gtad kyi gzer bu /
NK040(thi)003:1354: gcig brgyud min pa bka' rgya mdzad /
NK040(thi)003:1355: rnal 'byor pa dad pa che zhing chos la brtson pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:1356: phyi ma'i don la brtson nas /
NK040(thi)003:1357: ri khrod byed pa de rnams la gcig rgyud gyis la dmigs pa re re ston /
NK040(thi)003:1358: lar nan ltar ma 'chun min pa /
NK040(thi)003:1359: 'di rnams sdig che bas gsang nas gcig brgyud gyis /
NK040(thi)003:1360: mkha' 'gro'i snying khrag a ma rang gi thugs bcud dam pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:1361: gong gi mtha' gtad de rnams gang byed kyang /
NK040(thi)003:1362: nub mo nyal ba'i dus su gnyan sa go bzlog bya ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:1363: gos mgo mjug bsgyur nas gyon /
NK040(thi)003:1364: mgo phyi rjes su bstan nas nyal /
NK040(thi)003:1365: khra ther gyi mkha' 'gro sde lnga khros ma nag mo lnga ru bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1366: chon thag de lcag gi d+r+wa gur du sgoms /
NK040(thi)003:1367: steng gi nam mkha' gdan du gting /
NK040(thi)003:1368: nyi zla zhabs kyi 'og nas shar /
NK040(thi)003:1369: sa gzhi rin chen gdug ltar phub /
NK040(thi)003:1370: rtsi shing brag ri mthur du skyes /
NK040(thi)003:1371: lha 'dre rnams la gnas med pas bdag la shin tu khros par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1372: gong gi mthad gtad de rnams byed pa'i dus na /
NK040(thi)003:1373: ma'i bdud bzhi lam khyer las /
NK040(thi)003:1374: lnga bdun dgu gsum lha 'dre'i la tshig yin //
NK040(thi)003:1376: zhag lnga'am bdun tshun chad la ma slong na /
NK040(thi)003:1377: gong bzhin mtha' gtad bya ste /
NK040(thi)003:1378: de ma slong ba slong ba'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:1379: cho 'phrul re re tsam byung nas tshar tshad ma byung na /
NK040(thi)003:1380: gong bzhin du ste de ni ma snyol snyol pa'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:1382: cho 'phrul tshar tshad 'dres nas mgo skor na /
NK040(thi)003:1383: de la gser gyi lde'u mig dgos /
NK040(thi)003:1384: rig pa phud nas d+aa kir bskyed //
NK040(thi)003:1385: bem po'i rkang lag gsum bcad nas //
NK040(thi)003:1386: sgyed por bcug nas yul chen bkal //
NK040(thi)003:1387: gnyan sa'i ri brag gri rtses gtub //
NK040(thi)003:1388: chu mtsho ka p+aa la yis bcus //
NK040(thi)003:1389: bem po dang bcas spel nas su //
NK040(thi)003:1390: mgron rnams thams cad d+aa kir dmigs //
NK040(thi)003:1391: mchod sbyin gang ltar dgyes pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:1393: ma chod chod pa'i mchog yin no //
NK040(thi)003:1394: de ni ma 'byed 'byed pa'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:1395: slong nas snyel ma thub na ni rgyun du cho 'phrul 'ong ba ste /
NK040(thi)003:1396: de la mnan pa'i gnam sa cha lang brdeb dkrug byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1397: ma cig gi zhal gdams snyan rgyud las /
NK040(thi)003:1398: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma kham nag gzi brjid ldan pa gcig tu bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1400: g.yon pas sa bzung la gnam sa cha lang brdeb
NK040(thi)003:1401: brdeb byas pas de'i bar na gnas pa'i lha 'dre
NK040(thi)003:1404: rnyog pas skad ngan 'don zhing khas blangs dam bcas pa'i tshad tshad ma byung bar du gzir /
NK040(thi)003:1405: de ltar byung ba dang lhod pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:1406: 'di ni slong nas snyol ma thub na min pa mi byed do //
NK040(thi)003:1407: des ni ma snyol snyol ba'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:1408: mtha' gtad byed pa la yang /
NK040(thi)003:1409: dam pa rgya gar gyi zhal nas /
NK040(thi)003:1410: ma ran mtha' la gtad pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:1411: mi dgos mtha' gtad byed pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:1412: lha 'dre'i tshig pa hur log nas //
NK040(thi)003:1413: gnyis phung ya nga'i lam la 'gro nyan gda' //
NK040(thi)003:1416: mi dgos pa'i mtha' gtad byas na /
NK040(thi)003:1417: bshan pa lag dmar dang 'dra zhing /
NK040(thi)003:1418: lha srin rnams tshig pa za nas tshe 'dir tshe thung nad mang /
NK040(thi)003:1419: ma nyes pa'i kha yog chen po 'byung /
NK040(thi)003:1420: mi dge ba sna tshogs char pa 'babs pa ltar 'ongs zhing /
NK040(thi)003:1421: phyi ma mnar med kyi gnas su 'gro bas /
NK040(thi)003:1422: gang rung rung du mtha' gtad ma byed cig /
NK040(thi)003:1423: gang rung du mtha' gtad mi byed pa shin tu gal che'o //
NK040(thi)003:1424: mi dgos kha med byung na gong gi mtha' gtad gang rung re tsam byed pas chog /
NK040(thi)003:1425: yang nad gcod pa byed pa la /
NK040(thi)003:1426: zhi ba'i gar nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i dmigs pa la /
NK040(thi)003:1428: rang nyid mkha' 'gro sku mdog dkar mo rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1429: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de'i thugs kar
NK040(thi)003:1430: 'od zer gyi chu rgyun byung bas nad pa'i lus
NK040(thi)003:1431: ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1432: bla ma brgyud pa la gsol ba btab pa la rten pa zhi ba'i gar stabs so //
NK040(thi)003:1433: dbang la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo gcig bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1434: de la mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo'i tshogs kyis bskor bar bsgoms la /
NK040(thi)003:1435: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1436: nad pa bem po dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:1437: gri gug gi btsag la thod par blugs /
NK040(thi)003:1439: drag po ni nad pa la ar gtad bya /
NK040(thi)003:1440: rang nyid mkha' ma sku mdog mthing nag bya /
NK040(thi)003:1444: 'khor de 'dra ba'i tshogs kyis bskor bar bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:1445: phata drag bya ba'i skad byung /
NK040(thi)003:1446: nad pa yang sngang zhing 'dar bar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1447: de sku yi dmigs pa gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:1449: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas d+r+wa ba ma /
NK040(thi)003:1451: phata byas pas 'khor mkha' 'gro ma mang po'i bskor ba /
NK040(thi)003:1452: phata ha drag po byas la /
NK040(thi)003:1453: nad pa'i lus kyi gdon de mtha'i mun pa gsib kyis song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1454: nad pa la byin rlabs bya /
NK040(thi)003:1457: rgyas pa la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo
NK040(thi)003:1458: zhal gcig phyag gnyis gri gug thod khrag can gcig
NK040(thi)003:1459: bsgom / nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1460: sha khrag thod zhal nang du blugs la /
NK040(thi)003:1461: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis gsol bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1464: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog mthing nag /
NK040(thi)003:1465: zhal gcig phyag gnyis mtshon cha sna tshogs thog ste /
NK040(thi)003:1466: ha phata drag po bsgrags pas /
NK040(thi)003:1467: bem po de mkha' 'gro mas btsag nas gsol bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1469: thugs kyi 'dul ba la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK040(thi)003:1470: dbu la rigs lngas brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1471: phata byas pas thugs las mkha' 'gro ma grangs med bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1472: nad pa la byin rlabs byas pas sdug bsngal zhi bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1473: rgyas pa la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1474: stag lpags rlon pa gon pa gcig gis /
NK040(thi)003:1475: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1476: mkha' 'gros nad pa'i rke la 'jus nas lcags bsreg gis sa gzhi la rgyab pas /
NK040(thi)003:1477: gzhob hrag gis btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1480: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1481: sku stod seng+ge'i g.yang gzhi gyon pa /
NK040(thi)003:1482: sku smad chu srin g.yang gzhi brgyan pa gcig bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1483: nad pa'i rnam shes rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1484: mkha' 'gro ma'i 'od kyi bem po la me 'bar bas tshig par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1487: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog dmar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1488: sku la rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1489: phyag gi sor mo rnams mkha' 'gro lngar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1490: byin gyi rlabs pas nad pa sos par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1492: rgyas pa la mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1493: phyag sor lnga gcan gzan lngar gyur nas /
NK040(thi)003:1494: lus nad 'dre dang bcas pa zos par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1496: drag po la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog mthing nag /
NK040(thi)003:1498: g.yas pas me dpung bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:1499: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1500: nad pa'i lus la me dpung rgyab pas /
NK040(thi)003:1501: nad 'dre dang bcas bsreg par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1504: bdag nyid mkha' 'gro ma ljang mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1505: phyag na bdud rtsi'i bum pa bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:1506: nad pa'i mgo thog tu bzhag la nad sel lus 'dre dang bcas pa dag par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1507: gcig rgyas pa la rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma dmar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1508: phyag g.yas na rdo rje rtse lnga bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:1510: lus nad 'dre dang bcas pa gzhob tu btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1513: rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1514: phyag na gnam lcags kyis 'khor lo rtsib stong dang ldan pa bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)003:1515: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1516: 'khor lo nad pa la rgyab pas /
NK040(thi)003:1517: nad pa 'dre dang bcas pa hrag gis btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1519: zhi ba'i gar stab nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i dmigs pa las /
NK040(thi)003:1520: bco lnga song bas mkha' 'gros 'dul ba'i rgyud rdzogs so ////
NK040(thi)003:1521: da pho rgyud kyis 'dul ba'i dmigs pa la /
NK040(thi)003:1522: bdag nyid ye shes kyi khro bo dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1524: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:1525: nad pa'i mgo thog tu bzhag la /
NK040(thi)003:1526: rdo rje'i lus la sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs byung bas nad zhi bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1529: rang nyid khro bo dkar po sbrul zhags bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:1530: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1531: sbrul zhags nad pa'i ske la btag nas /
NK040(thi)003:1533: sha khrag rus pa thar gyis song bas /
NK040(thi)003:1534: sde brgyad rnams kyis zos par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1537: rang nyid khro bo chen po sku dmog sngo skya ba gcig tu bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1538: sku la me ri 'bar ba las /
NK040(thi)003:1539: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1540: nang dang 'dre dang bcas pa bsreg par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1543: bdag nyid khro bo chen po sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK040(thi)003:1544: sdang mig 'jig tshul du gzigs pa /
NK040(thi)003:1545: ljags las ye shes kyi me 'bar bas gdon bgegs rnams tshig par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1548: bdag nyid khro bo dmar nag pa /
NK040(thi)003:1549: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1550: phata byas pas rang gi thugs ka nas /
NK040(thi)003:1551: ljags rdo rje rtse lnga las me stag 'phros pas /
NK040(thi)003:1552: nad pa dang bcas pa gzhob rag kyis song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1555: bdag nyid ye shes kyi khro bo sngo skya ba /
NK040(thi)003:1556: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK040(thi)003:1557: ye shes kyi ral gri nam mkha' la phyar ba /
NK040(thi)003:1558: nad 'dre dang bcas pa'i mgo lus gses par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1561: bdag nyid khro bo dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1562: rdo rje dang lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)003:1563: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1564: nad pa'i snying nas rdo rje dang lcags kyus bzung nas /
NK040(thi)003:1565: thal bar brlag par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1568: bdag nyid khro bo mthing nag sor mo rnams ye shes kyi bya khyung du gyur nas /
NK040(thi)003:1569: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1570: thugs las me 'phros nad pa'i 'dre dang bcas pa hrag gis btang bar bsam /
