NK040(thi)003:1573: bdag nyid ye shes kyi khro bo mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:1574: thugs las ye shes kyi khro bos steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad gang ba /
NK040(thi)003:1575: nad pa'i rig pa rang la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:1576: nad pa 'dre dang bcas pa de /
NK040(thi)003:1577: ye shes kyi khro bo grangs med kyis gsol bar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1579: ma cig gis gar stabs nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i dmigs pa 'di /
NK040(thi)003:1580: nad pa la 'debs dus dang po tshogs bya /
NK040(thi)003:1581: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro la gsol ba gdab /
NK040(thi)003:1582: dang po zhi ba'i dmigs pa bya /
NK040(thi)003:1584: des ma thub na drag po'i dmigs pa spo zhing bya /
NK040(thi)003:1585: nad 'dul dmigs pa kha bsgyur bya ba rdzogs so ////
NK040(thi)003:1586: pha dam pa rgya gar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)003:1587: gcod kyi yang gcod kyi man ngag 'di la gnyis ste /
NK040(thi)003:1589: mi ma yin la gcod pa gnyis las /
NK040(thi)003:1590: dang po ni byad ma dang thug na /
NK040(thi)003:1591: gti mug gi rgya mtsho me re re khol ba'i dbus su /
NK040(thi)003:1592: zhe sdang gi ri rab zur gsum pa shin tu rno ba /
NK040(thi)003:1593: gnam lcags kyi phur pa me nang nas bton pa 'dra ba lta bu gcig bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:1594: de'i rtse mo la byad ma'i nga rgyal gyi dben
NK040(thi)003:1595: khang khra ltem me ba gcig bsgom pa'i dbus su
NK040(thi)003:1596: byad ma gang yin pa de la bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:1597: de'i spyi bo'i steng na byad ma'i bla ma de sgom /
NK040(thi)003:1598: byad ma'i mdun na kho rang gi yi dam chos skyongs bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1599: g.yas su pha bu spun zla /
NK040(thi)003:1600: g.yon du ma dang sring mo chung ma /
NK040(thi)003:1602: rgyab tu zas nor rnams bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1603: shin tu zab pa'i gdam ngag 'di'i gnad kyis rang
NK040(thi)003:1604: gi sha khrag gi kho'i dben khang de dmar ltem
NK040(thi)003:1606: de nas phrag dog gi bsub ma ni /
NK040(thi)003:1607: rlung nag gis 'tshub ma ltar 'ur sgra dang /
NK040(thi)003:1609: tshag sgra dang bcas pa kyi li li sga ra
NK040(thi)003:1610: ra g.yon du 'khor ba gdam ngag 'di'i gnad kyis
NK040(thi)003:1611: / kho'i mgo thog gi bla ma yar bkyag nas /
NK040(thi)003:1612: bla ma de yang khrag gi sub mas kha phyir log tu bskor nas /
NK040(thi)003:1613: de rnams kho la zhe log nas kho dang bye bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1614: de bzhin du kho'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i las ngan stobs dang /
NK040(thi)003:1615: rang gi gdam ngag gis gnad kyis /
NK040(thi)003:1616: kho rang gi bsgom pa'i lha dang lha ma srin
NK040(thi)003:1617: sde brgyad dang bcas pa'i bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad
NK040(thi)003:1618: cu dang bcas pa thams cad kyang /
NK040(thi)003:1619: khrag gi sub mas kha phyir log tu kyi li li sga ra ra 'khor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1620: yid 'khrug ste byad ma la le lan bdas nas /
NK040(thi)003:1624: de nas rang gi lag pa g.yas pas sngar bsgom
NK040(thi)003:1625: pa'i ri rab rgya mtsho dang bcas pa de yar
NK040(thi)003:1627: byad ma'i dben khang chos skyong dang bcas pa de
NK040(thi)003:1628: ri rab phur pa'i dbal so dang 'dra ba des
NK040(thi)003:1629: dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi la tham gyis 'dzer
NK040(thi)003:1630: nas sha khrag thams cad chal gyis 'thor bar bsam
NK040(thi)003:1631: / kho'i chos skyongs lha srin sde brgyad bgegs rigs
NK040(thi)003:1632: stong phrag brgyad cu po thams cad kyis kho'i sha
NK040(thi)003:1633: zos khrag 'thung rus pa 'chom par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1634: lus kyi lhag ma ma lus bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1635: kho rang gi rnam par shes pa chos nyid du bstim par bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:1636: de nas rang nyid kyis kyang stong pa nyid dang
NK040(thi)003:1637: snying rje'i ngang la ma yeng bar gnas par bya'o
NK040(thi)003:1638: // de yang rang shug gi snying rje gcig skyes tshar tshad yin no //
NK040(thi)003:1639: cho 'phrul che na bzang tshar tshad gzhung dang 'dra ba yin gsungs /
NK040(thi)003:1640: byad ma ngos zin na r+n+ri'am tri las snga ma bzhin bsgom par bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:1641: spyir byad ma'am lha 'dre gang la yang rung ste /
NK040(thi)003:1642: rang gi sha khrag sub bskor gyis bskor ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:1643: kho rang gis bsam sbyor ngan pa'i stobs kyis /
NK040(thi)003:1644: rang gshed rang la bskor bas /
NK040(thi)003:1645: kho'i yi dam chos skyongs nye du yon bdag rnams kyis /
NK040(thi)003:1647: sde brgyad rnams kyi le lan brdas nas /
NK040(thi)003:1648: kho'i sha zos khrag 'thung ba man ngag yin /
NK040(thi)003:1649: mi ma yin lha 'dre la byed na /
NK040(thi)003:1650: sngar gyi dben khang mal du /
NK040(thi)003:1651: lha khang bsgom pa'i nang du mi ma yin gyi rgyal po la /
NK040(thi)003:1655: btsan la skya mi mi rta dmar po bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1656: bdud la mi nag rta nag can /
NK040(thi)003:1657: klu la mtsho kyi li li dang /
NK040(thi)003:1658: chu mig mgo dgu pa'i nang na mi lus sbrul mgo'i gdeng ka bdun dang ldan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1660: 'khor sbrul dang sbal pa nya dang lcong mo dud 'gro sna tshogs kyis bskor bar bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:1661: spyir lha 'dre'i cho 'phrul mngon yang rung /
NK040(thi)003:1662: rmi lam du byung yang rung ste /
NK040(thi)003:1663: gang yin pa de sha khrag mtsho dkyil gyi ri rab zur gsum du bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1664: rang gis sha khrag thams cad kyi rgya mtsho kyi li li 'khor bas /
NK040(thi)003:1665: lha 'dre rnams mgo 'khor nas yid 'khrug ste /
NK040(thi)003:1666: khrag lhad lhad skyugs par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:1667: yang ri rab rgya mtsho dang bcas par yar blang
NK040(thi)003:1668: nas mar rgyab pas lha 'dre rnams sha khrag dmar
NK040(thi)003:1669: tha ra ra thor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1671: gdon ngos ma zin na r+n+ri'am tri las gong ltar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1672: bsnyon pa la byed na lus lha khang du bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:1673: gang la yang cho 'phrul byung na 'dod thog yin /
NK040(thi)003:1674: de dus brtson 'grus shin tu bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:1675: nub gcig gnyis la cho 'phrul lhung gi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:1676: byams dang snying rje gnad du bsnun /
NK040(thi)003:1677: gcod kyis rgyal khams gang lag kyang //
NK040(thi)003:1678: yang rigs 'di 'dra'i gdam pa ma bkod phyir //
NK040(thi)003:1679: gru gsum snying gi dbus su bzhag nas ni //
NK040(thi)003:1680: bka' rgya dam du gnas par bya //
NK040(thi)003:1682: gcod kyi nang gi yang gcod 'di //
NK040(thi)003:1683: su la'ang ma spel thugs kyi nang du bcug /
NK040(thi)003:1684: gces pas bu'i lag tu bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:1685: gcig rgyud ma gtogs gnyis la spel ba na //
NK040(thi)003:1686: stong gsum mkha' 'gros chad pa chod //
NK040(thi)003:1687: zab brgyud g.yog mo la byin te //
NK040(thi)003:1689: yang na byad bzlog bsdus pa 'di ma cig gi dmigs pa phran tsheg las /
NK040(thi)003:1691: rang gi spyi bor mda' gang gi sar lab sgron mthing nag gcig bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1692: rang gi rnam par shes pa de yar spar /
NK040(thi)003:1693: lus po de ma cig lab sgron gyis bshus nas /
NK040(thi)003:1694: phyal gyis bting pa'i steng du /
NK040(thi)003:1695: rang gi sha rus khrag gsum spung pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:1696: rang gi mnyam por 'ong ba'i bdud bos nas /
NK040(thi)003:1697: byad ma rbod gtong dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:1698: byad ma lha srung dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:1699: byad ma sde tshan dang bcas pa 'dir shog cig /
NK040(thi)003:1700: ces bos pas der 'dus par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1701: lab sgron gyis lpags pa'i kha bsdus nas /
NK040(thi)003:1702: rgyu mas bcings te yang yang rgyab pas byad ma
NK040(thi)003:1703: gnod byed kyi sha khrag dmar thar thar song bar
NK040(thi)003:1704: bsam / dmigs pa lcags sreg gi sa gzhi la brdab pas /
NK040(thi)003:1705: gzhob rag rag btang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1706: phata brgya stong ci mang bya /
NK040(thi)003:1708: bla ma d+aa ki'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)003:1709: drag sngags ring mo'i khung phyung ba la 'di la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:1713: gsum du gcod pa zer gsungs /
NK040(thi)003:1714: de gsum chun gcig tu gcod pa la /
NK040(thi)003:1715: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed spyi dang mthun /
NK040(thi)003:1716: dngos gzhi nyams su len pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1717: gang shi ba de'i ro'am ro gos la gri sri sha ba'i mgo can bri /
NK040(thi)003:1718: gzugs skye mched tshang ba bya /
NK040(thi)003:1719: rang gi phyogs bzhi tho bzhi brtsegs /
NK040(thi)003:1720: tho bzhi'i rtsa ru dug shing gi ling ga bzhi bcings la /
NK040(thi)003:1721: dog pa sngo dmar gyi rgya gram du bres pas bsgril /
NK040(thi)003:1722: de nas rang nyid kyi phata brjod pas pha dam
NK040(thi)003:1723: pa rgya gar sku mdog mthing nag bzhengs pa'i tshu
NK040(thi)003:1725: gsum mche ba rab tu gtsigs pa /
NK040(thi)003:1726: sku la dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyi brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1727: g.yas pas thod pa'i d+aa ma ru dkrol ba /
NK040(thi)003:1728: g.yon pas mi rkang gis gling bu tshag tshag 'bud pa gcig bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1729: de'i dbu thog du bam gsar snying bsnol ma'i khri steng du /
NK040(thi)003:1730: rje btsun rdo rje rnal 'byor ma sku mdog zangs kyi mdog lta bu /
NK040(thi)003:1731: dbu skra thor lcogs gyen du bcing ba /
NK040(thi)003:1732: spyan gsum mi mngon pa'i dbyings su gzigs pa /
NK040(thi)003:1733: thod skam gyi dbu brgyan dang /
NK040(thi)003:1734: thod rlon gyi do shal byas pa /
NK040(thi)003:1735: sku la zhing chen g.yang gzhi khrag 'dzag pa /
NK040(thi)003:1736: g.yas pas zangs kyi gri gug rdo rje'i yu ba byas pa nam mkhar 'phyar ba /
NK040(thi)003:1737: g.yon pas zangs ma'i zhags pa dmar weng nge ba
NK040(thi)003:1738: gru mor bkon zhing thod zhal thugs kar 'dzin pa
NK040(thi)003:1740: bkyag na ri yang 'khyog pa mnan na sa gzhi non pa /
NK040(thi)003:1741: sku gzi brjid dang ldan pa gcig bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1743: dur khrod kyi mkha' 'gro sku mdog nag mo /
NK040(thi)003:1746: sku la dur khrod kyi rgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:1747: 'khor du nag mo 'bum gyis bskor ba bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1748: g.yon phyogs su las kyi mkha' 'gro sku mdog ljang nag /
NK040(thi)003:1749: g.yas ral gri g.yon thod khrag /
NK040(thi)003:1750: sku gar stabs kyi 'gying bag can la mkha' 'bum gyis bskor bar bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:1751: de la sogs pa'i mkha' 'gro ma grangs med pas bskor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1752: de nas rang gis phata brjod pas /
NK040(thi)003:1753: thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas /
NK040(thi)003:1754: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad nas /
NK040(thi)003:1755: gri sri la sogs gang yin pa /
NK040(thi)003:1756: dang po nad kyi sna 'dren pa /
NK040(thi)003:1757: bar du nad kyi tshang bca' ba /
NK040(thi)003:1759: khong gi srog gcod pa de'i gtso byas pa'i snang
NK040(thi)003:1760: zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre rnams 'od zer lcags kyu
NK040(thi)003:1761: lta bu'i snying dkar nag mtshams nas bzung zhing bkug
NK040(thi)003:1762: pas / kha rlung gis ded pa bzhin du 'tshub
NK040(thi)003:1763: nyi li li bsdus nas ro ras dang tho bzhi
NK040(thi)003:1765: gzhan yang gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis kyi gtso byas pa rnams mdun du bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1766: de'i rgyab tu rang 'dra ba grangs med kyis ha
NK040(thi)003:1767: dang phata kyi sgra di ri ri byed pas bskor
NK040(thi)003:1768: bar bsgom nas / snying rje tshad med pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:1769: sha khyer khrag khyer la sogs spyi dang mthun /
NK040(thi)003:1770: rjes su bsngo ba smon lam btab nas /
NK040(thi)003:1772: de nas skad cig gis ngang la /
NK040(thi)003:1773: rang gis thugs ka nas h'u mthing nag grangs med pa 'phros nas /
NK040(thi)003:1774: gnam sa bar snang sa rdo brag rtsi shing nags tshal kun la phogs pas /
NK040(thi)003:1775: de rnams kyang mkha' 'gro ma grangs med par gyur nas /
NK040(thi)003:1776: thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar mo g.yas lcags kyu /
NK040(thi)003:1777: g.yon pas thod pa'i zhal bu 'dzin pa /
NK040(thi)003:1778: stong gsum 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyis tshe
NK040(thi)003:1779: bkrag mdangs gzi brjid thams cad 'byung ba'i bcud mdangs
NK040(thi)003:1780: kun bsdus nas thod pa'i zhal bu rnams ltebs kyis
NK040(thi)003:1781: bkang nas / mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis gsol nas mnyes par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:1782: de nas mkha' 'gro ma thams cad gcig la gcig
NK040(thi)003:1783: thim nas mkha' 'gro ma de yang rang gi thugs
NK040(thi)003:1784: kar thim / rang bkrag mdangs dang gzi brjid ldan par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1785: de ma thag tu phata brjod pas /
NK040(thi)003:1786: rang gi thugs ka nas mkha' 'gro ma sku dmog dmar mo g.yas gri gug /
NK040(thi)003:1787: g.yon lcags kyu 'dzin pa dpag tu med pa 'phros nas /
NK040(thi)003:1788: gri sri la sogs gang yin de'i rke gri gug gis rbad rbad bcad par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1789: de nas rang nyid mkha' 'gro ma des kho'i lus
NK040(thi)003:1790: shag gis bshas nas lpags pa de phyal gyis bting
NK040(thi)003:1791: ba der / bdag lus tha mal pa'i sha khrag dang /
NK040(thi)003:1792: kho'i sha khrag rnam shes bcas pa nyil gyis spung par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1793: de rnams thams cad mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis /
NK040(thi)003:1794: gtso 'khor dang bcas pa kun gyis gsol nas rjes kyang med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1795: de nas phyi thun gcig la rang gi phata gcig brjod pas /
NK040(thi)003:1796: thugs ka nas mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog dmar mo gcig gis g.yas pas zangs ma'i gri gug /
NK040(thi)003:1797: g.yon pa zangs ma'i zhag pa dmar po bsnam nas /
NK040(thi)003:1798: gri sri'i mgul du 'phangs pas hrig gis bzung nas /
NK040(thi)003:1800: skad ngan tse re re 'don cing bdag la srog snying phul ba'i sgra 'don par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1801: bar bar gri gug gis lus dum bur gtub nas /
NK040(thi)003:1802: gzugs phung sha khrag nyil gyi btang ba de /
NK040(thi)003:1803: rang dang gtso 'khor kun gyis zos pas lhag ma med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1804: brgya bskor dag tu bzung ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:1805: de nas shing mi'i mgul gyi snal ma sngo dmar la 'then cing /
NK040(thi)003:1806: chos tshad ma byung bar du gcun pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:1808: yon bdag pho mo'i ngar mi dang /
NK040(thi)003:1809: ro ras shing gis me rnams drag po'i me la sreg pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:1810: dmigs pa ni rang gi mdun du rje btsun ma
NK040(thi)003:1811: me zhal gnam du gdangs pa'i nang du bskyed pa'i
NK040(thi)003:1812: gzugs dang rang gi sha khrag dang bcas pa nyi
NK040(thi)003:1813: li li spung spung song bar bsam zhing me sbar
NK040(thi)003:1816: rgyal ba'i yum chen rnal 'byor ma //
NK040(thi)003:1817: sku mdog dmar mo drag po'i tshul //
NK040(thi)003:1818: zhabs gnyis gar thabs bdud bzhi 'dul //
NK040(thi)003:1819: drag po'i mche ba rab tu gtsigs //
NK040(thi)003:1820: ral pa dmar ser gyen du brjid //
NK040(thi)003:1821: g.yas pas gri gug 'phyar ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:1822: dur khrod gnas brgyad tshogs su bsgrol //
NK040(thi)003:1823: g.yon pas thod khrag 'dzin pa yis //
NK040(thi)003:1824: gri sri gri nag phug sri dang //
NK040(thi)003:1825: chung sri gnod byed zhal du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1827: drag po'i gnas su sku bskyod la //
NK040(thi)003:1828: chos nyid bden pa'i me chen spar du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1829: rnam rtog dug lnga'i phung po bsreg tu gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1830: bgas chags 'khrul pa'i rkyen snang gzhom du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1832: drag po'i gnas nas sku bskyod la //
NK040(thi)003:1833: chos nyid bden pa'i me chen spar du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1834: rnam rtog dug lnga'i phung po bsreg tu gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1835: bag chags 'khrul pa'i rkyen snang gzhom du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1836: rang byung gsal ba'i me chen sbar du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1837: bag chags 'khrul ba'i gnod byed bsreg tu gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1838: 'khrul pa gnyis 'dzin gyi bdud chen gzhom du gsol //
NK040(thi)003:1840: de nas sngags brjod pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1841: bam ha ri ni sa dz+wa la ram /
NK040(thi)003:1842: gnod byed gri sri sha trum ma ra rbad nan /
NK040(thi)003:1843: ces brjod la sbyin sreg blug go //
NK040(thi)003:1844: yon bdag pho mo kun lag pa sbrel la bskor /
NK040(thi)003:1845: ngar mi sha dum khrag dum sreg /
NK040(thi)003:1846: bar bar du bdag gzhan kun gyi rig pa spar zhing /
NK040(thi)003:1847: mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:1848: rjes su mkha' 'gro bzhi'i brdung ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:1850: bro 'di gang dang gang gi bro //
NK040(thi)003:1851: bro 'di pha brgyud dpa' bo bro //
NK040(thi)003:1852: pha brgyud dpa' bo'i bro brdung pas //
NK040(thi)003:1853: phyi stong nyid ngang du sangs se sang //
NK040(thi)003:1854: bar mnyam nyid ngang du pri li li //
NK040(thi)003:1855: nang ye shes ngang du ya la la //
NK040(thi)003:1856: gdon 'dre bgegs mgo la chem se chem //
NK040(thi)003:1858: bro 'di gang dang bro 'di ma brgyud mkha' ma
NK040(thi)003:1859: brgyud mkha' phyi stong nyid bar mnyam nang ye shes
NK040(thi)003:1861: bro 'di bro 'di sangs rgyas mkha' sangs rgyas mkha'
NK040(thi)003:1862: phyi stong bar mnyam nang ye shes gdon 'dre bgegs
NK040(thi)003:1863: mgo la h'u / bro 'di bro 'di mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i bro //
NK040(thi)003:1864: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i phyi stong bar mnyam nang ye shes gdon 'dre bgegs bsngo ba smon lam gdab /
NK040(thi)003:1865: tshogs mchod la 'bad pa gal che /
NK040(thi)003:1866: 'di rnams gcig brgyud yin pas kun la gsang /
NK040(thi)003:1867: ma cig gis sras la gdams pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:1868: gcig brgyud min pa kun la mi spel ba'i bka' rgya dam pa yod /
NK040(thi)003:1869: bkra shis bde legs byang chub don du bsngo /
NK040(thi)003:1870: shing mi bzhi'i khong par sha mgo can bzhi /
NK040(thi)003:1872: gnyan sa spo dus khyer rgyu gcig /
NK040(thi)003:1873: nyin dza stag ling gang bdes bris la sgro bar bsogs /
NK040(thi)003:1874: khug rtag ma byung bar du dgug gzhug ci tshar bya /
NK040(thi)003:1875: khug rtags byung nas bsad las bya /
NK040(thi)003:1876: gsod rtags tshar tshad la sogs ma thon bar du nan tan byas la gtad /
NK040(thi)003:1877: tshar nas sbyin bsreg blug la spo ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:1878: rang gi zhabs su lcags kyis khong sgrom sgo med
NK040(thi)003:1879: kyi nang du las kyi gshin rje kha gdangs ba'i
NK040(thi)003:1880: nang du rang nyid khros ma nag mo zhabs gnyis
NK040(thi)003:1881: gnam lcags kyi phur pa dmar zang nge bas 'dor
NK040(thi)003:1882: res byas pas / gshin rje'i kha nang du bcug la bsad pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:1883: gri sri'i rnam shes mi spang /
NK040(thi)003:1884: yang dur gcod bsdus pa byed na /
NK040(thi)003:1885: dur de gzhal yas khang pa gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa gcig tu bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1886: de'i nang du pam las pad+ma ram las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gcig tu bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1887: de'i yid du ma ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK040(thi)003:1888: kha nas ye shes kyi me 'bar ba gcig tu bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1889: gzhal yas khang pa'i steng du bdag nyid yum chen
NK040(thi)003:1890: mo khros ma nag mo gzi brjid dang ldan pa
NK040(thi)003:1891: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK040(thi)003:1892: mche ba bzhi gtsig pa g.yas gri gug g.yon thod khrag bsnam pa gcig bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1893: de'i thugs kha nas mkha' 'gro ma lag na gri gug can /
NK040(thi)003:1896: zhags pa thogs pa grangs med pa khri phrag stong phrag spros pas /
NK040(thi)003:1897: za 'dre shig shed dri za dang bcas pa phyogs
NK040(thi)003:1898: bzhi mtshams brgyad dang bcas steng 'og thams cad nas
NK040(thi)003:1900: ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma kha nas me 'bar ba /
NK040(thi)003:1901: de'i me lce kha nas sbrang bu song ba bzhin bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1902: yum chen mo'i phyag g.yas na mi lpags kyi g.yang gzhi dmar thing nge ba gcig bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:1903: de g.yug pas bdag dang yon bdag gi tshe la brku ba srog la 'jab pa /
NK040(thi)003:1904: gdon bgegs kyi rigs su gyur pa /
NK040(thi)003:1905: za 'dre shi gshed dang bcas byad ma lha srung
NK040(thi)003:1906: dang bcas pa btum nas yar sum cu rtsa gsum
NK040(thi)003:1908: mar dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi la gcar gyis brtab nas sang bas /
NK040(thi)003:1909: thal ba rdul phran bzhin du brlag par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:1910: g.yon na gnam lcags kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa gcig bsnam nas /
NK040(thi)003:1911: gdon bgegs kyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad mdun du bkug la /
NK040(thi)003:1912: rdo rje rgyab pas thal ba rdul phran bzhin du
NK040(thi)003:1913: brlag cing sgro me la bsreg pa bzhin bsam mo
NK040(thi)003:1914: // stong pa nyid kyi ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:1915: dmigs pa de gsum la yang grangs med byed /
NK040(thi)003:1920: gri 'dul ba'i gdam pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:1923: gang zhig 'gro ba'i don byed cing //
NK040(thi)003:1924: sems can rnams la phan bdag phyir //
NK040(thi)003:1925: char dbab gdams pa 'di ltar bya //
NK040(thi)003:1926: matsho'am chu mig mnyan sa ru //
NK040(thi)003:1927: gsang nas rang nyid 'gro bar bya //
NK040(thi)003:1928: phyogs kyi phye phud 'o phud bsog /
NK040(thi)003:1929: gang 'tshogs chu gtor rgya chen bya //
NK040(thi)003:1931: spyir yang khams gsum sems can dang //
NK040(thi)003:1932: sgos yul phyogs 'di yi sems can rnams //
NK040(thi)003:1933: mu ges gdung bas snying re rje //
NK040(thi)003:1934: bdag gi lus srog 'di dag ni //
NK040(thi)003:1935: lha klu rnams la sbyin par btang //
NK040(thi)003:1936: de'i dngos grub bdag la ni //
NK040(thi)003:1937: yul phyogs 'di ru char phab nas //
NK040(thi)003:1938: bdud rtsi char chen phab par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1939: lus mchod brgya stong grangs med phul //
NK040(thi)003:1940: bar bar spros bral ngang la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:1941: char pa 'bebs gyur the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:1942: gal te zhag gsum lnga la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:1943: bsdad kyang char pa med gyur na //
NK040(thi)003:1944: gnad kyi gdams pa 'di ltar bya //
NK040(thi)003:1945: rang nyid gcer bu phata kyi gdab //
NK040(thi)003:1946: rig pa ngar bskyed brtul bshug bya //
NK040(thi)003:1947: gdeng thob rnal 'byor gang zhig gis //
NK040(thi)003:1948: khyung gi ting 'dzin bzung byas la //
NK040(thi)003:1949: klu dang sa bdag thams cad ni //
NK040(thi)003:1950: 'dar zhing char pa phab par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:1951: rig pa ngar bskyed phata kyi gdab //
NK040(thi)003:1952: yang na rdzas sbyor ar la gtad //
NK040(thi)003:1953: char phob rjod cing mchong khrab bya //
NK040(thi)003:1954: des ni mi pheb mi srid do //
NK040(thi)003:1955: pheb nas klu gnyan yul bdag la //
NK040(thi)003:1956: mchod pa bya zhing lus mchod do //
NK040(thi)003:1957: byams pa'i sems ni bsgom par bya //
NK040(thi)003:1958: char 'beb zhal gdam bdud rtsi yin /
NK040(thi)003:1960: nad pa tshab chen dang gnyan thog tu 'gro ma bde ba yin na /
NK040(thi)003:1961: rgyal po gnad gcod ltar byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:1962: grogs mched gcig rje btsun ma dmar mo'i nga rgyal dang ldan nas /
NK040(thi)003:1963: gnyan sa'i sa rdo bum gter gyi tshul du bzung la /
NK040(thi)003:1964: sa phyogs de'i lha 'dre bstim nas /
NK040(thi)003:1966: dbang sdud zil non tshogs 'gyed rjes chog la sogs nyams len gzhung ltar bya /
NK040(thi)003:1967: chod pa dang rdo gter phal 'phangs /
NK040(thi)003:1969: de ltar brgya rtsa brgyad bcad pas chog /
NK040(thi)003:1971: zil non la sogs lam gyi byed las spyi dang mthun pa rdzogs nas /
NK040(thi)003:1972: khyad par du gnas kyi byed las kyi skabs su /
NK040(thi)003:1974: zhabs su lcags mkhar bsgom pa'i skabs su phata kyis rang nyid khros ma nag mo'i thugs ka nas /
NK040(thi)003:1975: gnam lcags kyis tho lum chen po gcig gis khyim
NK040(thi)003:1976: de na gnas pa'i lha 'dre gnas khang thams cad
NK040(thi)003:1978: lha 'dre kho rang gis gnas khang 'dre dang bcas
NK040(thi)003:1979: pa rang gi zhabs kyi lcags khang gi nang du
NK040(thi)003:1980: tshud par bsgom / de nas gtan bting ba la sogs nyams len bcun lugs spyi dang mthun /
NK040(thi)003:1981: mthar gnyan sa chod pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:1982: ru ba yin na skya ba dang sprad la /
NK040(thi)003:1983: rjes chog byed lugs spyi dang mthun /
NK040(thi)003:1984: khang pa yin na rjes chog tshar nas /
NK040(thi)003:1985: phata brjod cing lha 'dre thams cad so sor gshegs par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:1986: khang pa gzhal yas khang byin gyis brlab la rab gnas bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:1988: ro gcod dmigs pa dril ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:1989: rang nyid khros mas ro ni rdo rje yis //
NK040(thi)003:1992: de nas rum la nyams len skyongs //
NK040(thi)003:1993: mo ri rang ro gcig tu bsre //
NK040(thi)003:1994: phata kyi rig pa gter du sba //
NK040(thi)003:1995: lha 'dre yong la tshims par sbyin //
NK040(thi)003:1999: stong nyid rig pa'i rtsal sbyangs bya //
NK040(thi)003:2001: bem ro ma'i nyams len ni /
NK040(thi)003:2002: spyi bor ma cig lab sgron bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:2003: rang gi rnam par shes pa de thig le dkar
NK040(thi)003:2004: la dmar ba bya ma gsar gyi sgo nga tsam
NK040(thi)003:2006: phata byas pa dang snying kha nas spyi bor bud sde /
NK040(thi)003:2007: ma cig gi thugs kar thim nas ma cig dang
NK040(thi)003:2008: bcas pa nam mkhar 'ja' 'od du yal bar bsam
NK040(thi)003:2009: / lus po 'gyel ba las rang gdon dang gnyan
NK040(thi)003:2010: sa'i gdon gyi gtso byas snang srid kyi lha 'dre
NK040(thi)003:2011: rnams kyis gtor ma bya khyis btog pa ltar khyer
NK040(thi)003:2012: / bar bsam zhing / ngag tu gzhan 'phrul dbang
NK040(thi)003:2013: byed man chad sa 'og sa steng yan chad bgegs
NK040(thi)003:2014: rigs stong phrag brgyad cu ma lus pa rnams kyis
NK040(thi)003:2015: / bar bsam zhing / / bdag gis lus phyi sha gzugs drug /
NK040(thi)003:2022: dbang po rnam pa lnga dang don snying /
NK040(thi)003:2025: khyed rnams la bdag gi lan chags 'khor /
NK040(thi)003:2029: bde ba dang ldan pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:2031: de ltar brgya 'am stong la sogs grangs ci mang du bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2032: thugs rje chen po'i zhi gcod nyams su len par 'dod pas /
NK040(thi)003:2034: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa song nas /
NK040(thi)003:2035: skad cig gis gdan drang tha dad med par /
NK040(thi)003:2037: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis steng du /
NK040(thi)003:2038: rang gis sems gyi ngo bo yi ge h+r+aihdakara po tsheg drag dang bcas pa /
NK040(thi)003:2039: de las 'od 'phros sems can gyi don byas nas /
NK040(thi)003:2041: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK040(thi)003:2042: rang nyid thugs rje chen po sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK040(thi)003:2043: g.yas pas bdag la gnod par byed pa'i bgegs dang /
NK040(thi)003:2044: gnyan sa la gnas pa'i gzhi bdag gis gtso byas
NK040(thi)003:2045: pa'i sems can thams cad mchod sbyin 'deg pa'i phyag
NK040(thi)003:2046: rgya mdzad pa / g.yon pas phreng ba dmar po bsnam pa /
NK040(thi)003:2047: ral pa'i thor tshug gyen du bcing pa la /
NK040(thi)003:2048: dar dang rin chen sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:2049: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)003:2050: de'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du
NK040(thi)003:2051: yi ge h+r+aihdakara po de'i mthar yi ge drug pas
NK040(thi)003:2054: bdag la gnod par byed pa'i gdon bgegs 'byung po dang /
NK040(thi)003:2055: gnyan sa la gnas pa'i gzhi bdag gis gtso byas
NK040(thi)003:2056: pa'i snang srid lha 'dre rigs drug gi sems can
NK040(thi)003:2057: thams cad 'od zer gyis bsdus nas /
NK040(thi)003:2058: rang gis phyogs bzhi dang nye 'khor du yod par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:2059: de nas yi ge drug pa bsgrang pa tsam gyis thugs ka'i h+r+aihdang sngags phreng las /
NK040(thi)003:2060: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi kha dog dkar po byung nas /
NK040(thi)003:2061: phyag g.yas pa'i 'dzub mo lnga'i kha nas dkar kyi li li babs nas /
NK040(thi)003:2062: bdag la gnod byed 'byung po gdon bgegs dang /
NK040(thi)003:2063: gnyan sa la gnas pa'i gzhi bdag dang /
NK040(thi)003:2064: sems can thams cad kyis mthong bas /
NK040(thi)003:2065: sdang sems dang sdug sems zhi nas /
NK040(thi)003:2066: thugs rje chen po'i skur gyur par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:2067: ma thob pa thams cad kyi bdud rtsi lhag ma la longs spyod nas /
NK040(thi)003:2068: thams cad yi ge drug pa mgrin gcig tu 'don par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:2069: de nas rang nyid la sku drin che zer bstod nas /
NK040(thi)003:2071: la las bskor ba byed par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2072: thun 'jog pa'i dus su 'das ma 'ongs da ltar nas ba yid la mi byar /
NK040(thi)003:2073: gnas lugs phyag rgya chen po'i ngang la 'jog go //
NK040(thi)003:2074: de'i rjes su bdag gi lus sbyin du btang ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba 'dis /
NK040(thi)003:2075: 'gro ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams
NK040(thi)003:2076: cad spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang sku mnyam par
NK040(thi)003:2077: gyur cig / gsungs mnyam par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:2079: yon tan phrin las dang mnyam par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:2080: mdzad pa mnyam par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:2082: dam chos bdud kyi gcod yul 'di /
NK040(thi)003:2083: ma cig lab kyi sgron mas zangs ri mkhar dmar du thod smyon bsam 'grub la rgyud do //
NK040(thi)003:2084: de nas rim par brgyud nas bdag la'o //
NK040(thi)003:2085: gnyan sar jag rkun dog na /
NK040(thi)003:2086: jag gcod mgo 'phyang ma byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:2087: gong gis gnas kyi bye brag lcags khang bsgom pa'i dus su /
NK040(thi)003:2088: phata brjod pa tsam gyis lcags khang gis kha na
NK040(thi)003:2089: lcags sreg gi dra ba sa bkab pa'i d+r+wa mig
NK040(thi)003:2090: tu r+n+ri mgo thur du bstan pa grangs med bsam
NK040(thi)003:2091: / r+n+ri yongs gyur pa las jag rkun gang yin
NK040(thi)003:2092: pa mgo thur du bstan nas d+r+wa mig tu rkang
NK040(thi)003:2093: bol 'thog nas lus gdon dang gnas gdon gnyis kyi
NK040(thi)003:2095: de la jag rkun bstim zhing skabs skabs su 'gugs 'dren ci nus bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2096: de yan chad kyi gzer bu'i gdams pa song /
NK040(thi)003:2097: spyi don gsum pa spyi ching gal mdo'i rims pa la bco lnga ste /
NK040(thi)003:2098: spra btags legs nyes kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2100: slong tshad tshar tshad kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2104: bdud bzhi gegs sel gyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2106: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i mngon rtogs kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2107: las bzhi'i sbyin sreg gis ching /
NK040(thi)003:2108: dbang bskur chos sgoo 'byed pa'i ching /
NK040(thi)003:2109: ngo sprod nam mkha' sgo 'byed kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2110: lhan thabs gnad kyi phreng pa'i ching /
NK040(thi)003:2112: gcod khrid gsal sgron gyi ching ngo //
NK040(thi)003:2113: dang po spra rtags legs nyes kyi ching ni /
NK040(thi)003:2115: stobs dang ldan pa'i skyes bu yis //
NK040(thi)003:2116: gzhan phan dmigs pa skyong ba ni //
NK040(thi)003:2117: phan dang mi phan brtag pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2118: nad gzhi che chung legs nyes dang //
NK040(thi)003:2119: gdon rigs gang yin dbye ba ni //
NK040(thi)003:2120: spra ltas brtag cing spang len byed //
NK040(thi)003:2121: 'di la man ngag gsum yin te //
NK040(thi)003:2123: las dang legs nyes rtags thabs dang //
NK040(thi)003:2124: spang len thabs dang bshan 'byed thabs //
NK040(thi)003:2125: nad pa dag gis drod tshad rtags //
NK040(thi)003:2126: skyabs 'gro gsol ba rim bzhin btab //
NK040(thi)003:2127: rang rig h+r+aihls rdo rje rnal 'byor ma //
NK040(thi)003:2128: dmar mo gri gug thod khrag 'dzin //
NK040(thi)003:2129: gang yin nad pa tshogs su bsgral //
NK040(thi)003:2130: rig pa rang gi thugs kar bstim //
NK040(thi)003:2131: sha khrag longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK040(thi)003:2132: mgron la yang yang bkye ba yis //
NK040(thi)003:2134: dam la btag cing gnyis med sgom //
NK040(thi)003:2135: de nas rang rigs mkha' 'gro mas //
NK040(thi)003:2136: g.yas pas lcags kyu kha brgyad kyis //
NK040(thi)003:2137: gnod byed gang yin snying nas bzung //
NK040(thi)003:2138: rang dbang med par srog nas drangs //
NK040(thi)003:2139: skad ngan tse re 'don nas ni //
NK040(thi)003:2140: skrags sngangs 'dar zhing srog snying phul //
NK040(thi)003:2141: de nas thun du bcad cing mdun du sgom //
NK040(thi)003:2142: de nas seng ge'i nyal stabs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:2144: bdag gis rig pa yi ge +aah nad pa'i nang du yod par bsam //
NK040(thi)003:2145: de la rig shes gtad la nyal //
NK040(thi)003:2146: gnyis pa rmi lam yul yin pas //
NK040(thi)003:2147: gdon rnams phan dang mi phan gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:2148: dang po gdon ngos bzung ba ni //
NK040(thi)003:2149: zhang blon mi dpon ban+de dang //
NK040(thi)003:2150: sprel dang chu chen me 'bar dang //
NK040(thi)003:2151: rta khyi lha khang bu chung rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2152: gnod skyel 'dzing dang rgol la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:2154: grong ral ra khyi phag bud med //
NK040(thi)003:2155: bya nag rlung nag khyi mo nag /
NK040(thi)003:2156: mdzo mo rtol mo gang ral dang //
NK040(thi)003:2157: sbra gur nil seng mo gdon sman //
NK040(thi)003:2158: sbal sbrul nya lcong bskyed shing chu //
NK040(thi)003:2159: gzhon nu blu brid ba glang lug /
NK040(thi)003:2160: mdze sprang rigs ni klu yin no //
NK040(thi)003:2161: g.yag dang mi nag khyi nag dang //
NK040(thi)003:2162: rta dang mun nag sa sub 'thib //
NK040(thi)003:2163: de rnams bdud du shes par bya //
NK040(thi)003:2164: thog ser rlung sub sngags pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2165: mgar dang tsh+wa tsh+wa gza' gdon yin //
NK040(thi)003:2166: phug ron mi nag lkug pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2167: mun rub lug khyu btsud rmis na //
NK040(thi)003:2168: dmu'i rigs su shes pa bya //
NK040(thi)003:2169: rta pa rlung 'tshub mi dmar dang //
NK040(thi)003:2170: spyang khu khyi dmar rmis na btsan //
NK040(thi)003:2171: ban bon zhub can chas brgyan can //
NK040(thi)003:2172: gzhi ma gnyan gyi cho 'phrul yin //
NK040(thi)003:2173: mi rgan ra thod bya pho dang //
NK040(thi)003:2174: bu tsa ra rlag the'u rang yin //
NK040(thi)003:2175: gsum pa phan dang mi phan ni //
NK040(thi)003:2176: gong du rmis pa de rnams kyis //
NK040(thi)003:2177: gus pa phul dang dga' tshig bzlo //
NK040(thi)003:2178: dbang du 'dus pas sos par nges //
NK040(thi)003:2179: kha zas ster dang las grogs byed //
NK040(thi)003:2180: dam la thog pas sos par nges //
NK040(thi)003:2181: lhung dang bros dang brdung btag dang //
NK040(thi)003:2182: bsad bcad brdul du brlag pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2183: bskyed shing bcad dang chu skam dang //
NK040(thi)003:2184: lha khang 'der so zhig dang bsgyel //
NK040(thi)003:2185: khyi nag bskor dang bud med du //
NK040(thi)003:2186: mi dam shi dang nor rdzas bor //
NK040(thi)003:2187: gdon rnams thub par the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:2189: gyod dang kha mchu shag las rgyal //
NK040(thi)003:2190: mkhar len so ma skas la 'dzeg /
NK040(thi)003:2191: gos gyon kha zas yid 'ongs ster //
NK040(thi)003:2192: bor rnyed yi ge bri klog byed //
NK040(thi)003:2193: dar phyar dung 'bud lha cha bskrol //
NK040(thi)003:2194: de rmis bzang rtags nad pa sos //
NK040(thi)003:2195: sems bskyed dag pas phan bdag bya //
NK040(thi)003:2197: gnyis pa de las bzlog pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:2198: zil gyi non dang 'jigs gzugs ston //
NK040(thi)003:2199: yig cha lha skor stor dang rul //
NK040(thi)003:2200: rtsa ba'i slob dpon khros nas bkyon //
NK040(thi)003:2201: ma sring 'dun byas chas ngan ston //
NK040(thi)003:2202: b+ha ga ston dang khros 'thab byed //
NK040(thi)003:2203: rang nyid bcing rtags rmis pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2204: gos ngan go dang thur du song //
NK040(thi)003:2205: tsha rgod byin dang bu ram dang //
NK040(thi)003:2206: de rnams shin tu spang bar rigs //
NK040(thi)003:2207: gcan spyang rgol dang 'thab pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2209: 'dam dang mi gtsang gos ngan rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2210: nad gzhi che ste thub par 'ongs //
NK040(thi)003:2211: gzhan yang rmi lam bzang ba 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:2212: lha cha bor dang yig cha stor //
NK040(thi)003:2213: shin tu ngan pas spangs bar bya //
NK040(thi)003:2214: rang nyid bcing rtags rmis pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:2215: ngan pa yang dag yin pa des //
NK040(thi)003:2216: nad pa mi sos rang yang brlag /
NK040(thi)003:2217: gzhan yang rmi lam ci ngan yang //
NK040(thi)003:2218: lha cha dkrol dang stor rnyed dang //
NK040(thi)003:2219: yid dga' ma sring chas bzang na //
NK040(thi)003:2220: dngos grub yin te bzang por 'ong //
NK040(thi)003:2221: rmi lam bzang ngan bsre ba ni //
NK040(thi)003:2222: nyams tshad yin pas dmigs pas gzir //
NK040(thi)003:2223: de ltar legs rtags spang blang bya //
NK040(thi)003:2226: gnyis pa spyod lam rnam bzhi la gnyis kyi dang po /
NK040(thi)003:2229: phata gnyis byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:2230: gcig gis ma cig lab sgron gyis skyil krung thog tu rang gis mgo sngas par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:2231: gcig gis rang gis rnam par shes pa ma lab sgron gyi thugs kar thim par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2233: yang phata gsum byas pa tsam gyis gcig gis ma cig gis steng na /
NK040(thi)003:2234: gser gyi khri thog na sh+aakya thub pa la bskal
NK040(thi)003:2235: bzang gis sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis kyis bskor nas
NK040(thi)003:2236: bzhugs pa des / gnas gdon lus gdon la sogs
NK040(thi)003:2237: bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad la chos bshad par
NK040(thi)003:2238: bzhugs pa des / sgoms / de ni steng lha tshogs kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2239: yang phata gcig gis rang gis bem po de /
NK040(thi)003:2240: blos khyab tshad gcig tu gyur par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2241: de nas bar lus kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:2242: gcig gis zhabs lcags mkhar nang gis gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis dang /
NK040(thi)003:2243: sa phyogs der gnas pa'i lha 'dre thams cad kheb nas gar yang 'gro dbang med par bsam /
NK040(thi)003:2244: des ni mgo bskor mi 'ongs ba'i gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:2245: nyil chung 'phar non gyi dmigs pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2246: de ni 'og gdon tshogs kyis chings /
NK040(thi)003:2247: des nyal ba'i rnal 'byor gyi ching bzhi song nas /
NK040(thi)003:2249: bems ro ma byed pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2250: phata gnyis byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:2251: gcig gis rnam shes spyi gtsug tu lab sgron gyi thugs kar thim par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2252: gcig gis rang gi bem po 'gyel ba de /
NK040(thi)003:2253: lha 'dre rnams kyis hab thob byed par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2254: spyod lam rnam bzhi gang byed kyang de ltar bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:2255: spyi gtsug tu ma gcig dang 'du 'bral med par par bsgom mdzod dang /
NK040(thi)003:2256: gcod pa ci ltar ngan yang 'pho ba mi dgos gsungs /
NK040(thi)003:2257: yang langs nas 'gro dus gom pa spo ba dang sprad la /
NK040(thi)003:2258: phata gcig byas pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:2259: mal du sh+aakya thub pa gong bzhin bzhugs nas chos gsungs bar bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2260: tshur pheb tsa dzahmh'u bam hohbyasa pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:2261: sh+aakya thub pa gtso 'khor rang gi thugs kar thim par bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:2262: de ni rnal 'byor pa rang gi gnas srung gis dmigs pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2263: nad pa'i gnas srung gis dmigs pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:2264: nad pa rang langs nas 'gro ba'i mal du ro
NK040(thi)003:2265: che la bam pa rul ba gcig gis gnyan sa
NK040(thi)003:2267: de ni nad pa rang gis byed las so //
NK040(thi)003:2268: des gnyis pa spyod lam rnam bzhi song /
NK040(thi)003:2269: gsum pa slong tshad tshar tshad kyi ching la lnga ste /
NK040(thi)003:2272: chod tshad nad gdon sel thabs gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:2273: tshar tshad dngos grub 'byung dang gsum //
NK040(thi)003:2274: nad can dang ni nad med la //
NK040(thi)003:2275: so sor 'ong ba stan dang bzhi //
NK040(thi)003:2277: so sor shan 'byed shes dang lnga //
NK040(thi)003:2278: dang po slong tshad cho 'phrul la //
NK040(thi)003:2279: phyi ni lha 'dre'i slong tshad dang //
NK040(thi)003:2280: nang du na tsha'i slong tshad dang //
NK040(thi)003:2281: gsang ba nyon mongs slong tshad dang //
NK040(thi)003:2282: nad pa byin chen slong tshad dang //
NK040(thi)003:2283: nad med rnal 'byor slong tshad dang //
NK040(thi)003:2284: dang po lha 'dre'i slong tshad la //
NK040(thi)003:2285: mngon sum gzi byin rmi lam sum //
NK040(thi)003:2286: dang po mngon sum slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2287: gnyan sa de ru phyin pa'i tshe //
NK040(thi)003:2288: ma nyes kha yog phog pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2290: pha rol gzhan gyi rang nyid la //
NK040(thi)003:2291: brdung dang bkyig dang sha breg dang //
NK040(thi)003:2292: mi bsnyen sgrog cing gsod grab byed //
NK040(thi)003:2294: sngar mthun pa'i slob dpon dang //
NK040(thi)003:2295: mched grogs yon mchod gnyen 'brel rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2296: bye dang bral dang 'gras pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2298: sa g.yos chom chag 'ur sgra dang //
NK040(thi)003:2299: ming nas bzung zhing 'bod pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2300: mi sdug gzugs ston rna lcags 'debs //
NK040(thi)003:2302: ri 'phen nyi zla brdeg pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2304: nyin par mun rug zla ba shar //
NK040(thi)003:2305: mgo bcad snying phyung khyer la sogs //
NK040(thi)003:2307: gnyis pa gzi byin slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2308: gnyan sar phyin nas ba spu g.yo //
NK040(thi)003:2310: sngang ba la sogs cir yang 'byung //
NK040(thi)003:2311: gsum pa rmi lam slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2312: mes tshig chus khyer rbab 'dril dang //
NK040(thi)003:2313: ri dwags gtso bo zhang blon dang //
NK040(thi)003:2314: skya 'khal skya mi ngo mi shes //
NK040(thi)003:2315: khrab can ra lug ba glang dang //
NK040(thi)003:2316: bya dang gcan gzan la sogs dang //
NK040(thi)003:2317: gong du bshad pa'i cho 'phrul rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2319: de gsum phyi yi slong tshad yin //
NK040(thi)003:2320: gnyis pa nang gi slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2321: spyi bo'i gtsug nas rkang mthil bar //
NK040(thi)003:2322: skrang 'bur shu ba thar thor dang //
NK040(thi)003:2323: gnyan slog gag pa 'bras rim dang //
NK040(thi)003:2324: glang shu bal ldag 'brum bu dang //
NK040(thi)003:2325: 'khru dang skyug pa la sogs dang //
NK040(thi)003:2326: gzhan yang na tsha zug gzer che //
NK040(thi)003:2327: rkyen bag tsam la skrag sngang 'byung //
NK040(thi)003:2328: de rnams nang gi slong tshad do //
NK040(thi)003:2329: gsum pa gsang ba'i slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2331: mi dga' kun la tshig pa za //
NK040(thi)003:2332: bsgom mi 'dod dang blo nor dang //
NK040(thi)003:2333: don med khro tshig za ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2336: lcib snying 'dod dang sa phyogs dang //
NK040(thi)003:2338: rgod 'phro bying dang rmug pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2340: bza' btung yid mi 'ong pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2341: the tshom za dang gcod la 'gyod //
NK040(thi)003:2342: nyin mtshan phul dus med pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2344: skad 'don mi nus mal mi bde //
NK040(thi)003:2345: mdor na yid kyi khong 'khrig mang //
NK040(thi)003:2346: rnam rtog slong ba'i tshad yin no //
NK040(thi)003:2347: bzhi pa nad pa'i slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2348: gong gi cho 'phrul de rnams dang //
NK040(thi)003:2349: khyad par nad pa'i rmi lam sngar bas 'khrug /
NK040(thi)003:2350: gcod pas khyim dang rim gro sman dpyad dga' //
NK040(thi)003:2351: bsam pa'i 'dun pa skyo ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2352: gnyan sa de ru phyin pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2353: na tsha che zhing phyir thu bsam //
NK040(thi)003:2354: gzhan yang rmi lam nyams snang du //
NK040(thi)003:2356: slong chen yin pas ngo mtshar che //
NK040(thi)003:2357: gdengs dang ldan pas nyams su blangs //
NK040(thi)003:2358: bla ma'i gdam ngag gcun pa gces //
NK040(thi)003:2359: lnga pa rnal 'byor slong tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2360: gang gi de rnams 'ong steng du //
NK040(thi)003:2361: khyad par bud med khye'u chung gis //
NK040(thi)003:2362: bslu zhing dngos su brdeg pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2363: yul du ma 'dug zer ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2365: de ni slong ba'i tshad yin te //
NK040(thi)003:2366: dga' dang mi dga' zhe 'dod bral //
NK040(thi)003:2367: nyams len la ni 'bad par bya //
NK040(thi)003:2368: gnyis pa chod tshad la yang gsum //
NK040(thi)003:2369: nad can dang ni nad med gnyis //
NK040(thi)003:2370: de la phyi nang gsang ba gsum //
NK040(thi)003:2371: dang po nad can de la ni //
NK040(thi)003:2372: ru ba skyas pa bcag pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2373: dmag gzing 'ong dang bros zhog dang //
NK040(thi)003:2374: sked shing chags dang chu mig skams //
NK040(thi)003:2375: bcing thag bcad dang dngos su thar //
NK040(thi)003:2376: bud med ngu dang shi dang bsreg /
NK040(thi)003:2377: sems can btag zin grol ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2378: zas nor mi la shor ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2379: gos phud gcer bu khrus byed rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2380: nad pa dag gis chod tshul yin //
NK040(thi)003:2381: gnyis pa nad med chod tshul ni //
NK040(thi)003:2382: 'thab pa rdum byas pho brang brtan pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2383: bsnyen bkur zhabs rtogs byed pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2384: rta nor ba glang 'bul ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2385: shing thog ja chang lo yag rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2386: rnal 'byor pa yis chod tshad yin //
NK040(thi)003:2387: dang po phyi yi chod tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2389: 'thab pa rdum pa byed pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2390: glo snying 'phrog thal gtad pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2391: sha sgo ri la gram pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2392: ngo mi shes pa'i bud med dang //
NK040(thi)003:2393: zhang blon stag shar gang 'tshogs kyis //
NK040(thi)003:2394: phyag dang zhabs gtog byed pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2397: dar zab gser dngul rta lug 'bru //
NK040(thi)003:2399: srog snying phul dang chos zhus dang //
NK040(thi)003:2400: byin rlabs skyabs 'gro sems bskyed zhu //
NK040(thi)003:2401: de rnams gnyan sa'i chod tshad yin //
NK040(thi)003:2402: gnyis pa nang gi chos tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2403: nang na na nad pa sos pa'i chod tshad tsha sngar bas chung ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2404: lus po yang dang za ma 'dod //
NK040(thi)003:2405: rnag khrag chu ser 'dzag pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2406: skyug sbyong la sogs byed pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2407: khang gsar brdung dang bang gsar brtsigs //
NK040(thi)003:2408: nag po'i khung du 'dzul nas thar //
NK040(thi)003:2409: sho gru rtsod pa rgyal ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2410: khral dang bu lon mjal ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2411: lus kyi sro shig 'phyag pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2412: gos hrul phud dang snyi phud phyag /
NK040(thi)003:2413: mda' mdung rno mtshon bzung ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2415: dmag mi tshong pa ban bon song ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2416: lha khang 'gyel dang sder so zhig /
NK040(thi)003:2417: dri chen dri chu 'dor ba rmis //
NK040(thi)003:2418: yid ni stong zhing dga' la bde //
NK040(thi)003:2419: lus las sbal sbrul lcong mo dang //
NK040(thi)003:2420: sdom sdig grog sbur 'bu srin dang //
NK040(thi)003:2421: bu chung spre'u li li bud pa rmis //
NK040(thi)003:2422: ngo shes sems can shi sreg dang //
NK040(thi)003:2423: sha nye shi dang nor shor dang //
NK040(thi)003:2424: chu skam shing skam rir me shor //
NK040(thi)003:2425: nyi zla shar dang skas la 'dzegs //
NK040(thi)003:2426: gangs dkar rtser phyin nam mkha' g.ya' dag dang //
NK040(thi)003:2427: shel dang nor bu bum gter rnyed //
NK040(thi)003:2428: gos gsar gon dang mkhar lan tshar //
NK040(thi)003:2429: nam langs khrus byas gyen la 'gro //
NK040(thi)003:2430: mchod rten bskor byed mkha' la 'phur //
NK040(thi)003:2431: ngo tsha med par gcer bur rgyug /
NK040(thi)003:2432: me tog dkar ser thu ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2433: dar phyar lha cha dkrol brdung rmis //
NK040(thi)003:2434: nad gdon dag gis chod tshad yin //
NK040(thi)003:2435: gsum pa gsang ba'i chod tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2436: yid dga' bde zhing spro ba dang //
NK040(thi)003:2437: dad pa skye zhing ting 'dzin gsal //
NK040(thi)003:2438: na tsha chung zhing nges shes skye //
NK040(thi)003:2439: de ni gsang ba'i chod tshad do //
NK040(thi)003:2440: spyi don gsum pa tshar tshad bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:2441: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba ste //
NK040(thi)003:2442: dang po phyi yi tshar tshad bstan pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:2443: rmi lam zang zing 'jam pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2444: dbang zhu phyag dang bskor byed dang //
NK040(thi)003:2445: chos zhu sdom len zhabs tog rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2446: phyi yi lha 'dre'i tshar tshad yin //
NK040(thi)003:2447: nad zhi lus bde sems gsal la //
NK040(thi)003:2448: sha nye shi sreg thal ba rlung khyer dang //
NK040(thi)003:2449: sbal sbrul 'bu srin tshig skam dang //
NK040(thi)003:2450: grong zhig gza' bsreg nor shor dang //
NK040(thi)003:2451: ru skyas zag 'dor khrus byas khong khrag bshad //
NK040(thi)003:2452: nad gdon nang gi tshar tshad do //
NK040(thi)003:2453: gsang ba dag gi tshar tshad ni //
NK040(thi)003:2454: srog snying phul la dam bca' dang //
NK040(thi)003:2455: dgongs pa gdengs ldan nyams nga med //
NK040(thi)003:2456: lha 'dre nye ring mi rtsi bar //
NK040(thi)003:2457: mnyam pa'i ngang du gnas pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2458: rnam par rtog pa mi skye zhing //
NK040(thi)003:2459: stong gsal dgongs pa rtsis zin dang //
NK040(thi)003:2460: 'dre yang rang gi sems su shes //
NK040(thi)003:2461: na tsha chos nyid ngang du dag /
NK040(thi)003:2463: rigs par ngar ldan gsal le ba //
NK040(thi)003:2464: bde gsal ngang du hrig ge ba //
NK040(thi)003:2465: mnyam bzhag ngang du skad de ba //
NK040(thi)003:2466: mtshan bcas kyi dmigs pa mi 'dzin pa //
NK040(thi)003:2467: mtshan med ngang du mnyam gnas na //
NK040(thi)003:2468: gsang ba dag gis tshar tshad do //
NK040(thi)003:2469: spyir phyi yi tshar tshad snyad can ni //
NK040(thi)003:2470: rdzas dang bza' btung thams cad la //
NK040(thi)003:2471: snyad can byung na ma chod do //
NK040(thi)003:2472: snyad med byung na chod pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:2473: nang gi tshar tshad snyad can ni //
NK040(thi)003:2474: tshar tshad byung yang yid ma bde na ma chod //
NK040(thi)003:2475: tshar tshad brda' tsam byung nas yid bde na chod //
NK040(thi)003:2476: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub de ru rdzogs //
NK040(thi)003:2477: gdengs ldan gyi rnal 'byor yin par gsungs //
NK040(thi)003:2478: de ltar drod tshad dang ldan par byed la //
NK040(thi)003:2479: dang po phyi nang gsang gsum dang ma ldan na //
NK040(thi)003:2480: gnyan sar bsdad pa'i don mi 'byung //
NK040(thi)003:2481: de phyir dang po slong ba'i tshad gsum dang ldan pa'i dus //
NK040(thi)003:2482: gdengs ldan mthar skyol nyams su blang //
NK040(thi)003:2483: gnyis pa chod pa'i tshad dang ma ldan na //
NK040(thi)003:2485: chod tshad gsum dang ldan pas nyams su blangs //
NK040(thi)003:2486: de ni tshar tshad gsum dang ma ldan na //
NK040(thi)003:2487: me thog skye 'phro lus pa dang //
NK040(thi)003:2489: mchog thun dngos grub mi 'byung bas //
NK040(thi)003:2490: tshad dang ldan pas nyams su lang //
NK040(thi)003:2491: yang gnyan sa'i 'dre che chung gi cha shas /
NK040(thi)003:2492: ting nge 'dzin khul ma khul dang /
NK040(thi)003:2493: dgongs pa zil gyi gnon ma non dang /
NK040(thi)003:2494: sngar gyis 'khreb ma 'khreb kyis khyad par dang /
NK040(thi)003:2495: rang gi nad gdon gyi sgrib pa che chung gi cha shas dang /
NK040(thi)003:2496: drod tshad kyang snga phyi dang dngos grub che chung dang /
NK040(thi)003:2497: nad gdon che chung gi khyad par 'byung ste /
NK040(thi)003:2498: la las nub gcig la slong tshad /
NK040(thi)003:2500: tshar tshad kun rdzogs pa yong yod /
NK040(thi)003:2501: nub mo gsum la rdzogs pa yang yod /
NK040(thi)003:2502: nyi shu tshun chad nas rdzogs pa yang yod /
NK040(thi)003:2504: cho 'phrul dang tshar tshad gang byung yang /
NK040(thi)003:2505: nang nub kyi yid la bzung ba gal che /
NK040(thi)003:2508: bla ma'i zhal gyi gdams pa rnams /
NK040(thi)003:2509: nyams su tshud pa gnad du che'o //
NK040(thi)003:2510: mchod par 'ong na rjes snyog yang yod /
NK040(thi)003:2511: chod nas sdod na nad bsnon pa yang yod /
NK040(thi)003:2512: de phyir drod tshad gal che /
NK040(thi)003:2513: slong tshad gsum dang ma ldan na /
NK040(thi)003:2514: nad pa la nad gdon bag la nyal /
NK040(thi)003:2515: rnal 'byor pa la nyon mongs bag la nyal /
NK040(thi)003:2516: de phyir slong tshad gal che /
NK040(thi)003:2517: chod pa'i tshad dang ma ldan na /
NK040(thi)003:2518: nad pa'i nad mi chod cing /
NK040(thi)003:2519: rnal 'byor pa'i nyon mongs rnam rtog mi chod /
NK040(thi)003:2520: tshar ba'i tshad dang ma ldan na /
NK040(thi)003:2521: nad pa'i nad mi phan rkyen dngos grub tu mi 'char /
NK040(thi)003:2522: rnal 'byor nyams rtogs ye shes su mi slong /
NK040(thi)003:2523: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub mi 'byung /
NK040(thi)003:2525: chod tshad dang tshar tshad la yang cho 'phrul 'dra ba'i tshar tshad dang /
NK040(thi)003:2526: tshar tshad 'dra ba'i cho 'phrul gnyis 'dra min 'byung bas ngos bzung ba gal che /
NK040(thi)003:2527: bla ma'i gdam ngag la bslab par bya /
NK040(thi)003:2528: gnyan sa gcig tu rdzogs pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2529: gnyan sa'i nus pa la rag las pas btang bzhag la mkhas pa gal che ste /
NK040(thi)003:2530: gdam ngag bslab cing nan tan bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2531: dang po slong tshad rmi lam ngan pa la sogs yid la mi 'ong ba sna tshogs 'byung /
NK040(thi)003:2532: bar du non tshad ci yang mi 'byung /
NK040(thi)003:2533: tha ma chod tshad bzang po 'byung /
NK040(thi)003:2534: de ni tshad gsum gyi zhabs bsdu'o //
NK040(thi)003:2535: de ltar tshar tshad ci byung yang chags zhen dang
NK040(thi)003:2536: dga' brod rlom sems gang yang mi byed cing rmi
NK040(thi)003:2537: lam bzhin du shes par bya /
NK040(thi)003:2538: bzhi pa 'dra min shan 'byed kyis ching la drug ste /
NK040(thi)003:2539: dang po gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis kyis shan 'byed cing ngo shes pa ni lus gdon /
NK040(thi)003:2540: ngo ma shes na ni gnas gdon yin /
NK040(thi)003:2541: dang po ngo shes de nas ngo ma shes par gyur na /
NK040(thi)003:2542: gnas gdon lus gdon du bardzusa pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2544: de nas shes na lus gdon gnas gdon du bardzusa pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2545: ngo sbas 'gyur ldog byas na gnas gdon yin /
NK040(thi)003:2546: sngar rmi lam du khyi rta 'der so la sogs
NK040(thi)003:2547: rmis nas gnod pa rnams da byung na lus gdon
NK040(thi)003:2548: yin / dang po lus gdon gyi cho 'phrul byung nas /
NK040(thi)003:2549: rjes su gnas gdon gyi cho 'phrul byung na gnas gdon zhan pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2550: sngon du gnyan sa'i cho 'phrul byung na /
NK040(thi)003:2551: rjes su lus gdon gyi cho 'phrul byung na 'bring ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:2552: gnyan sa'i cho 'phrul rtag par byung nas /
NK040(thi)003:2553: lus gdon gyi cho 'phrul 'ong ma nus na gnyan sa drag pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2554: tshar tshad cho 'phrul dus gcig 'ong ba'i rigs kyang yod /
NK040(thi)003:2555: des gnas gdon lus gdon gnyis kyi shan 'byed kyang song /
NK040(thi)003:2556: gnyis pa cho 'phrul dang tshar tshad gnyis kyi shan 'byed la /
NK040(thi)003:2558: mda' mdung la sogs mtshon rgyab pa'am /
NK040(thi)003:2559: mdzo g.yag la sogs rwa can gyis brdung nas lus la rnag khrag bshad pa /
NK040(thi)003:2562: rang dang nye du gang dmar shi ba /
NK040(thi)003:2563: rang gi khang pa 'gyel ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2566: dgra la shor ba rmis pa /
NK040(thi)003:2567: dug la rjen zas byas pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2568: stong gsum mes tshig rlung gis gtor ba /
NK040(thi)003:2569: rang gi rang zos pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2570: lus khyung sbrul nya chen pos mid la lus rdul phran bzhin du gtor /
NK040(thi)003:2571: rang gi rang gis zos pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2572: gzhan la byin pa gzhan gyis glo snying rang la byin nas zos pa rmis na /
NK040(thi)003:2578: sngo tshod 'thung dang sgog sngon za /
NK040(thi)003:2579: sbang ma tsha g.yer sgog gsum dang /
NK040(thi)003:2580: thur du song dang lud gseb phyin /
NK040(thi)003:2581: khung du 'dzul dang mun pas gtib /
NK040(thi)003:2582: sha btsos rlangs can sha khrag rlon pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2583: gro mon ram pa mar nag lcags spyad /
NK040(thi)003:2584: bu ram nag 'dur ster ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2585: gshin po tsho 'dus nas bskyel bsu bkur sti byed pa /
NK040(thi)003:2586: me tog dmar po'i gling du phyin pa /
NK040(thi)003:2587: lus la gos dmar sar pa gon pa /
NK040(thi)003:2588: mgo la zhwa nag zhwa sngon gon pa /
NK040(thi)003:2590: bud med rigs mi 'dra ba mang pos bkur bsti byed pa rnams ni /
NK040(thi)003:2591: mgo bskor ba'i tshar yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:2592: da rung mal du bsdad par bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2593: des cho 'phrul tshar tshad gnyis kyis shan 'byed song /
NK040(thi)003:2594: spyir chod dka' sla gnyis la /
NK040(thi)003:2597: mi mang po shi ba'i phung shul rnams 'phral 'jig te 'dris sla gting thung ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:2599: brag phug dang grog phug rnams 'phral phug gnyis kar 'jigs pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2600: shing gcig chu mig rgya mtsho pha 'ong rnams /
NK040(thi)003:2601: slar mi 'jigs kyang gting che bying che /
NK040(thi)003:2603: pe kar rgyal po dkor bdag rnams ni shes pa rtsub rigs pa mtho dman che /
NK040(thi)003:2604: 'phral cho 'phrul 'ang gdug rtsub che yang slong ba sla /
NK040(thi)003:2606: dam sri dang srin mo ma mo rnams ni /
NK040(thi)003:2611: sems mi bde slong ba sla /
NK040(thi)003:2612: non pa sla phyi 'brang byed du 'ong ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:2613: klu bdud klu gnyan sa bdag sa srin rnams gnyid che shes pa 'thib /
NK040(thi)003:2620: gting che zhe gnag pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2621: btsan dang thel rang yul lha ma sangs rnams zang zing mang /
NK040(thi)003:2622: rmi lam gtad med mang po ston /
NK040(thi)003:2632: ma slong ba dang ma non pa thams cad la /
NK040(thi)003:2633: rgyun sring ba gal che ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:2634: ro dang 'dre la gcod pa sla /
NK040(thi)003:2635: na tsha dang sdug bsngal la gcod pa dka' /
NK040(thi)003:2636: de bas chags sdang chos brgyad la gcod pa dka' /
NK040(thi)003:2637: phyi gcod pa bas nang gcod pa dka' bgo che /
NK040(thi)003:2638: dngos grub myur ba yin no //
NK040(thi)003:2639: phan dga' phan 'dod zhan pa spong /
NK040(thi)003:2640: na tsha cho 'phrul ci byung yang /
NK040(thi)003:2641: the tshom yid gnyis spang bar bya /
NK040(thi)003:2642: gsum pa mo rtsis sman gsum gyi shan 'byed ni /
NK040(thi)003:2643: dang po mo dang rtsis la brten nas gcod pa slong ba'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:2644: khyim na khrid de lto dge bshes pa rim gro byas na /
NK040(thi)003:2645: bsha' lug thag bshal dang 'dra bas myur tu shi ba yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2647: gcod pa nad slong ba'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:2648: mo rtsis gnyis la rten nas su /
NK040(thi)003:2649: khyim du khrid de lto dge dang //
NK040(thi)003:2650: shes pa rim gro byas pa bzhin //
NK040(thi)003:2651: nad pa myur du 'gro ba yin //
NK040(thi)003:2653: des mo rtsis kyi shan 'byed song /
NK040(thi)003:2654: gnyis pa sman pas rtsa chu la brtag ste /
NK040(thi)003:2655: tsha grangs la sogs nad rnams ngo shes par byas nas /
NK040(thi)003:2656: nad gang yin so sor dmigs pas gcun te /
NK040(thi)003:2657: des kyang ma thub na mtha' gtad byed cing rgyab 'dre snang srid yongs la gtad cing /
NK040(thi)003:2658: nad bcud so so'i rtsi dgu sman bcu byed pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2660: sman pas rtsa chu gnyis la brtag /
NK040(thi)003:2661: tsha grangs la sogs shan 'byed nas //
NK040(thi)003:2662: so sor bcun te rgyab 'dre rnams //
NK040(thi)003:2663: snang srid kun la gtad nas su //
NK040(thi)003:2664: nang bcud rtsi sman gang 'gro byed //
NK040(thi)003:2666: des mo rtsis sman gsum gyi shan 'byed song /
NK040(thi)003:2668: sems can rang rgyud pa gnyis shan 'byed ni /
NK040(thi)003:2671: sbal lcong sbrul gsum la sogs pa'i sems can snang na /
NK040(thi)003:2672: phata cig byas pa tsam gyis rang nyid ma cig
NK040(thi)003:2673: lab sgron sku mdog mthing nag tu gyur par sgoms
NK040(thi)003:2674: / yang phata nyi shu rtsa gcig byas pa tsam
NK040(thi)003:2675: gyis rang gi thugs kha nas mda' rgod sgro ma
NK040(thi)003:2677: gnam lcags gyis made'u tsh+wa tsh+wa si li li 'phro ba nyi shu rtsa gcig 'phros bas /
NK040(thi)003:2678: sems can gang yin pa'i snying dkar nag mtshams su rgyab pas thal ba bun gyis song bar bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:2679: des sems can gang yin pa de rang gi thog tshur 'chong ba'am /
NK040(thi)003:2684: sems can gang yin pa de /
NK040(thi)003:2685: 'jigs su rung ba gcig red par bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)003:2686: kho'i kha der rang rang pheb par bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)003:2688: smad kyis bardzisa nas kho yi thog tu 'dug pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2689: de ni cho 'phrul gyi shan 'byed do //
NK040(thi)003:2690: da ni sems can rang rgyud pa'i shan 'byed ni /
NK040(thi)003:2691: sems can de bros pas thar na gar 'gror thong la /
NK040(thi)003:2692: de'i rjes su the tshom mi byed pa gal che'o //
NK040(thi)003:2693: de man rang bzhin thog tu sdad na /
NK040(thi)003:2694: sems can gang yin pa de bsad dogs pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2695: the tshom byas na rang nyid na ba'am /
NK040(thi)003:2696: shi dog pa'i phyir shan 'byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2697: de cho 'phrul dang sems can rang rgyud gnyis kyi shan 'byed pa song /
NK040(thi)003:2698: lnga pa mi dang mi ma yin pa'i shan 'byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:2699: nub mo'am rang kher gcod byed pa'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:2700: mngon sum du snang srid pa mthong na /
NK040(thi)003:2701: phata cig byas pa tsam gyis rang nyid kho yi khar phab ste /
NK040(thi)003:2704: des rang zhir 'gro ba yin ste /
NK040(thi)003:2705: de'i rjes su rang nyid kyang /
NK040(thi)003:2706: skye med ngang du 'dug pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:2707: mi'i nang nas dgra byung bas khra ther la sogs ca co shor na /
NK040(thi)003:2708: byams snying rje bsngo ba smon lam gyis gdab bo //
NK040(thi)003:2709: des ma nus na kho'i rjes la bzung la /
NK040(thi)003:2710: gnyan khrod 'di nyid yin nam log gi gnyan chen la gtad nas /
NK040(thi)003:2711: tshar tshad ma byung gis bar du mtha' gtad byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2712: tshar tshad byung nas mthu dang mnan pa la sogs bla ma'i zhal las shes /
NK040(thi)003:2713: des mi dang mi ma yin pa'i shan 'byed pa song /
NK040(thi)003:2714: drug pa skyon dang yon tan gnyis shan 'byed pa la /
NK040(thi)003:2716: gcod dbang ma thob par slob dpon gyi phyir 'chad cing rang gis nyams su len pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2717: slob mas kyang dbang ma thob par nyams su len cing /
NK040(thi)003:2718: man ngag bcun pas nad pa la sogs dngos grub skabs re byung yang /
NK040(thi)003:2719: dpon slob gnyis ka tshe'i dus bstung nas /
NK040(thi)003:2720: na tsha drag pos shi bar byed cing dmyal ba 'gro ba yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2722: dbang med pa la dngos grub med //
NK040(thi)003:2723: bye ma btsir ba'i mar dang 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:2724: de bas dbang bskur dam pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:2725: rab tu 'bad de blang byar bya //
NK040(thi)003:2728: gang gis rgyud lung nga rgyal gyis //
NK040(thi)003:2729: dbang bskur med par 'chad cing nyan //
NK040(thi)003:2730: nyams su len cing man ngag gis //
NK040(thi)003:2731: dngos grub skabs re thob na yang //
NK040(thi)003:2732: slob dpon slob ma gnyis ka ni //
NK040(thi)003:2733: tshe la bstung nas shi ma thag /
NK040(thi)003:2734: dngos grub mi thob dmyal bar 'gro //
NK040(thi)003:2738: dbang thob cing slob dpon gyi phyir 'chad nas dpon
NK040(thi)003:2739: slob gnyis kas nyams su len cing man ngag gis
NK040(thi)003:2740: gcun na / nad phan pa la sogs dngos grub gang yang thob cing /
NK040(thi)003:2741: phyi mar phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub gang yang thob pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2743: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK040(thi)003:2744: sangs rgyas go 'phang rgyang mi ring //
NK040(thi)003:2745: lag na rin chen thog pa'i mis //
NK040(thi)003:2746: longs spyod rgyang mi ring ba bzhin //
NK040(thi)003:2747: dngos grub myur te the tshom med //
NK040(thi)003:2748: des skyon dang yon tan gnyis kyi chings so //
NK040(thi)003:2749: lnga pa log rgyug 'byam gsum gyi ching la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:2753: dang po log pa la gnyis ste /
NK040(thi)003:2755: log non rang gi ngo bo gnyis so //
NK040(thi)003:2757: gzhung chung las gzhi rang gi 'dres bsgyur nas log pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2758: gnyan sa'i lha 'dres bsgyur nas log pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2759: spyod pa ma legs pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2760: gtan log chen po dang bzhi'o //
NK040(thi)003:2761: dang po gnyan khrod du 'gro khar skrag shum shum byed nas 'gro ma spob pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2762: skyon mang po byung nas 'gro bshol ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:2763: gnyis pa ni gnyan sar lha 'dre'i cho 'phrul 'jigs pa byung nas bros pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2764: ngan pa la ngan par 'dzin pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2765: bzang po la dga' brod du 'dzin na log /
NK040(thi)003:2766: gsum pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i bslab bya 'gal ba'i spyod pa byed pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:2767: bzhi pa spyir chos thams cad dang 'gal ba'i spyod pa ngan pa rnams byed pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:2768: gnyis pa gcod log na stag mos wa sha len /
NK040(thi)003:2770: gnyan sar phyin nas lha 'dre'i cho 'phrul 'jigs pa byung nas bros na /
NK040(thi)003:2774: mi phod pa la thog rdzis byed nas /
NK040(thi)003:2775: bros sa gang yin pa'i gnyan sa der phyi rjes su 'ong nas bsdad cing /
NK040(thi)003:2776: mngon rtogs kyi rim pa gong ltar nyams su len cing /
NK040(thi)003:2777: khyad par du gang na yod pa'i gnam sa cha lang rdeb dkrug gis mtha' gtad byed cing /
NK040(thi)003:2778: tshar tshad ma byung gis bar du bsdad do //
NK040(thi)003:2779: de ni slong chen snyem zhugs log non gyi gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:2781: gnad gcod sdug na lha 'dre gnad kyis bskul /
NK040(thi)003:2783: cho 'phrul tshar tshad gang yang ma byung na slong ma thub pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2784: de la gong du bstan pa'i phyi nang gsang gsum
NK040(thi)003:2785: gyi mtha' gtad gang dgos skabs dang bstun la bya'o
NK040(thi)003:2788: kha mchu dum rting bzlog zer ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:2789: cho 'phrul tshar tshad tshul bzhin du byung yang /
NK040(thi)003:2790: da dung mal du bsdad na 'byams pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2792: gos nag po bskon chis sam /
NK040(thi)003:2793: mi rnams ngo 'dzum nag pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2795: rdo 'phro thur la 'gro chis byas pa'am /
NK040(thi)003:2796: gos phud nas gyon chis byas pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2797: zhal lce mdun ma byas rgyab bzlog pa'am /
NK040(thi)003:2798: spyad pa khyer rgyab tshur la gtad pa'am /
NK040(thi)003:2799: khral bu lon sod rgyab bdas pa rmis pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2800: gzhan yang sbrul byung nas bskor ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2801: skyas pa lang long tshur la byung ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2802: sems can grol zin btag chis byas pa'am /
NK040(thi)003:2803: zhing rmo chis byas pa rmis na /
NK040(thi)003:2804: chod rgyab bsdad yun ring na nad bsnon chis yin te 'byams pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:2805: de la gcod 'byams na rnal 'byor thal ba stor ces gsungs pas /
NK040(thi)003:2807: des log rgyug 'byams gsum gyi chings so //
NK040(thi)003:2808: drug pa bug ral 'khyams gsum gyi ching la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:2812: dang po gcod bug pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:2813: gnyan sa nas logs su nyin bskor la song kyang ma phebs nas /
NK040(thi)003:2814: zhag la thog na bug pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2815: gcod bug na dmigs pa rgyang zhag gces /
NK040(thi)003:2816: ces gsungs pas zhag la thog na sngar gyi gnyan
NK040(thi)003:2817: sa der rang nyid 'dug par bsgom zhing sngar ltar
NK040(thi)003:2818: nyams len la gcun par bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2820: gnyan sar chod ma tshud par 'gro dgos byung na ral ba yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2821: 'gro mi des rdo gtel bzung ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:2822: rang gi zhabs nas rdo blang nas /
NK040(thi)003:2824: rang nyid rje btsun mar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:2826: lha 'dre thams cad bsdus nas rdo la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:2827: rang gis mdzu gu lnga mkha' 'gro ma lngar bsgoms nas /
NK040(thi)003:2828: gnas po de tsir gyis bzung bar bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2830: snod de lcags kyi spar bur bsam pa'i kha sbrul nag gi bsdom par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2831: de lus la 'chang zhing khyer nas rang gi zhabs su bcug la /
NK040(thi)003:2832: gar 'dug sa der sngar gyi gnyan sa der yin par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:2833: tshar tshad ma byung bar du sngar ltar nyams len bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2834: gcod ral na rdo rje'i go ra gces /
NK040(thi)003:2837: mal du 'dug mi'i gcod pa rnams kyis dpon des /
NK040(thi)003:2838: rang nyid khros ma nag mor bsgom la thugs ka
NK040(thi)003:2839: nas gnam lcags kyis rdo rje dpag tu med pa
NK040(thi)003:2840: 'phros / rdo rje'i gur khang chen po gcig tu gcod sgar ba kun tshud par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:2841: gcod pa gcig pu yin zhing mal du 'dug mi med na /
NK040(thi)003:2843: rdo rje'i go ra ni mi dgos gsungs /
NK040(thi)003:2845: gnyan mig ma non pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:2846: gcod 'khyams na lha 'dre'i barla bzung gces /
NK040(thi)003:2848: gnyan sa de'i gnyan mig ma non na /
NK040(thi)003:2849: gnyan mig logs su snang na /
NK040(thi)003:2850: de'i sa rdo shing gsum blangs la rang gi zhabs su bcug go //
NK040(thi)003:2852: bdun pa bdud bzhi gegs sel gyi ching la /
NK040(thi)003:2854: bdud kyi ngo bo ngos bzung ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2855: de nyid bsal ba'i thabs so //
NK040(thi)003:2857: dang po bdud kyi ngo bo ni gnyis 'dzin gyi shes pa rang rgyud pa yin no //
NK040(thi)003:2859: gang zhig dge ba la bar du gcod par byed pas na bdud zhes bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:2860: gsum pa dbye ba la bzhi ste /
NK040(thi)003:2862: thog bcas bdud dang thog med bdud //
NK040(thi)003:2863: dga' brod bdud dang snyem byed bzhi //
NK040(thi)003:2865: dang po thog bcas kyi bdud ni /
NK040(thi)003:2866: phyi snang ba mngon par zhen cing /
NK040(thi)003:2867: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya'i chos la sogs /
NK040(thi)003:2869: ngan pa la sdang ba yin la /
NK040(thi)003:2870: bar pa la gti mug yin /
NK040(thi)003:2871: lag len du mi dang gcan gzan la sogs /
NK040(thi)003:2872: dngos su byung ba la skrag cing bros pas /
NK040(thi)003:2873: snang ba dgrar lang pa la zer ro //
NK040(thi)003:2874: gnyis pa thog med kyi bdud ni /
NK040(thi)003:2875: spyir nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang /
NK040(thi)003:2876: gzung 'dzin la sogs rnam rtog gi kun tu btag pa rnams yin la /
NK040(thi)003:2877: lag len du mi dang gcan gzan la sogs pa dngos su byung ba la skrag cing bros pas /
NK040(thi)003:2878: snyang ba dgrar langs la zer ro //
NK040(thi)003:2879: gnyis pa thog med kyi bdud ni /
NK040(thi)003:2880: spyir nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang gzung 'dzin la
NK040(thi)003:2881: sogs rnam rtog gi kun tu btags pa rnams yin
NK040(thi)003:2882: la lag len du gnyan sar rmi lam ngan pa
NK040(thi)003:2883: la sogs 'dre gdon la skrag cing bros pas gdon
NK040(thi)003:2884: gyi sna 'dren red nas na tsha sdug bsngal slar
NK040(thi)003:2886: gsum dga' brod kyi bdud ni /
NK040(thi)003:2887: spyir nyams dang ting 'dzin la sogs 'jig rten gyi
NK040(thi)003:2888: bsnyen bkur longs spyod la dga' zhing brod pa yin
NK040(thi)003:2889: la / lag len du gnyan sar na tsha sdug bsngal zhi ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2891: dgra gdon gyi mi tshugs pa la sogs pa'i byin
NK040(thi)003:2892: rlabs phra mo la dga' zhing brod pa la zer
NK040(thi)003:2893: / bzhi pa snyems byed kyi bdud ni /
NK040(thi)003:2896: phan gnod bde sdug la sogs pa'i gnyis 'dzin rnams yin la /
NK040(thi)003:2897: lag len du gcod pa byin rlabs yod dam med /
NK040(thi)003:2898: na tsha phan nam mi phan /
NK040(thi)003:2899: gnyan khrod 'grim phod dam mi phod /
NK040(thi)003:2900: skyon yod med la sogs la mo btab ste /
NK040(thi)003:2902: na tsha e drag bsam pa lta bu /
NK040(thi)003:2903: dur khrod dang lung stong dang /
NK040(thi)003:2904: 'brog dgon pa la sogs pa'i sa /
NK040(thi)003:2905: gnyan khrod rnams su phyin yang /
NK040(thi)003:2906: bdag la bar chad dang gnod pa mi 'byung ste /
NK040(thi)003:2908: bdag lta bu la lha dang bla mas spyan gyis gzigs /
NK040(thi)003:2909: dkon mchog gsum gyis thugs rjes skyobs /
NK040(thi)003:2910: dpa' bo mkha' 'gros srung skyob byed pa'i snyems 'chang ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2911: gcod kyi gdams pa zab mo yod snyams pa'i gdeng 'chang ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2912: nang du lha med 'dre med kyi stong nyid rtogs pa'i nyams len yod bsam pa'i ngom pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:2913: lha 'dre'i cho 'phrul ci byung yang lus sbyin pas chog ster nus na 'dre 'ong mi nus /
NK040(thi)003:2917: de ltar byas pas chog snyam nas gcod byed pa la zer /
NK040(thi)003:2918: gong du bstan pa'i thog bcas kyi bdud de la nam yang mi phod pa'i yul drug yod de /
NK040(thi)003:2924: g.yang za rnams kyi srog la brgol bas mi phod do //
NK040(thi)003:2928: de rnams kyis srog la rgol bas mi phod ste /
NK040(thi)003:2930: shal rong sgyed po mi btsugs 'tshal //
NK040(thi)003:2931: brag zur phyams rtse mi bardzi 'tshal //
NK040(thi)003:2933: des bdud bzhi'i ngos bzung ba song /
NK040(thi)003:2934: gnyis pa bdud de nyid bsal ba'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:2935: blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyi bsal ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2936: dam tshig gi sgo nas bsal ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:2937: yon tan gyi sgo nas zhabs bsdu ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:2939: dang po blo rab kyi 'dre bdud dang rang snang du gcod pa'i thabs ni /
NK040(thi)003:2941: re ba med pa sangs rgyas gcod //
NK040(thi)003:2942: dog pa med pas 'khor ba gcod //
NK040(thi)003:2943: nyam nga med pa 'dre bdud gcod //
NK040(thi)003:2945: gcod bya med pas chos kun gcod //
NK040(thi)003:2947: de lta bu'i don ni gcod gsang spyod rnal lam ma'i nang du gsal bas der shes so //
NK040(thi)003:2948: gnyis pa blo 'bring gis 'dre bdud gcod pa'i sa btsal ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:2949: 'dre bdud khyod lus la gnod dam sems la gnod /
NK040(thi)003:2950: lus ni bem po rdo dang khyad med pas rdo la 'dre bdud gnod dam /
NK040(thi)003:2951: sems ni dngos med nam mkha' dang khyad med pas /
NK040(thi)003:2952: nam mkha' la 'dre bdud gnod dam /
NK040(thi)003:2953: sems ngas ma mthong ba la /
NK040(thi)003:2954: 'dre bdud kyis gang nas mthong snyam pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:2955: sems lhod kyis klod la bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:2956: gsum pa dbang po tha mas 'dre bdud nyid la gtad pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:2958: gnas po bdud la g.yar bas gzhi 'bras gcig tu 'dres /
NK040(thi)003:2959: skyel ma dgra la bcol bas 'jigs med btsan sar thar /
NK040(thi)003:2960: nad pa 'dre la bcol bas nad med bde bar 'tsho /
NK040(thi)003:2961: lam khyer rkyen la byas pas mi mthun 'gal rkyen bral /
NK040(thi)003:2963: gnyan sa de ru sleb nas nyams len 'di ltar bya ste /
NK040(thi)003:2964: 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas lus ngag yid gsum bdag tu bzung nas /
NK040(thi)003:2965: gces 'dzin byas pas gnas skabs su 'dre dang gdon bgegs gnod /
NK040(thi)003:2966: na tsha dang sdug bsngal byung /
NK040(thi)003:2969: de bdag 'dzin gyi lan pa yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:2970: da ni nga'i lus 'dis rgyu sngon gyis las la grub /
NK040(thi)003:2971: rkyen pha ma'i 'dod chags gis bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:2972: 'bras bu dal 'byor gyi mi lus thob /
NK040(thi)003:2973: dbang po skye mched thams cad tshang ba'i lus po
NK040(thi)003:2974: 'di mdzes shing gtsang ba yid du 'ong ba gces
NK040(thi)003:2975: shing phongs pa / dgos shing mkho ba'i lus 'di /
NK040(thi)003:2976: spyir 'gro drug sems can gyi blud du 'bul /
NK040(thi)003:2977: dgos drin can pha ma'i don du bsngo /
NK040(thi)003:2978: yang dgos lha 'dre khyed tsho'i don du gtong bas /
NK040(thi)003:2980: mi ring na chos la zo /
NK040(thi)003:2981: zhen pa til 'bru tsam yang mi byed do //
NK040(thi)003:2982: su 'dod pas khyer gcig byas pas /
NK040(thi)003:2983: lus la chags zhen mi byed par mchil snab bzhin du bor la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:2984: mdze ro bzhin du bskyur la thong /
NK040(thi)003:2985: phyi sa bzhin du spang la btang /
NK040(thi)003:2986: sa rdo bzhin du bdag 'dzin med par bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:2987: 'dre dang gdon bgegs rnams lus po kyi ma lus
NK040(thi)003:2988: par zos par bsgom la lus dngos 'dzin can de
NK040(thi)003:2990: sems stong pa nyid ni ngo bo mi 'dug /
NK040(thi)003:2991: de la bdag 'dzin dang gces 'dzin gyi dgos pa mi 'dug /
NK040(thi)003:2992: nya ra bya rgyu dang srung rgyu mi 'dug /
NK040(thi)003:2993: lus kyi duhkha dang gnyer kha mi dgos par 'dug /
NK040(thi)003:2994: snyam la lhod de 'jog pa yin /
NK040(thi)003:2995: gcod mkhan phal cher lus mi gtsang ba'i phung po rnag khrag gi rkyal pa /
NK040(thi)003:2996: ngar snab kyi phung po 'di bdag la dgos pa mi gada'o //
NK040(thi)003:2997: su 'dod pas khyer cig zer te /
NK040(thi)003:2998: de la skyon bzhi yod pas mi 'thad do //
NK040(thi)003:2999: gcig tu zhen nas sbyin par gtong na ma dag pa'i sbyin par 'gro nas tshogs mi rdzogs /
NK040(thi)003:3000: gnyis pa la bdag la mi mkho ba gcig 'dre
NK040(thi)003:3001: la sbyin yang mi phan te kho la mi mkho
NK040(thi)003:3002: / gsum pa 'dres khyer du byung dogs pa'i sna bkab tu 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3003: bzhi pa lus mi gtsang ba'i thum po yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:3004: 'dre zhen pa log nas mi 'dod la re ba'i phyir yin pas mi 'thad do //
NK040(thi)003:3005: 'o na ci ltar byed na las mtha' gsum la go ba len dgos te /
NK040(thi)003:3006: las mtha' gsum ni nga na nga thog btang /
NK040(thi)003:3007: skyug ni bro na bro thog tu btang /
NK040(thi)003:3010: yang na nga thog tu btang ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3011: sems can 'di tsam gcig 'khor bar 'khyam pa la /
NK040(thi)003:3012: nga gcig pu 'khor bar 'khyams na ci yin /
NK040(thi)003:3013: 'di rnams sdug bsngal gyi mnar na /
NK040(thi)003:3014: nga gcig po sdug bsngal ba ci nyes /
NK040(thi)003:3015: sems can 'di rnams thams cad kyi don du /
NK040(thi)003:3016: bdag gis lus ngag yid gsum glud du bsngo ba la 'gro snyam pa'i 'dun pa dang ldan pas /
NK040(thi)003:3017: ya nga ba bag tsha ba gang byung ba la mi bros par slar de ka brgyud de phata /
NK040(thi)003:3019: lus ngag yid gsum shing bcad nas 'gyel ba'i sdong po ltar khres se bskyur bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3020: skyug bro na bro thog tu btang ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3021: gang skyug bro ba'i mi gtsang ba'am /
NK040(thi)003:3023: gos rul la sogs yid yul du gang skyug bro
NK040(thi)003:3024: ba'i steng du snyem zhugs pa de ka ched du
NK040(thi)003:3025: gnyer la / gza' btung gos sogs longs spyod de skyug bro na skyug pa slar 'thung zhing /
NK040(thi)003:3026: rjes su ci yang mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bskyur bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3027: mi phod pa la thog bardzisa btang ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3028: lus ngag yid gsum gyis la spyod pa rbud chod la btang la /
NK040(thi)003:3029: lha 'dre mi gsum la sogs gang mi phod cing /
NK040(thi)003:3030: the tshom dang snyem zhugs pa de nyid kyi dus
NK040(thi)003:3031: su rtogs pa sna ma bskyil bar nyams byung rgyal
NK040(thi)003:3032: du btang / gang la chags pa de spang /
NK040(thi)003:3033: sdang ba de dang du blangs mdor na gnyis 'dzin gyi mdud pa bshig la /
NK040(thi)003:3034: snang ba thams cad thad kar bcad la bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:3035: de rnams byas pas bdud lam du slong nyon mongs pa grogs su 'char /
NK040(thi)003:3041: byang chub kyi go 'phang brnyes par 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)003:3042: de ni gtsang tsog ro snyom 'jigs pa thog bardzisa kyi gnad do //
NK040(thi)003:3043: des ni blo rab 'bring tha ma'i sgo nas bdud bas la ba song /
NK040(thi)003:3045: gnyis pa dam tshig gi sgo nas /
NK040(thi)003:3046: bdud bsal ba la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)003:3051: yar sangs rgyas la re ba mi bca' /
NK040(thi)003:3052: mar ngan song la nyams mi nga /
NK040(thi)003:3053: 'chi bdag gi gshin rje'i bka' chad dang /
NK040(thi)003:3054: bsun ma byung yang skrag 'jigs mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3055: dbang phyug chen po byung yang grub mtha' mi spang /
NK040(thi)003:3056: bdud bye ba dung phyur gyi dmag dpung byung yang g.yo 'gul mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3057: rang gi snying khar mda' btsug kyang khong khro mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3058: 'gro ba khri phrag dus gcig la rgyal nad kyis 'chi bar mthong yang /
NK040(thi)003:3060: rang da lta nyid du sangs rgyas kyang /
NK040(thi)003:3061: rang don du gzhan su la yang gnod 'tshe mi byed /
NK040(thi)003:3062: gnam sa thams cad dus gcig la 'khrugs kyang dgongs pa la g.yo ba med /
NK040(thi)003:3063: lta ba klong gyur gyi ngang du thag chod la bzhag go //
NK040(thi)003:3065: sngon 'gro'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:3066: rang 'dod kyi 'khri ba cung zad kyang mi bsam /
NK040(thi)003:3067: dngos gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i tshe /
NK040(thi)003:3068: gzhan don gyi blo rgya mi bskum zhing je cher bskyed la /
NK040(thi)003:3069: mi dang mi ma yin pa'i bskul spyod zer te /
NK040(thi)003:3070: slong gi cho 'phrul la sogs ci byung yang ri bo ltar g.yo 'gul med pa /
NK040(thi)003:3071: rgya mtsho'i 'jings ltar kha gting med pa /
NK040(thi)003:3072: nyi zla ltar gsal 'grib med pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:3073: rgyun 'babs kyi chu bo ltar rgyun chad med pa /
NK040(thi)003:3074: nam mkha' ltar yang dog med pa /
NK040(thi)003:3075: sa gzhi ltar 'pho 'gyur med par bya /
NK040(thi)003:3076: de yang lus dur khrod kyi ro bzhin du bskyur /
NK040(thi)003:3077: ngag pi wang gi gsang thag bcad pa ltar bskyur /
NK040(thi)003:3078: sems ran 'thag chu bcad pa ltar bskyur /
NK040(thi)003:3079: lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'du shes thams cad sog
NK040(thi)003:3080: phon thag pa bcad pa ltar shig se bskyur la
NK040(thi)003:3081: bzhag cing / g.yo 'gul bsam sems srag srig gang yang mi bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3084: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa /
NK040(thi)003:3085: gsang sngags kyis dam tshig rnams ma nyams par bsrung zhing /
NK040(thi)003:3086: de rnams dang mi 'gal bar byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:3087: spyod pa'i dam tshig yin la /
NK040(thi)003:3088: bye brag tu lha la sogs pa rang la phan
NK040(thi)003:3089: par byed pa rnams la dga' ba'i 'dun pas gsol
NK040(thi)003:3090: mchod mi bya / 'dre bdud la sogs pas rang
NK040(thi)003:3091: la gnod bya ba ci byas shing 'khon du ci
NK040(thi)003:3092: mchod mi bya / btsal kyang / de rnams gang
NK040(thi)003:3093: la yang ngan lan khro gtum rnam 'gyur ngan pa
NK040(thi)003:3094: gnod sems ngan spyod gang yang med par byed pa
NK040(thi)003:3095: mchod mi bya / btsal kyang / / bzang byas ngan byas gang yang khyad med pa /
NK040(thi)003:3096: dug dang bdud rtsi ro mnyam pa /
NK040(thi)003:3097: gcod byed pa'i dus su gzhung lugs kyiis chos nyams
NK040(thi)003:3098: su len lugs tshul bzhin ma gtog pa gzhan gang
