NK040(thi)003:3099: yang mi byed / khyad par du rigs byed mtha' dag spang ste /
NK040(thi)003:3100: rgya kong tse 'phrul gyi rgyal po byung yang rtsis mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3101: bram ze pra se na byung yang mo mi btab /
NK040(thi)003:3102: gshin rab mi bo byung yang bon mi byed /
NK040(thi)003:3103: phyag na rdo rje byung yang srung skyob mi zhu /
NK040(thi)003:3104: gal te rang la gzhan gyi bskur ba'i slad du
NK040(thi)003:3105: byas kyang mi dgag par de la spro ba mi
NK040(thi)003:3106: bskyed do // thams cad gzhan don du bsngo /
NK040(thi)003:3107: 'jig rten gyi bya ba la mi 'jug /
NK040(thi)003:3108: gzhan 'dre 'dul la sogs pa'i rim gro la mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3111: tshar tshad slong tshad mi bsgrag go //
NK040(thi)003:3112: dngos grub ci byung yang spro ba mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3113: legs nyes kyi ltas ci byung yang dgag sgrub mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3114: lha 'dres cho 'phrul ci bstan cing snang srid thams
NK040(thi)003:3115: cad g.yo ba'i slong la sogs phyi nang gsang gsum
NK040(thi)003:3116: ci byung yang / khyad med gal ma mchis su bor /
NK040(thi)003:3117: gang la yang snyam snyem med par thag chod rbud chod du btang /
NK040(thi)003:3118: smyo spyod kyis dbang gis gnyan sar thab gzhob dang /
NK040(thi)003:3119: sa rko rdo zlog shing bcad chu mig dkrug mtsho brdung /
NK040(thi)003:3120: brag bshag pa la sogs pa lha 'dre'i gnas la
NK040(thi)003:3121: sogs la thub thub rung rung gang yang ched du
NK040(thi)003:3123: stab kyis de 'dra rang ngam gzhan gyis byed pa byung na yang /
NK040(thi)003:3124: de rnams la rnam rtog khong 'khrig snyam snyem gang yang mi bya /
NK040(thi)003:3125: rdzas ngan gyi dud pa mi btang /
NK040(thi)003:3126: dus ma yin par phata skad mi gdab /
NK040(thi)003:3128: gcod kyi gdam pa 'di gnyan gnyan 'dra yang mi gnyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:3131: dam dam 'dra la lhod pa'i chos yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:3132: dam tshig dang ldan pas 'tsho shes pa gal che'o //
NK040(thi)003:3134: zhe sdang dang 'gran sems kyis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3135: rgo nyo dang pho tshod kyis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3136: pho rus dang khe drag kyis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3137: nga rgyal dang che tshul gyis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3138: dregs pa dang rang 'dod kyis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3139: rnyed pa dang bkur bstis mi 'gro /
NK040(thi)003:3140: nges 'byung gis dad pa chen pos 'agro'o //
NK040(thi)003:3141: des dam tshig sgo nas bdud bsal ba song /
NK040(thi)003:3143: gsum pa yon tan gyi sgo nas zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3144: lar spros bcas zang zing du ma bas /
NK040(thi)003:3145: spros med pha rol phyin pa'i don la /
NK040(thi)003:3146: thun gcig mnyam par bzhag pa gnad che /
NK040(thi)003:3147: gnyan khrod brgya stong bskor babs skad cig ma'i snyem thag chod pa gal che /
NK040(thi)003:3148: 'dus byas kyi zas nor dpag tu med pa dngos su gtong ba bas /
NK040(thi)003:3149: zhen 'dzin dang bral ba'i dmigs pas lus sbyin par btang zhing dge sbyor thun re bsod nams che /
NK040(thi)003:3150: phal pa'i gnas su lo gcig bsgom pa las /
NK040(thi)003:3151: gnyan sa ri khrod du zhag gcig gi nyams len byed pa 'gyur che /
NK040(thi)003:3152: chos spyi'i nyams len rgyug ded zla ba gcig byas pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3153: bdud chod pa'i gdams pa thun gcig nyams su blangs pas lam rtags myur /
NK040(thi)003:3154: tshe 'di'i 'du 'dzi bsod nams kyis longs spyod dpag tu med pa byas pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3155: 'dod yon gyi 'khri pa chod de chog shes kyis
NK040(thi)003:3156: 'dun pa skad cig ma re skyes pa dpal 'byor
NK040(thi)003:3157: che ba yin / thun mong gi bsam pa bzang po mang po bas /
NK040(thi)003:3158: mchog gis sems bskyed gcig gi nang du 'dus pas dga' ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3159: gnyen po stobs dang bcas pas bsgoms bde gsal mi rtogs pa shar ba bas /
NK040(thi)003:3160: gnyen po dang bral ba'i sgom rang babs gzhi thog tu phebs stobs che ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3161: shes bya'i gnas mang po la mkhas pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3162: don gyi shes bya gcig shes pa gal che ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3163: lar cho 'phrul dang bar chad ci byung yang /
NK040(thi)003:3164: bdag la srung du gsol brgya tham pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3165: gsod cig zo gcig khyer gcig ces pa'i tshig gcig gis dga' ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3166: lha srung brgya la ra mdar bzlog pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3167: lha 'dre stong la za ru bcol bas dga' ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3168: lus la srung ba brgya btag pa bas /
NK040(thi)003:3169: na dga' shi skyid lan gcig gis dga' ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3170: des yon tan gyi sgo nas zhabs bsdu ba na song /
NK040(thi)003:3171: brgyad pa gol shor gyi ching bstan pa la gnyis ste /
NK040(thi)003:3172: dang po gol shor sa la ni /
NK040(thi)003:3174: tho co drag las su byas na gol /
NK040(thi)003:3176: snyom las su byas na gol /
NK040(thi)003:3177: nad chod dang 'jigs skyobs kyi dbang du byas na gol /
NK040(thi)003:3179: gcod sha sbyor du shor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3180: gnyan sar bud med brten pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:3181: gcod drag sngags su shor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3183: khro bo'i bskyed rim dang drag sngags bzla ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:3184: gcod tha mal du shor ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3190: che ba gsum gyi ngar bskyed /
NK040(thi)003:3191: ces gsungs pas lta ba'i rbad khams che ba /
NK040(thi)003:3192: gdam ngag gi lo rgyus che ba /
NK040(thi)003:3193: lus srog gi gtong phod che ba'o //
NK040(thi)003:3194: yang gcod 'di la lta bsgom spyod 'bras kyis gtan la phab dgos ste /
NK040(thi)003:3195: mal sa gnyan sa ri khrod /
NK040(thi)003:3198: spyod pa ro snyom thog rdzis /
NK040(thi)003:3199: rim gro sha khyer khrag khyer /
NK040(thi)003:3200: nyams len na dga' shi skyid /
NK040(thi)003:3201: lam khyer phung po gzan bskyur /
NK040(thi)003:3202: dam tshig dge med sdig med /
NK040(thi)003:3203: 'bras bu gnyis med lhun grub 'di nyams su blangs par bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3204: ces zab don las gsungs so //
NK040(thi)003:3205: yang gcod 'di la phyi nang gsang gsum gyis sgo nas gtan la phab dgos ste /
NK040(thi)003:3207: gnyan sa ri khrod 'grim pa phyi yi gcod //
NK040(thi)003:3208: phung po gzan du skyur ba nang gi gcod //
NK040(thi)003:3209: bdag 'dzin rtsad nas gcod pa gsang ba'i gcod //
NK040(thi)003:3211: yang gcod 'di la theg pa chen po'i lam gal che ste /
NK040(thi)003:3213: byams dang snying rje sems bskyed gsum //
NK040(thi)003:3214: gcod kyi gzhung lam 'gro sa yin //
NK040(thi)003:3216: yang gcod 'di la them pa gsum gyi so btsug pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:3218: snga them snga ru ma non na //
NK040(thi)003:3219: dgra ngan dag la bya shor 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:3220: de la zil non gnad bdun dgos //
NK040(thi)003:3222: gong du zil non gyi skabs su song //
NK040(thi)003:3223: bar them bar du ma non na //
NK040(thi)003:3224: dpa' bo'i lag gis mtshon shor 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:3225: de la rdo rje'i sbrul zhags dgos //
NK040(thi)003:3227: gzhung gis 'gros dang man ngag gi gcun thabs dang /
NK040(thi)003:3228: 'gro na rdo gtes bzung ba rnams yin no //
NK040(thi)003:3229: phyi them phyi ru ma non na //
NK040(thi)003:3230: nor len phyi rjes bsnyag pa 'dra //
NK040(thi)003:3231: de la dmag dpon khyung nag bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:3233: rjes chog gi skabs su gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3235: tshad rnam pa gsum dang ldan dgos te /
NK040(thi)003:3236: de yang rnal 'byor pa'i tshad gsum dang /
NK040(thi)003:3238: dang po rnal 'byor pa'i tshad gsum la /
NK040(thi)003:3240: cho 'phrul dang tshar tshad ma byung gi bar du gcun pa'o //
NK040(thi)003:3242: tshar tshad byung yang da dung zhag re mal du bsdad la /
NK040(thi)003:3243: mgo skor rjes snyog e 'ong brtag go //
NK040(thi)003:3245: tshar tshad legs po thon nas rjes chog byed nas spo bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3246: gsum pa lha 'dre'i tshar tshad gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3247: cho 'phrul dang tshar tshad gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3248: yang gcod 'di la gnad dgu dag gis 'dzer bsdom dgos te /
NK040(thi)003:3249: de yang 'don mi 'bros par myur ba'i gnad /
NK040(thi)003:3250: ro bsres dbyings bsres bsdeb na chun gcig tu chod pa'i gnad /
NK040(thi)003:3253: ma bsnyol na bsnyol ba'i gnad /
NK040(thi)003:3255: slong chen snyems zhugs log non gyi gnad /
NK040(thi)003:3256: gtsang rtsog ro snyom 'jigs pa thog rdzis kyis gnad /
NK040(thi)003:3257: dkar nag shan 'byed lha 'dre rol khrid dang dagu'o //
NK040(thi)003:3258: 'di rnams gzhung gi stod smad bar gsum du gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3259: yang gcod 'di la phata brjod dgos pa'i don ni /
NK040(thi)003:3261: phata kyis gdams pa 'di la bcu gnyis ston par byed pa 'di la /
NK040(thi)003:3262: phata bskyed par byed pa'i yul gsum dang gcig /
NK040(thi)003:3263: phata 'phel bar byed pa'i grogs gsum dang gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:3264: phata gzeng bstod pa'i dus gsum dang gsum /
NK040(thi)003:3265: phata lta ba'i gdeng gsum dang bzhi /
NK040(thi)003:3266: phata bsgom pa'i nyams gsum dang lnga /
NK040(thi)003:3267: phata spyod pa'i nges med gsum dang drug /
NK040(thi)003:3268: phata thob pa'i 'bras bu gsum dang bdun /
NK040(thi)003:3269: phata dran pa gsum dang brgyad /
NK040(thi)003:3270: phata gseng ba gsum dang dgu /
NK040(thi)003:3271: phata bsgyur ba gsum dang bcu /
NK040(thi)003:3272: phata rgyun chad med pa gsum dang bcu gcig /
NK040(thi)003:3273: phata la bzla ba gsum dang bcu gnyis so //
NK040(thi)003:3274: de la dang po phata skye bar byed pa'i yul gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3275: phyi snang ba'i yul la chags zhen skyes na phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3276: nang 'dzin pa'i sems la nyon mongs skyes na phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3277: bsgom pa'i dus bying rmug skyes na phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3278: phata skye ba'i yul ni gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3279: phata 'phel bar byed pa'i grogs gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3280: rgyud pa'i bla ma dang mjal dus su /
NK040(thi)003:3281: byin rlabs 'phel ba'i grogs su 'gro bas phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3283: dge sbyor 'phel ba'i grogs 'gro bas phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3284: gcig pur 'grog pa'i dus su nyams myong 'phel ba'i grogs su 'gro bas phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3285: phata 'phel bar byed pa'i grogs gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3286: phata gzeng bstod pa gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3287: mi mang po'i gseb nas rig pa ngar can gzeng bstod de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3288: rang gcig po'i dus su dran pas gzeng bstod de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3289: sgom pa'i dus su gsal ba la gzeng bstod de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3290: phata gzeng stod pa la gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3291: phata lta ba'i gdeng gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3292: dus gsum mtha' bral rtogs pas lta ba'i gdengs te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3293: lhug par rtogs pas lta ba'i gdengs te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3294: gnyis med bde chen rtogs pas lta ba'i gdengs te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3295: phata lta ba'i gdengs gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3296: phata bsgom pa'i lam gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3297: khrom gseb tu bla ma bsgom te phata /
NK040(thi)003:3298: rang gcig pu'i dus su dpa' bor bsgom ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3299: las byed kyi dus su dum bur bsgom ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3300: phata bsgom pa'i lam gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3301: phata spyod pa'i nges pa med pa gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3302: dus la nges pa med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3303: gnas la nges pa med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3304: grogs la nges pa med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3305: phata spyod pa nges med gsum mo /
NK040(thi)003:3307: sems la rtogs pa med pas rtogs pa'i 'bras bu chos sku thob de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3308: ngag sgra la rang bzhin med par rtogs pas 'bras bu longs sku thob ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3309: lus kyis sems can gyi don byed nus pas 'bras bu sprul sku thob ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3310: phata thob par byed pa'i 'bras bu gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3312: gsol 'debs kyi dus bla ma dran par bya ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3313: bskyed rims kyi dus su yi dam dran par byas te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3314: 'jigs par 'gro ba'i dus su d+aa ki dran par bya ste phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3317: lus bying na phyag dang bskor bas gseng de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3318: ngag bying na mdo dang snying pos gseng de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3319: sems bying na ting nge 'dzin gyis bsing de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3322: lus kyi bya ba bsgyur de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3323: ngag gi cal col bsgyur te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3324: sems kyi dran rtogs bsgyur te phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3326: phata rgyun chad med pa gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3327: lus zag bcas kyi dge ba rgyun chad med de phata bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3328: ngag bzlas brjod rgyun chad med de phata bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3329: sems ting nge 'dzin la rgyun chad med de phata bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3330: phata rgyun chad med pa gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3331: phata la bzla ba gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3332: gzhi gnyis med shes pa la lta ba med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3333: rtsa ba mthong ba la bsgom pa med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3334: don rtogs pa la rnam smin med de phata bya /
NK040(thi)003:3335: phata la bzla ba gsum mo //
NK040(thi)003:3336: dam pa rin po ches mdzad pa'i phata chos sum cu so drug go //
NK040(thi)003:3337: dgu pa mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i mngon rtogs kyi ching ni /
NK040(thi)003:3338: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i tshogs las zur du yod pas der gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3339: bcu pa dbang bskur chos sgo 'byed pa'i ching ni /
NK040(thi)003:3340: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i dbang chog zur du yod pas der gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3341: bcu gcig pa ngo sprod nam mkha' go 'byed kyi ching ni /
NK040(thi)003:3342: ngo sprod nam mkha' sgo 'byed zur du yod pas der gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3343: bcu gnyis pa las bzhi sbyin bsregs kyis ching ni logs su yod pa la gsal /
NK040(thi)003:3344: bcu gsum pa lhan thabs gnad kyis phreng bas ching /
NK040(thi)003:3345: bcu bzhi dam pa'i 'phrul gcod kyi ching /
NK040(thi)003:3346: bco lnga pa gcod khrid gsal sgron gyi ching dang gsum ni zur du gsal lo //
NK040(thi)003:3347: yang lus la nad med dang zhing gcod yin na thog ma'i zil non 'phen sa dbang sdud /
NK040(thi)003:3348: dmar 'gyed la sogs pa'i nad gcod thabs dang bcas pa gcig kyang mi dgos /
NK040(thi)003:3349: de na ci byed na thog ma sems bskyed dang /
NK040(thi)003:3351: bar du skyabs 'gro sems bskyed gsol 'debs bdud rtsi dkar 'byed /
NK040(thi)003:3352: dmar 'gyed 'dod yon lnga la dmigs pa dus re la nyi shu rtsa gcig dang /
NK040(thi)003:3353: gtor gzhong mas bsngo ba smon lam dang /
NK040(thi)003:3354: gtor len gong du yod pa ltar spyi skabs bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3355: nad can gnyan mig btsal ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:3356: nad med dge sbyor skyong ba gnyis /
NK040(thi)003:3357: zhi drag gcun thabs so sor gces /
NK040(thi)003:3359: de rnams kyis dngos gzhi nyams len gyis rims pa song /
NK040(thi)003:3360: spyi don gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga ni /
NK040(thi)003:3361: nang par snga mo nas dpon slob kun gyis gnyan sar gar 'gro sar zil gnon gong bzhin 'phangs /
NK040(thi)003:3362: de nas dpon slob kun gyi gcod thun skor gcig rdzogs pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:3363: dem byed de ni khra ther byed cing /
NK040(thi)003:3364: zil non nang ma bsdu ba ni /
NK040(thi)003:3365: shar nas rnga rke rims par g.yas bskor du bsdu zhing /
NK040(thi)003:3366: shar du bud+d+ha d+aa ki ni h'u /
NK040(thi)003:3368: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro bdag gis thugs kar bsdu /
NK040(thi)003:3369: de bzhin du lhor rat+na d+aa ki ni h'u /
NK040(thi)003:3370: rin chen mkha' 'gro bdag gi thugs kar bsdu /
NK040(thi)003:3371: nub du pad+ma d+aa ki ni h'u /
NK040(thi)003:3372: pad+ma mkha' 'gro bdag gi thugs kar bsdu /
NK040(thi)003:3373: byang du karma d+aa ki ni h'u /
NK040(thi)003:3374: las kyi mkha' 'gro bdag gi thugs kar bsdu /
NK040(thi)003:3375: khra ther bzo ba'i dus su badz+ra d+aa ki ni h'u brjod cing /
NK040(thi)003:3376: rdo rje mkha' 'gro bdag gi thugs kar bsdu /
NK040(thi)003:3378: stan bkyag nas sngar rdo gtel khrid zin yod na /
NK040(thi)003:3379: len nas skud pa dkrol zhing zur du bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:3380: lcags khang nang gi gnas gdon lus gdon rnams /
NK040(thi)003:3381: rgya grog tshang la rdog rto phog pa bzhin du /
NK040(thi)003:3382: lcags khang gi khar zings kyi bud nas phyi'i lha 'dre rnams dang lhan cig tu yod par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3383: de yang dkar nag shan 'byed lha 'dre rol khrid kyis gnad ces gsung pas /
NK040(thi)003:3385: rang nyid khros ma nag mor bsgom pa'i mdun du rde'u gcig bzhag la /
NK040(thi)003:3387: na mo rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas
NK040(thi)003:3388: pa'i bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK040(thi)003:3390: lha 'dre khyed rnams kyis nang nas bdag cag rnal
NK040(thi)003:3391: 'byor pa'i bka' la mi nyan pa gsung la mi
NK040(thi)003:3392: bstod pa / dngos grub mi ster ba /
NK040(thi)003:3394: mgo bskor rjes snyog phyir 'brang byed pa yi lha
NK040(thi)003:3395: 'dre gang yin pa thams cad rde'u 'di la khug
NK040(thi)003:3399: de nas blang nas gcod ral ba'i skabs kyi rdo gtel bzung nas khyer lug dang mthun no //
NK040(thi)003:3400: de nas khres se bsgrig pa yin te /
NK040(thi)003:3401: gal te char pa babs na kun gyi mal stan phud cing phata brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK040(thi)003:3402: rang nyid rje btsun ma sku mdog dmar mo re re bsgom la /
NK040(thi)003:3403: kun gyi shing phra ma'i lcags mtshan gyis go kha bshad cing phata brgya brjod /
NK040(thi)003:3404: nged 'di nas tsher spo ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:3405: gnas su ma pheb kyi bar du kha char ma btang cig /
NK040(thi)003:3408: der gnas pa'i sa bdag klu gnyan rnams bra ma'i
NK040(thi)003:3409: lcags tshan gyis bshad nas kha char mi btang bar
NK040(thi)003:3410: khas blangs te / de rnams kyi dbang po sgo lnga nas me dmar phyu ru ru 'bar nas /
NK040(thi)003:3411: snang srid lha klu sa bdag rnams tshig la khad de char bcad pas /
NK040(thi)003:3412: nam mkha' dwangs zhing nyi ma tsha bar bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3413: kun gyis de ltar nyams su len pa gal che ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3414: de nas khal rta yod na bkal thon pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:3416: rjes la dag pa rnam gsum ni /
NK040(thi)003:3417: rjes chog byas pas snang srid dag /
NK040(thi)003:3419: phata brjod pa tsam gyis sngar gyi lcags khang de
NK040(thi)003:3420: nyid yongs su 'gyur pa las rin po che sna
NK040(thi)003:3421: tshogs las grub pa'i sa gzhi 'dod yon sna tshogs
NK040(thi)003:3423: de'i steng du rang dang lha 'dre thams cad slob dpon slob bu'i tshul du bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3424: de nas rang nyid mal gyi nyal sar skyil krung bcas nas bsdad la /
NK040(thi)003:3425: sems can thams cad kyi don du skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed de /
NK040(thi)003:3426: swa b+ha was stong par gyur pa'i ngang las /
NK040(thi)003:3427: b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs grub pa'i sa gzhi rnam par dag pa'i dbus su /
NK040(thi)003:3428: pam las pad+ma a las zla ba'i steng du h+r+aihdakara
NK040(thi)003:3429: po 'od zer kun tu 'phro ba las 'od zer
NK040(thi)003:3431: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mchod /
NK040(thi)003:3432: sems can thams cad smin 'od zer tshur 'dus yongs
NK040(thi)003:3433: su gyur pa las bdag nyid thugs rje chen po
NK040(thi)003:3434: kha sar pa ni sku mdog dkar po zhal cig
NK040(thi)003:3435: phyag gnyis pa / g.yas mchod sbyin /
NK040(thi)003:3437: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan du mas brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)003:3438: zhabs sems dpa'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'i dbu la /
NK040(thi)003:3439: zla ba'i gdan la bla ma 'od dpag med bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)003:3441: mgrin par +aah thugs kar zla ba'i steng h+r+aih h+r+aihls
NK040(thi)003:3442: 'od 'phros pas sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK040(thi)003:3443: spyan drangs badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah dzahmh'u bam
NK040(thi)003:3444: hoh ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa gnyis su
NK040(thi)003:3445: med pa las mchod pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:3446: badz+ra ar+g+ham pra tits+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)003:3448: skyon gyi ma gos sku mdog dkar /
NK040(thi)003:3450: rang gi thugs ka'i h+r+aih'i mtha' bskor du /
NK040(thi)003:3451: yi ge drug pas g.yas su 'khor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:3452: de nas ngag tu ma ni pad+me h'u /
NK040(thi)003:3453: ces brgya rtsa brgyad bgrang zhing /
NK040(thi)003:3454: yid kyi thugs ka'i yi ge drug pa las 'od
NK040(thi)003:3455: zer bdud rtsi'i 'dod yon phun sum tshogs par spros
NK040(thi)003:3456: pas gnas gdon lus gdon snang srid kun der gnas
NK040(thi)003:3457: pa'i / lha 'dre rnams kyi sdig sdug nad dang bsnad yar rmas 'gram /
NK040(thi)003:3459: nor gyi shor god la sogs sos nas /
NK040(thi)003:3460: lus kyi lang tsho bkrag mdangs dang ldan zhing lha
NK040(thi)003:3461: 'dre rang dang gnas khang dang longs spyod kyis lha
NK040(thi)003:3462: 'dre gzhan gyis lus dang gnas khang longs spyod thams
NK040(thi)003:3463: cad zil gyis mnan par bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:3464: de nas yum chen gyis rjes chog ni /
NK040(thi)003:3465: phata rang nyid ma cig dkar mo /
NK040(thi)003:3466: phata mdun du yum chen ser mo /
NK040(thi)003:3467: phata bar du snang srid lha 'dre rnams bsam mo //
NK040(thi)003:3468: ma cig yum chen gnyis kyi thugs ka'i a dkar
NK040(thi)003:3469: ser las 'od zer la sogs sngar ltar babs pas
NK040(thi)003:3470: / snang srid kyi don sngar ltar bsam zhing /
NK040(thi)003:3472: dmigs pa brgya rtsa brgyad dang /
NK040(thi)003:3475: de nas phata gnyis bzlas pa tsam gyis gcig gis snang srid lha 'dre thams cad mnyes nas /
NK040(thi)003:3476: lha 'dre rnams kyis byis pa dkar mdzes yid du
NK040(thi)003:3477: 'ong ba'i ro gcig rang la 'chi ba med pa
NK040(thi)003:3478: tshe'i dngos grub tu phul bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:3479: gcig gis yum chen rang la thim nas /
NK040(thi)003:3480: rang nyid rje btsun ma dmar po gcig tu gyur
NK040(thi)003:3481: pa'i gri gug gis rtse mos ro de blangs nas
NK040(thi)003:3482: g.yon gyi ka p+aa la'i nang du bcug ste /
NK040(thi)003:3483: gri gug gis rgyab pa dmar nyob kyis song bar bsam /
NK040(thi)003:3484: ngag tu ram yam kham gsum brjod pa tsam gyis thugs ka nas me chu rlung gsum spros pas /
NK040(thi)003:3485: sha khrag gi dngos po sreg sbyong bkrus nas dwangs ma la +aahmh'u /
NK040(thi)003:3486: gnyis brjod pa tsam gyis gcig gis zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi gyur par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3487: gcig gis rang gi 'thung ba tsam gyis gzi brjid longs spyod phun sum tshogs te /
NK040(thi)003:3488: tshe'i dngos grub tu gyur par bsgoms /
NK040(thi)003:3490: de nas yig brgya bsngo bas dge rtsa dag /
NK040(thi)003:3492: ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:3493: gang yang bdag blo gti mug pas //
NK040(thi)003:3494: legs spyod 'di la nyes byas gang //
NK040(thi)003:3495: gang phyir lus can skyabs gyur pa //
NK040(thi)003:3496: de kun gnas bdag rnams kyis bzod par gsol //
NK040(thi)003:3497: gang yang bdag cag las dang po pa'i sems can du gyur pas /
NK040(thi)003:3498: gcod yul nyams su blang ba la /
NK040(thi)003:3499: chad pa dang lhag pa gong 'og 'khrug pa ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba /
NK040(thi)003:3500: mchod pa'i dngos po chung zhing ngan pa gtsang sbras la phyed pa /
NK040(thi)003:3501: mdor na nyes pa'i tshogs ci mchis pa thams cad bzod par mdzad du gsol /
NK040(thi)003:3502: badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya ces sogs yi ge brgya pa lhag chad kha bskang bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3504: zab don thugs snying las phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK040(thi)003:3505: grub thob gcod kyi brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad
NK040(thi)003:3506: bdag dang snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad
NK040(thi)003:3508: lha 'dre khyed rnams kyis dang po bdag la cho
NK040(thi)003:3509: 'phrul gdug rtsub bstan zhing gnod pa bskyal ba dang
NK040(thi)003:3510: / phyi nas gus par 'dud cing phan btag pa dang /
NK040(thi)003:3511: bdag gis kyang khyed rnams la spyod lam 'jam pos lus sbyin par btang ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:3512: spyod lam rtsub mos gnod pa bskyal ba la sogs
NK040(thi)003:3513: pa thabs sna tshogs kyis sgo nas lha 'dre byang
NK040(thi)003:3514: chub kyi lam la bkod pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba
NK040(thi)003:3515: la brten nas lha 'dre khyed rnams kyi rgyud la
NK040(thi)003:3516: yod pa'i bsam sbyor nyon mongs pa'i gdug rtsub thams
NK040(thi)003:3517: cad zhi nas / byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:3518: khyed rnams kyis bdag la mtho mtsham zhing gnod pa bskyal ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:3519: phyis nas chos byas cing gus par btud pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba la brten nas /
NK040(thi)003:3520: rgyal po byams pa'i stobs dang /
NK040(thi)003:3521: gnod sbyin sha za spun lnga bzhin du /
NK040(thi)003:3522: bdag gis 'khor gyi 'dus pa dang por gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:3523: khyed rnams kyis las ngan gyi sgribs pa bag chags
NK040(thi)003:3524: dang bcas pa skad cig nyid la byang zhing dag
NK040(thi)003:3525: nas kun mkhyen sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po
NK040(thi)003:3527: rnal 'byor pa bdag gis kyang lha 'dre khyed rnams la lus sbyin pa btang ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:3528: byams pa'i sems kyis khyed rnams rjes su bzung ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba la brten nas /
NK040(thi)003:3530: rgyal bu dge don bzhin du pha rol tu phyin
NK040(thi)003:3531: pa thams cad myur du rdzogs nas rang gzhan thams
NK040(thi)003:3532: cad don gnyis ldan pa'i sangs rgyas rin po che
NK040(thi)003:3533: myur du thob par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:3535: spyir rjes chog 'di rnams gzab na gcod lam du 'gro ba yin pas /
NK040(thi)003:3538: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa yis /
NK040(thi)003:3539: ces sogs gong du gtor gzhong ma'i 'gab tu yod pa'i bkra shis de ltar bya'o //
NK040(thi)003:3540: de nas sngar rdo gtel khrid nas yod na /
NK040(thi)003:3541: rang gi yig drug bzla zhing rdo gtel la phu byed cing /
NK040(thi)003:3542: rdo gtel de thugs rje chen por byin gyis rlabs
NK040(thi)003:3543: la dkar tha ra ra rang rang gi gnas su
NK040(thi)003:3545: sngar gyi gnyan sa de la rang gi rgyab bstan nas rdo gtel rgyab tu 'phang ngo //
NK040(thi)003:3546: de nas thab kha mal bsdud gnyan mig dag /
NK040(thi)003:3548: kam ka ni dang yig brgya brjod cing /
NK040(thi)003:3549: nyal sa dang thab kha bshig go //
NK040(thi)003:3550: de nas lha 'dre rnams la rten gyi skyel dar bzhag pa ni /
NK040(thi)003:3551: rdo la yig drug brko la thugs rje chen por bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3552: ye shes pa spyan drangs la bstim /
NK040(thi)003:3553: gnyan sa 'dir gnas pa'i snang srid kyi lha 'dre
NK040(thi)003:3554: bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad rnams kyis yi ge
NK040(thi)003:3557: gsol ba btab pa'i yul du 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK040(thi)003:3558: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)003:3560: 'jug bsdud phyir bzhag rnam gsum ni //
NK040(thi)003:3561: sha sogs snang srid bzhag pa gces //
NK040(thi)003:3563: phata gcig byas pa tsam gyis rang gi sha khrag nyil gyis song ste /
NK040(thi)003:3564: gnyan sa stim gyis gang nas mal du lha 'dre rnams kyis bsgo bsha' byed par bsam la /
NK040(thi)003:3565: ngag tu bdag gis gnas po chen po gnas bdag chen po 'di rnams la /
NK040(thi)003:3566: khyod snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre thams cad kyis gnod dang 'tshe ba ma byed gcig /
NK040(thi)003:3567: gal te bdag gis gnas po 'di la gnod pa byas na /
NK040(thi)003:3569: gnam lcags rdo rje'i sgyog rgyab /
NK040(thi)003:3570: yung dkar drag po'i thun brdeg /
NK040(thi)003:3572: de bas longs spyod chen po 'dis tshim par gyis la /
NK040(thi)003:3573: spyi'i lha 'dre thams cad kyis gnas bdag 'di rnams la gnod 'tshe ma byed la /
NK040(thi)003:3574: dga' mgur byang chub kyi sems dang ldan nas /
NK040(thi)003:3575: so so rang rang gi gnas su gyes shig /
NK040(thi)003:3577: shes pa keng rus gar byed gces /
NK040(thi)003:3578: bzhad pa'i gad rgyang bcu gnyis gces /
NK040(thi)003:3580: phata ces brjod pas khros ma dgu la sogs pa'i
NK040(thi)003:3581: phyi yi zil non thams cad bdag gis thugs kar
NK040(thi)003:3582: bsdu / de nas 'gro ba dang sprad la phata
NK040(thi)003:3583: gcig brjod pas rang gi rus pa phyi na sha
NK040(thi)003:3585: nang na rkang dang lha ba med pa'i rus pa dkar si li ba /
NK040(thi)003:3586: rkang dang lha ba lhu tshig gi bar na me lhab lhab /
NK040(thi)003:3587: du ba thul thul byed pa gar khyug khyug byed nas ngag tu /
NK040(thi)003:3594: ces pa bzhad pa'i gad rgyang bcu gnyis sgrog cing /
NK040(thi)003:3595: phyi bltas mi byed cing gnyan sa ma bud kyi bar du 'gro ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3596: de nas pha lta'i gnyan mgo mthong ba dang /
NK040(thi)003:3597: dbang bsdud la sogs gong dang 'dra ba yin /
NK040(thi)003:3598: gcod 'phro mi bcad na gong gi de ltar byed pa yin la /
NK040(thi)003:3599: gcod 'phro bcad nas khyim du 'gro na /
NK040(thi)003:3600: gong ltar rdo gtel bzung mi dgos /
NK040(thi)003:3601: gad rgyang bcu gnyis sgrog cing /
NK040(thi)003:3602: yar mar mi mthong ba'i sa mtshams su khyung nag bzhag dgos te /
NK040(thi)003:3604: phyi them phyi ru ma non na /
NK040(thi)003:3605: nor len phyi rjes snyag pa 'dra /
NK040(thi)003:3606: de la dmag dpon khyung nag bzhag /
NK040(thi)003:3607: ces gsungs pas yar gnyan sa mi mthong /
NK040(thi)003:3608: mar khang pa mi mthong ba'i mtshams su /
NK040(thi)003:3609: tho gcig brtsig la bya khyung gi sku'am /
NK040(thi)003:3610: khrmo bris la kha phyi rjes su bstan nas bzhag la /
NK040(thi)003:3611: ngag tu khrmo khrmo zhes brjod pas bya khyung nag
NK040(thi)003:3612: po me'i gshog pa can gsum gyis lag sbrel nas
NK040(thi)003:3613: kha phyi rjes su gyu nas yod par bsgom /
NK040(thi)003:3614: de nas phata brjod pas rang dang gnas khang gi
NK040(thi)003:3615: bar la 'od snam shar tsam gyis 'brel pa'i lam
NK040(thi)003:3617: rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo gser gyi
NK040(thi)003:3618: rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur nas hri li li
NK040(thi)003:3619: 'od kyi li li song nas khyim du phyin par
NK040(thi)003:3620: bsgom mo // nad pa mi skya pho mo dang /
NK040(thi)003:3621: gcod dmigs bzung mi shes pa yin na /
NK040(thi)003:3622: rjes chog gi byed las thams cad gcod dpon gyi rog byed dgos so //
NK040(thi)003:3623: spyir gcod byed pa la gcod mgo dang /
NK040(thi)003:3624: gcod 'phro gzab pa rnal 'byor dam tshig yin /
NK040(thi)003:3626: gcod 'phro gcod nas khyim du 'gro bsam pa'i gnyan
NK040(thi)003:3627: sa de la slong tshad dang chod tshad tshul bzhin
NK040(thi)003:3629: des rjes kyi bya ba song /
NK040(thi)003:3630: de ltar sbyor dngos rjes gsum gcig tu dril ba'i sgo nas /
NK040(thi)003:3631: bdud kyi gcod yul dgos 'dod kun 'byung rin po
NK040(thi)003:3632: che mu tig gi phreng ba zhes bya ba song
NK040(thi)003:3633: ngo // kye ma 'di la mi brtson su zhig yod //
NK040(thi)003:3634: rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab dgongs rgyud dam chos 'di //
NK040(thi)003:3635: thar pa'i lam ston 'dren mchog dam pa yin //
NK040(thi)003:3636: zab rgyas kun khyab kun phan nor bu 'di //
NK040(thi)003:3637: phyogs 'dzin grub mtha' spang ba'i tho ba yin //
NK040(thi)003:3638: rin chen rin thang med pa'i gcod gzhung 'di //
NK040(thi)003:3639: gdul bya dang ba 'dren pa'i lcags kyu yin //
NK040(thi)003:3640: chos pa'i shan 'byed chos kyi gser gling yin //
NK040(thi)003:3641: lha 'dre dbang sdud gsang ba'i lcags kyu yin //
NK040(thi)003:3642: nyon mongs lam slong ye shes me dpung yin //
NK040(thi)003:3643: bar chad lam slong bkra shis dpal 'bar yin //
NK040(thi)003:3644: 'chi bdag bdud dpung srung ba'i 'khor lo yin //
NK040(thi)003:3645: nad rnams kun 'joms sman gyi rgyal po yin //
NK040(thi)003:3646: drag sngags kun bzlog byad ma 'bum sdug yin //
NK040(thi)003:3647: byang chub lam sgron thar pa'i them skas yin //
NK040(thi)003:3648: 'chi ba lam slong chos sku'i zhing khams yin //
NK040(thi)003:3649: kye ma 'di la mi 'jug su zhig yod //
NK040(thi)003:3650: gcod gzhung zab rgyas rgya mtsho rgya chen las //
NK040(thi)003:3651: nyung 'dus zab don don 'di bkod pa ni //
NK040(thi)003:3652: tshad ma gsum ldan man ngag dam pa yin //
NK040(thi)003:3653: rang bzo pho tshod 'di la ma mchis snyam //
NK040(thi)003:3654: 'on kyang ma shes log shes 'gal 'khrul tshogs //
NK040(thi)003:3655: gcod brgyud mkhas grub rnams la gzod par gsol //
NK040(thi)003:3656: legs pa'i lam ston dge ba'i tshogs mchis na //
NK040(thi)003:3657: 'gro kun bdud bzhi'i mtha' las rgyal bar shog /
NK040(thi)003:3658: gcod gzhung 'di rang bzo dang pho tshod ma yin pa'i don ni /
NK040(thi)003:3659: ma cig gis gsungs pa'i zhal gdam bcu gsum ma /
NK040(thi)003:3661: nyer zhi rin chen sgron ma /
NK040(thi)003:3664: spa yig la sogs rnams dang /
NK040(thi)003:3665: +aar+ya de bas mdzad pa'i gzhung chung /
NK040(thi)003:3666: dam pa mdzad pa'i dmigs pa skor gsum /
NK040(thi)003:3667: pan+di ta don yod rdo rjes mdzad pa'i zab don thugs snying /
NK040(thi)003:3668: kun dgas mdzad pa'i gces pa nyer gcig /
NK040(thi)003:3671: ma cig ma cig gi zhal gdam gser zhun ma /
NK040(thi)003:3672: ma cig gis gser thur ma /
NK040(thi)003:3673: ye blos mdzad pa'i dkar sbyor /
NK040(thi)003:3674: o rgyan pad+mas mdzad pa'i gter gcod /
NK040(thi)003:3675: gzhan yang bla ma gong ma rnams kyis mdzad pa'i
NK040(thi)003:3676: yig sna la sogs man ngag rnams la brten nas
NK040(thi)003:3677: / bdud kyi gcod yul dgos 'dod kun 'byung rin
NK040(thi)003:3678: po che mu tig phreng ba zhes bya ba 'di
NK040(thi)003:3679: / / kah thog pa'i 'bangs kyi tha mar gyur
NK040(thi)003:3680: pa'i ku su lu pu n+ye la k+sha sa sbyar
NK040(thi)003:3682: dpe 'di phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad dar zhing rgyas par gyur cig /
